\id DEU - Mbula
\h Ɓǝsǝlǝki Nggurcau
\toc1 Tongnoia Malǝmce mala Musa mǝnana à tunǝi ama Ɓǝsǝlǝki Nggurcau ka
\toc2 Ɓǝs Nggur
\toc3 Nggur
\mt1 Ɓǝsǝlǝki Nggurcau
\imt1 MƏNCAU
\ip Malǝmce mala \bk Ɓǝsǝlǝki Nggurcau\bk* ka tsaɗya mala masǝlǝata acau mala Musa na mǝnana banggi amǝ Isǝrayila a nzali Mowap ka, yì ban mǝnana à yi cam kam a masǝlǝata gya mǝsauwe malea aɓa pǝɗanban, sǝ à malanǝ̀ kutio à nǝ̀ ak nzali Kan'ana ka.
\ip Aɓea mugulacau mǝnana à gilǝia aɓa malǝmcenî ka à nda ka: (1) Musa nyesǝ ɗenyicau arǝ acau-kumban mǝgulke mala apǝlǝa lumi-ine mǝnana à kùtí ka. Zǝmbi aɓwe ɓǝà ɗenyinǝ gingnǝban mǝnana Ɓakuli gingnǝia aɓa pǝɗanban ngga, sǝ ɓǝà dumnǝ okiru andǝ domǝsǝcau aban Ɓakuli. (2) Musa nyare banggia wia Anzongcau Lum sǝ ɓǝsǝlǝki bǝlia wia gìr mǝnana Nzongcau Mǝdǝmbe nakiyi ka, ace mǝnana ɓǝà sǝlǝ ama paɓamuru malea ɓǝ̀ pà aban Yahweh nǝmurǝi. Pǝlǝa ɓǝsǝlǝ bǝlia wia acau mala anggurcau ɗàngɗáng mǝnana à nǝ̀ yálmúr do-yilǝmu mala Isǝrayila a nzali pacau ka. (3) Musa kasǝɓalǝ aɓwe arǝ ɓá kùrcau mala Ɓakuli mǝnana pangnǝia ka, sǝ ndarǝ banggia wia ama bwal acau mala kùrcau mǝnia andǝ kùr ɓamuru arǝ kpatea, mǝnana dumǝna púp à nǝ̀ peǎ ka, ɓǝà pǝlǝi ɓǝ̀ duk bǝshe. (4) À pè Jesǝwa gara mala bwal túró do ɓwamǝgule amur aɓwe ace twal bancame mala Musa. Anzǝm mana Musa tuna nggyal mala ɓwangsǝki domǝsǝcau mala Ɓakuli, sǝ nana tsǝkbu male amur atau mala amǝ Isǝrayila ka, pǝlǝa wú a Mowap, a takuli mala Nggeasala Jodan.
\ip Múrcau mǝgule mala malǝmce mǝnia ka nda mǝnana ama Ɓakuli amsǝna aɓwana male mǝnana tària ka, sǝ tsǝ̀ngŋǝ́nià-bù, yì aɓwana male mǝnana earcea ka. Aɓwana male ka ɓǝà ɗenyinǝ mǝnia, ɓǝà earce sǝ ɓǝà oki wi, ace mǝnana ɓǝà kum yilǝmu andǝ lidǝmba mala tsǝkbu.
\ip Acau mǝnana aɓwana súrǝ̀ia pepè aɓa malǝmce mǝnia ka à nda ka amǝnana Yesu tunǝia ama nzongcau mǝgule mala anzongcau kat, mǝnana ama: <<Wu earce Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ ɓabum wun kat, andǝ yilǝmi wun kat, andǝ koman ma'wun kat.>> \xt 6:4-6\xt*
\iot Agir mǝnana a ɓalǝi ka
\io1 Nacau'ha mǝdǝmbe mala Musa \ior 1:1--4:49\ior*
\io1 Ɓaria nacau'ha mala Musa \ior 5:1--26:19\ior*
\io2 1. Anzongcau Lum \ior 5:1--10:22\ior*
\io2 2. Angguracau, andǝ atsǝkcau andǝ anunkiru \ior 11:1--26:19\ior*
\io1 Acau mala sǝlǝe ace kùtí a nzali Kan'ana \ior 27:1--28:68\ior*
\io1 Kwakita kùrcau ɗǝm a bǝshe \ior 29:1--30:20\ior*
\io1 Masǝlǝata acau mala Musa \ior 31:1--33:29\ior*
\io1 Lú mala Musa \ior 34:1-12\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Musa tita masǝlǝata bangcau male
\p 
\v 1 Amǝnia ka à nda ka acau mǝnana Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila kat, a nkaring takuli mala Nggeasala Jodan, a njenza, aɓa Araba\f + \fr 1:1 \fq Araba \ft ka nda ɓawanban aɓa pǝɗanban.\f* a mgbasho nǝ Suf, anre Paran, andǝ Tofel, andǝ Laban Hazerot, andǝ Dizahap ka.
\v 2 Twal a Horep, nǝ njar Nkono Seyir, aban ká Kadesh-Baniya ka, gya mala nongŋo lum-nong-mwashat na.
\p 
\v 3 Nda a pwari mǝdǝmbe mala lum-nong-mwashatia zongŋo aɓa lumi-inea pǝlǝa,\f + \fr 1:3 \fq lumi-inea pǝlǝa: \ft Akani ka amǝ Isǝrayila malanǝ̀ kùtí aɓa nzali Kan'ana, sǝama ɓǝ́ à kutina ɗiɗyal apǝlǝa lumi-ine mǝno à kùtí ka, twal a Kadesh-Baniya, ɓǝ̀ pà ace mgbicau mǝnana à mgbikî Yahweh raka.\f* anzǝm mana amǝ Isǝrayila nyingŋǝna Masar ka sǝ Musa nacau nǝ amǝ Isǝrayila, banggia wia gìr mǝnana kat Yahweh banggi wi ama ɓǝ̀ banggia wia púp ka.
\v 4 Anggo ka, Musa angŋǝna dǝmba linamurǝm amur Sihon Murǝm mala amǝ'Amor, mǝnana do a Heshbon ngga, andǝ Og Murǝm mala amǝ Bashan, mǝnana do a Ashtarot a Edǝri ka.
\v 5 A njartakuli mala nkaring Nggeasala Jodan, aɓa nzali mala amǝ'Mowap, sǝ Musa mǝngiɓa mǝnia yì nggurcau ka ama:\f + \fr 1:5 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ɓal 21:21-35\xt*\ft .\f*
\m 
\v 6 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm bangga sǝm cau, mǝnana sǝm nda a Horep ka, ama:
\pi1 Wun ngga, wu dumǝna a ban nkono man banì sauwuna, karǝna anggo.
\v 7 Wu pǝlǝa, wu twal gya ma'wun, sǝ wu o a nzali múr ankono mala amǝ'Amor, andǝ abu-nzali mǝnana kat à nda a murkala andǝia a Araba, aɓa nzali múr ankono, andǝ Negev, andǝ dulum a kún nggeamùr, aban ká nzali mala amǝ'Kan'ana, andǝ mala amǝ Lebano, kya bwal a kún Nggeasala Mǝgule, yì Yiufǝretis ka.
\v 8 Wu sǝni, ǝn pana wun mǝnia yi nzali ka. Wu kùtí aɓalǝi, wu kya e ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun. Mim Yahweh ka, ǝn kánagìr ama mǝ nǝ pè aká wun, yia Ibǝrayim, andǝ Ishaku, andǝ Yakupu, mǝnia yì nzali ka, andǝ amǝ'keà kat mana à nǝ̀ yia ɓǝlia nǝnzǝ́mò ka.
\s1 À twal aɓwana-mǝgule
\r (Puro 18:13-27)
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ cau ama:
\p 
\v 9 Ən bangga wun cau, a bàkú mǝno, ama:
\pi1 Pa mǝ nǝ gandǝ lidǝmba nǝ twal twalo mala duk ɓwamǝgule amur wun nǝmurǝam ɗàng.
\v 10 Acemǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, hatǝkina làkkì ma'wun, yalung ngga wu làkkìna kǝla làkkì mala anlero a bumkuli.
\v 11 Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh, yi Ɓakuli mala aká wun, tsǝa, ɓǝ̀ wu làkkì kàm kusǝ pas, sǝ ɓǝ̀ tsǝka wun buì, kǝla mana bang ama nǝ̀ pakka wun ngga!
\v 12 Lang sǝ mim nǝmurǝam ngga, mǝ nǝ gandǝ twal atanni ma'wun, andǝ dǝmbǝrya ma'wun andǝ aloasǝkiaban ma'wun a rǝarǝ wun?
\v 13 Wu twal aɓwana aɓalǝ wun, a koya tàu, aɓwana mana à kwarô, sǝ à ndanǝ sǝlǝe, à kǝ pea wia gulo ka. Amǝnia yì aɓwana ka, à nda mǝ nǝ tsǝia à nǝ̀ duk aɓwana-mǝgule amur wun ngga.
\p 
\v 14 Sǝ wun ngga, wu pam eare, ama, <<Gìr mǝnana kat a bang ama awu nǝ pè ka, mǝɓoarne na.>>
\p 
\v 15 Nda sǝ ǝn twal aɓwana-mǝgule amur atau ma'wun, aɓwana mana à kwarô sǝ à kǝ pea wia gulo ka. Ən tsǝia ɓǝà duk aɓwana-mǝgule amur wun: amǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mana à nǝ̀ ɗenyinǝ anggǝsan mala aɓwana á-mwashat, andǝ mala aɓwana gbǝman-mwashat, andǝ mala aɓwana lumi-tongno, andǝ mala aɓwana lum, kǝla amǝ'buno-gulo amur atau ma'wun.
\v 16 Sǝ ǝn pe amǝ'ɓashi ma'wun mǝnia yì kwarkiru, a mǝno yì pwari ka, ama:
\pi1 Wu ok acau mǝnana à nda a nre ka amǝ'eam wun ngga, sǝ wu pàk ɓashi aɓa mǝsǝcau a nre ɓwa andǝ mǝ'eambi, sǝ a nre ɓwa andǝ bǝri mǝnana ndanǝdo aɓalǝia ka.
\v 17 Wu kǝa lǝmdǝ tàrban aɓa pàk ɓashi ɗàng;\f + \fr 1:17 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa: \xt Pǝris 19:15; Nggur 16:19; Pas 24:23\xt*\ft .\f* wu ok cau mala koya ɓwa, ko mǝkyauwe, ko mǝgule. Wu kǝa ɓanggi ɓamǝsǝ kǝɓwa ɗàng, acemǝnana ɓashi ka, mala Ɓakuli na.
\pi1 Cau mǝnana kat gandǝ wun ngga, wu yinǝi abanam, mǝ nǝ yia oè.
\p 
\v 18 Sǝ a bàkú mǝno ka, ǝn kwarkir wun amur gir mǝnana kat wun nǝ̀ pàk ka.\f + \fr 1:18 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pur 18:13-26\xt*\ft .\f*
\s1 À tasǝ aburana ɓǝà kya shenzǝ nzali múr ankono
\r (Ɓal 13:1-33)
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ nacau aban amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 19 Pǝlǝa sǝm nying Horep, sǝm kútí nǝɓa nggea pǝɗanban mǝno kat mǝpà ɓangciunì, mǝnana wu sǝni a njar aban ká a nzali múr ankono mala amǝ'Amor, kǝla mǝnana Yahweh tsǝa ama ɓǝ̀ sǝm pàk ka. Lang sǝm yi bwalna Kadesh-Baniya ka,
\v 20 ǝn bangga wun nǝma: <<Wu bwalǝna nzali múr ankono mala amǝ'Amor, yì nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm kǝ pà sǝm ngga.
\v 21 Wu sǝni, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun tsǝ̀ngŋǝ́nà wun mǝnia yì nzali ka a ɓadǝm wun. Wu kyane, wu kya e ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun, kǝla mǝnana Yahweh, yi Ɓakuli mala aká wun, bangga wun ngga. Ɓangciu ɓǝ̀ kǝa pàkka wun, ko wun nǝ̀ gǝggǝli ɗang.>>
\p 
\v 22 Pǝlǝa wun kat ka, wu yiu abanam, wu bang ama, <<Came ɓǝ̀ sǝm túr aburana ɓǝà akdǝmba, ɓǝà kya shenzǝ ɓá nzalinì, sǝ ɓǝà yina sǝm nǝ cau amur njar mǝnana sǝm nǝ̀ eau nǝi, andǝ alá mǝnana sǝm nǝ̀ ká kàm ngga.>>
\p 
\v 23 Cê ɓoaram, nda sǝ ǝn twal aɓwana lum-nong-ɓari, ɓwa mwashat aɓa koya tàu ka.
\v 24 Amǝno yì aɓwana ka, à pǝlǝa à eauwe aban ká aɓa nzali múr ankono. À wari a bu Ɓangŋaban mala Eshkol, à kya shenzǝi, à sǝn ɓá nzalinì kat.
\v 25 Sǝ à twal aɓea ɓǝlanggun mala nzalinì, à bwal a buia, à yinǝia aban sǝm. À yi bangga sǝm ama, <<Nzali ka, mǝɓoarne na, mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm kǝ pà sǝmi ka.>>
\s1 Mgbikiru a Kadesh-Baniya
\r (Ɓal 14:1-10)
\sp Sǝ Musa lidǝmba nǝ cau ama:
\p 
\v 26 Sǝ wun ngga, wu ear ama wun nǝ̀ eauwe, wun nǝ̀ ká ɗàng; wu mgbicau arǝ nzongcau mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun.
\v 27 Wu nggwani aɓalǝ agumli ma'wun, sǝ wu bang ama, <<Acemana Yahweh ɓinǝmǝsǝ sǝm ngga, pusǝ sǝm aɓa nzali Masar ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ yi tasǝ sǝm a bù amǝ'Amor ɓǝà twalta sǝm.
\v 28 A ya ban sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ eauwe? Amǝ'eam sǝm ɓungina ɓabum sǝm nǝ cau mǝnana à bangga sǝm ama, <Aɓwana mǝno ka, à gulkio sǝ à dāh'rikya à kútì sǝm. Anggea-là malea ka, amǝgulke na, à gumbǝlia nǝ asheran mǝnana à dāh'rya à bwal kùli ka. Yàle sǝm sǝn akwatǝman-ɓwa kàm, aɓwana mǝnana à tunǝkia ama amǝ'kà Anak ka!> >>
\p 
\v 29 Pǝlǝa ǝn bangga wun nǝma, <<Cè wu gǝggǝli ɗàng; ǝn'ò ɓǝ̀ kǝa pakka wun arǝia ɗàng!
\v 30 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, mana kǝ ká dǝm wun ngga, nǝ̀ munǝ ace wun nǝ nggearǝì, kǝla mana pàk ace wun a Masar, mǝsǝ wun sǝni ka,
\v 31 sǝ aɓa pǝɗanban, ban mǝnana wu sǝnǝna twalo mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun twal wun, kǝla mana tárrú kǝ twal muni, a njargula mǝnana kat wu ging kam, sǝ wu yiu a ban mǝnia ka.>>
\p 
\v 32 Kat aɓa mǝnia ka, wu earnǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ɗàng;
\v 33 yì mana akà wun dǝmba, aban ká ace ala wun tà ban mana wun nǝ̀ duk kàttì ma'wun kàm, nǝ bǝsa a kùli nǝ bu-dù, sǝ nǝ pǝrɓang nǝ pwari ace lǝmdǝa wun njar mǝnana wun nǝ̀ pǝlǝ kam ngga.
\s1 Ɓashi a Kadesh-Baniya
\p 
\v 34 Yahweh ok gi acau ma'wun, bumi lúllô. Nda sǝ kángìr ama:
\pi1 
\v 35 Kǝɓwa pà kam a nza mǝɓike man, mǝnana nǝ̀ sǝn nzali mǝɓoarne mǝnana ǝn kángìr nǝma mǝ nǝ pè aká wun ngga, ɗàng.
\v 36 She kǝ Kalip, yì muna-ɓwabura mala Jefune. Yì ka, nǝ̀ sǝni, sǝ mǝ nǝ pè wi nzali mǝnana kusǝi parǝni ka, andǝ amǝkè, acemǝnana yì ka, kpata cau mem, Mim Yahweh, nǝ ɓabumi kat ka.
\p 
\v 37 Nda gbal, atàcau ma'wun ngga, bum Yahweh lul arǝàm, sǝ banggam ama, <<We gbal ka, a pà wu nǝ kútí kam ɗàng.
\v 38 Sǝama mǝbwalo kúntúró yì Jesǝwa, muna-ɓwabura mala Nun ngga, nǝ̀ kútí kam. Ɓakɓabumi, acemǝnana yì na nǝ̀ kánǝ amǝ Isǝrayila ɓǝà kya ak nzalinì ɓǝ̀ duk nzali liɓala malea ka.>>
\p 
\v 39 Pǝlǝa Yahweh bangga sǝm kat ama:
\pi1 Sǝ nggearǝ amuna mǝkèke ma'wun, mana wu bang ama à nǝ̀ pwania arǝ wun, andǝ amuna-burana ma'wun mǝnana yalung ngga à súrǝ̀ mǝɓoarne andǝ mǝɓane raka, à nǝ̀ kútí kam; mǝ nǝ pea wia mǝnia yì nzali ka, nǝ̀ duk girkuma malea.
\pi1 
\v 40 Sǝama wun adyan ngga, wu pǝlǝa, wu twal gya ma'wun aban ká aɓa pǝɗanban nǝ njargula ká Nggeamùr Nzuno.
\p 
\v 41 Pǝlǝa wu bang ama, <<Sǝm pàngŋǝ́nì Yahweh cauɓikea, sǝm nǝ̀ eauwe sǝm nǝ̀ ká munǝo, kǝla mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm sà'arǝ sǝm ngga.>> Nda sǝ koyan atà wun ngga gyar agirbura male arǝì, acemǝnana aɓa ɗenyicau ma'wun ngga, wu kǝ sǝni kǝla eau a nzali amúr ankono ka, pà nǝ̀ kwan ɗang.
\p 
\v 42 Sǝ Yahweh banggam ama, <<Banggia wia, ɓǝà kǝa na ama à nǝ̀ eau ɗang, sǝ ɓǝà kǝa munǝ ɗang, acemǝnana pà mǝ nǝ pà atà wun ɗàng, ɓǝ̀ ana raka aɓiwun amǝbura nǝ̀ nggá gandǝ wun.>>
\p 
\v 43 Nda sǝ ǝn bangga wun, sǝama wun ngga, wu tsǝkir cê ɗàng. Wu mgbicau arǝ sà'arǝban mala Yahweh, sǝ wu lo aɓa twalkicau, wu eau a nzali múr ankono.
\v 44 Sǝ lang amǝ'Amor mǝnana à do a mǝno yì nzali múr ankono, puro sǝ à yiu arǝ wun ngga, à pǝr wun kǝla mǝsǝnyi, à mesǝki wun a Seyir yi pur a Horma.
\v 45 Sǝ wu nyare wu yi ɓua a ɓadǝm Yahweh, sǝ Yahweh ka ɓinǝ ok ɓua ma'wun, kwakikiri arǝ wun ɗàng.
\v 46 Nda gìr mana tsǝa sǝ wu ueo a Kadesh wu pàkkì anonggio pas kàm ngga.
\c 2
\s1 Purî gya-gāli a ɓabondo
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ cau ama:
\p 
\v 1 Pǝlǝa sǝm pǝlǝ nǝnzǝ́m sǝm, sǝm twal gya aɓa pǝɗanban, a njargula ká Nggeamùr Nzuno, kǝla mana Yahweh banggam ngga. Sǝm twal anongŋo pas sǝm ndaban gumbǝli nzali múr ankono mala Seyir.
\v 2 Pǝlǝa Yahweh banggam ama:
\pi1 
\v 3 Banì sauwuna mana wu camarǝ gumbǝli ban mǝnia yì nzali múr ankono ka, kārǝ́na anggo. Adyan ngga, wu pǝlǝ múr wun nǝ njar-nza.
\v 4 Bangcau nǝ aɓwe, pea wia mǝnia yì nzongcau ka, ama, <<Wun ndo wun nǝ̀ kútí nǝɓa nzong-nzali mala aɓǝla ma'wun, yì amǝ'Edom, amǝkà Isǝwa, mana à ndanǝdo a Seyir ka. Yia ka ɓangciu nǝ̀ pàkkia wia arǝ wun. Ace mani ka, wu tsǝkir wun.
\v 5 Wu kǝa na ama wun nǝ̀ altacau, wun nǝ̀ munǝo arǝia ɗàng, acemǝnana pà mǝ nǝ pà wun ɓekǝ ban aɓa nzali malea ɗàng, ko ɓǝ̀ nda bǝti kǝla tangŋa mala ɓakusǝu mwashat ka. Acemǝnana ǝn panì Isǝwa mǝnia yì nzali múr ankono mala Seyir ka, dumǝna male.
\v 6 Wun ngga, wun nǝ̀ kúr girlina mǝnana wun nǝ̀ lǐ, andǝ mùr mana wun nǝ̀ nu ka a buia nǝ bolo-azǝrfa.>>
\p 
\v 7 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga tsǝ̀ngŋǝ́nà wun bù amur túró mana kat wu tsǝk abu wun amurí ka. Yì ka sǝlǝnace gya ma'wun nǝɓa nggea pǝɗanban mǝnia ka. Aɓalǝ apǝlǝa mǝno lumi-ine (40) ka, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun na atà wun bà; yàle ko wu ɗwanyi kǝgir ɗàng.\f + \fr 2:7 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Nggur 8:2-4; 29:5; Nehe 9:21\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 8 Ace mǝno ka, sǝm yi kútì nzong-nzali mala aɓǝla ma'sǝm, amǝkà Isǝwa mana à ndanǝdo a Seyir ka, sǝm mgbàllì njargula Araba a ɓè bù sǝm ɓǝ̀ ɓwa pur a Elat andǝ Eziyon-Geba ka. Sǝm twal gya aban ká a pǝɗanban mala amǝ'Mowap.
\p 
\v 9 Pǝlǝa Yahweh banggam ama, <<Wu kǝa na ama wun nǝ̀ altacau arǝ amǝ'Mowap ama wun nǝ̀ kánǝ lwa arǝia ɗàng, acemǝnana pà mǝ nǝ pà wun ɓekǝ ban aɓa nzali malea ama ma'wun na ka ɗàng. Mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana ǝn panì amǝkà Lotu nzali Ar, dumǝna girkuma malea.>>
\p 
\v 10 (Amǝ'Emit nda mǝnana à duk kam ɗiɗyal ka. Yià amǝ Emit ka, à làkkì sǝ à ndanǝ rǝcandǝa. Aɓwana amǝ'dāh'rike na, kǝla amǝ'Anak.
\v 11 Amǝ'Emit andǝ amǝ'Anak kǝm ngga aɓwana súrǝ̀ia ama amǝ'Refa, sǝama amǝ'Mowap kǝ tunǝia ama amǝ'Emit.
\v 12 Ɗiɗyal ka, amǝ'Hor nda mana à do a nzali Seyir ka, sǝ amǝkà Isǝwa mana à tunǝia ama amǝ'Edom ngga, à yi pǝria, à wal-luia sǝ à ak nzalinì arǝia, à duk kam, kǝla mana amǝ Isǝrayila pangnǝ aɓwana a nzali mǝnana Yahweh pea wia ɓǝ̀ duk malea ka.)
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ banggi amǝ Isǝrayila cau ama:
\p 
\v 13 Sǝ Yahweh bangga sǝm ama, <<Adyan ngga wu lo, wu yàlî myalmúr Zeret.>>
\p Anggo gbal sǝm lo, sǝm yàlî myalmúr Zeret.
\v 14 Lo ma'sǝm mana sǝm nying Kadesh-Baniya, sǝm twal gya sǝ sǝm yi yàlî myalmúr Zeret ka, twal sǝm apǝlǝa lumi-tàrú bwamdǝ tongno-nong-tàrú (38). Aɓa mǝno anggo ka aburana mǝnana kat à nda ka amǝ'lwa a nza mǝno ka, à wukina puppup, kǝla mana Yahweh Ɓakuli kángìr ama nǝ̀ twaltea ka.
\v 15 Yàle bu Yahweh Ɓakuli nǝ nggearǝì, nda mana pǝlǝ arǝia nǝ̀ máliǎ, she ɓǝ̀ teà twalna ka.\f + \fr 2:15 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Kor 10:1-5; Yahu 5\xt*\ft .\f*
\pi1 
\v 16 Lang aburana, amǝ'lwa kat, teà twalna, sǝ à wukina aɓalǝ aɓwana ka,
\v 17 Yahweh banggam ama,
\v 18 <<Yalung ngga, wun nǝ̀ kàr nǝ nzong-nzali mala amǝ'Mowap a Ar.
\v 19 Sǝama lang wu gbàshìnà nzong-nzali mala amǝkà Amon ngga, wu kǝa na ama wun nǝ̀ lulbumia, ko wun nǝ̀ altacau arǝia, mǝnana nǝ̀ tsǝia ɓǝà lo munǝo arǝ wun ngga ɗàng. Mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana pà mǝ nǝ pà wun kǝ ban aɓa nzali mala amǝ'Amon ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga ɗàng. Ən panì amǝkà Lotu nzalinì, dumǝna malea na.>>
\p 
\v 20 (Mǝnia yì nzali ɗiɗyal ka, amǝ'Refa, mǝnana amǝ'Amon tunǝia ama amǝ'Zamzum ngga, à nda ka aɓwana mana à duk kam ngga.
\v 21 Yià gbal ka aɓwana amǝcandǝe na, à làkkì pas, sǝ à dāh'rikya kǝla amǝ'Anak. Sǝama Yahweh bwalì amǝ'Amon kàm, à wal-luia pas, sǝ à tsǝk acilia à nying nzalî. Nda sǝ amǝ'Amon ak nzali pǝlǝ malea, sǝ à duk kam ngga.
\v 22 Kǝgìr mǝmwashati na Yahweh pè ace amǝ'Edom, yì amǝkà Isǝwa, mana à ndanǝdo a Seyir ka. Yahweh bwalì amǝ'Edom kàm, à wal-lú amǝ'Hor pas, acilia ka à pǝria, à ak nzali arǝia, sǝ à duk kam bà yalung.
\v 23 Ma mala amǝ'Avit mana à duki arǝ amuna-là, tù aban nggea-là Gaza ka, amǝ'Kafto mǝnana à pur a Kafto ka, à nda à yi twaltea, sǝ à yi do a nzali malea ka.)
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ cau ama:
\p 
\v 24 Yahweh bangga sǝm ama:
\pi1 Wu lo, wu bwal-njar! Wu yàllî ɓangŋaban Arnon. Wu sǝni, ǝn pana wun Sihon, ɓwa'Amor, Murǝm Heshbon andǝ nzali male. Wu kyarǝì nǝ lwa, wu ak nzali male ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun.
\v 25 Twal a yalung ngga, mǝ nǝ tsǝk aɓwana a ɓanza kat, ɓǝà dum nǝ ɓangciu sǝ múrià ɓǝ̀ kàrria arǝ wun. Acemana à nǝ̀ okce wun, ǝn'ò nǝ̀ bwalia sǝ rǝia nǝ̀ ɓǝla nǝ ɓangciu ace wun.
\s1 À gandǝ Sihon murǝm Heshbon a lwa
\r (Ɓal 21:21-30)
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ ne amǝ Isǝrayila cau ama:
\p 
\v 26 Nda ǝn loasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân a pǝɗanban Kedemot, ɓǝà kya aban Murǝm Sihon, ɓwa Heshbon nǝ mǝnia yì cau do-rǝpwala ka, ama:
\pi1 
\v 27 Eara sǝm, ɓǝ̀ sǝm kútí nǝɓa nzali mô. Sǝm nǝ̀ kútí kporong amur njargula. Pà sǝm nǝ̀ kyanggî múr njargula ɗang.
\v 28 Wu makka sǝm girlina mana sǝm nǝ̀ li, andǝ mùr mana sǝm nǝ̀ nu ka; sǝm nǝ̀ kúria nǝ bolo-azǝrfa ma'sǝm. Kǝgìr mǝnana sǝm earkiyice ka, nda mǝnana ama wu eara sǝm ɓǝ̀ sǝm kùtí nǝɓa nzali mô nǝ kusǝ sǝm,
\v 29 kǝla mana amǝkà Isǝwa, mǝnana à do a Seyir, andǝ amǝ'Mowap mǝnana à do a Ar, à eara sǝm, sǝm kútí nǝɓa nzali malea ka. Sǝm nǝ̀ kutio she sǝm kat ka sǝm yàlǝ́nì Nggeasala Jodan, sǝm kutina a nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm kǝ pà sǝmi ka.
\p 
\v 30 Sǝ Murǝm Sihon, ɓwa Heshbon ngga ɓinǝe; ko eara sǝm ɓǝ̀ sǝm kútí nǝɓa nzali male ɗàng. Mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun tǝrna ɓabumi sǝ múrí candǝna ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ tasǝì a ɓabù wun, ɓǝ̀ wu gandǝi a munǝo, kǝla mǝno yalung pàk ka.
\p 
\v 31 Pǝlǝa Yahweh banggam ama:
\pi1 Sǝni, Ən tinatà pà Murǝm Sihon andǝ nzali male a bù wun. Wu tita kyan nǝ lwa arǝì wu lì nzali male, sǝ wu e ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun!
\p 
\v 32 Pǝlǝa Murǝm Sihon andǝ amǝ'lwa male puro ace yinǝ munǝo arǝ sǝm a Jahaz.
\v 33 Sǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm tasǝia a ɓabù sǝm, nda sǝm gandǝi andǝ amuna-burana male, sǝm kiɗiki andǝ aɓwana male kat.
\v 34 A bákuì mǝno ka, sǝm ak alá male, sǝm kiɗikia kat, sǝ sǝm twalta aɓwana kat, aburana andǝ amamǝna, andǝ amuna mǝkeke. Ko sǝm nying kǝɓwa nǝyilǝmu ɗang.
\v 35 Kǝ agirkusǝu na sǝm gbǝwia kǝla kume-lwa ace ɓamur rǝ sǝm, andǝ gǝna-lwa mana sǝm pwan arǝ alá mana sǝm ea ka.
\p 
\v 36 Tite amur nggea-là Aruwa, mana nda a kún Ɓangŋaban Arnon, andǝ là mǝnana aɓa ɓangŋaban aban ká nzong-nzali mala amǝ Gilǝyat ka, sǝm limurǝm amúrià nǝ lwa. Ɓekǝ nggea-là pà kàm mǝnana gandǝ sǝm a lwa ka ɗàng; Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm tasǝia a ɓabu sǝm.
\v 37 Kǝ nzali mala amǝ'Amon nda mana sǝm gbàshì banià raka, yì kún Nggeasala Jabok, andǝ anggea-là mala nzali múr ankono andǝ abân mǝnana kat Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm tsǝka sǝm nzongcau ama, ɓǝ̀ sǝm nyia, ɓǝ̀ sǝm kǝa jea raka.
\c 3
\s1 Isǝrayila lì Og Murǝm mala amǝ Bashan nǝ munǝo
\r (Ɓal 21:31-35)
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 1 Anzǝm mǝno ka, sǝm pǝlǝa sǝ sǝm eau a njargula ká nzali Bashan. Og, yì murǝm Bashan ngga, puro ace mǝnana nǝ̀ munǝ arǝ sǝm a Edǝri; yì sǝ aɓwana male mǝnana à pur munǝo ka, à soa sǝm.
\v 2 Pǝlǝa Yahweh banggam ama:
\pi1 Cè ɓangciu pàkkô arǝì ɗàng. Ən angŋa dǝmba ǝn pano wi a ɓabuo, yì andǝ aɓwana male kat andǝ nzali male. We ka, awu nǝ pàkki wi kǝla mǝnana a pakkì Sihon murǝm mala amǝ'Amor, mǝnana do a Heshbon ngga.
\p 
\v 3 Anggo sǝ yi pa, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm ngga yi pà Og murǝm Bashan gbal a ɓabù sǝm, yì andǝ aɓwana male kat. Sǝm wal-luia kat ko kǝɓwa ueo a banì ɗàng.
\v 4 A bàkú mǝno ka, sǝm lì ka anggea-là male kat; kǝ nggea-là pà kàm mana sǝm e arǝia raka; anggea-là lumi-tongno-nong-mwashat aɓa bu-nzali Argop, aɓa nzali-murǝm mala Og a Bashan.
\v 5 Anggea-là mǝno kat ka à kàriá nǝ asheran amǝ'dāh'rike, sǝ akúnla ka à peǎ nǝ anggun mǝcandǝe ace gìria; ɗǝm ngga à ndanǝ amuna-là mǝnana à kàriá nǝ asheran raka.
\v 6 Sǝm kiɗikia\f + \fr 3:6 \fq kiɗikia: \ft À tària kǝla pàgir aban Yahweh nǝ twaltea kàng.\f* puppup kǝla mana sǝm pàkkî Sihon murǝm Heshbon ngga; sǝm twalta aburana, andǝ mamǝna, andǝ amuna aɓa koya nggea-là.
\v 7 Sǝama agirkusǝu andǝ agirkuma mala anggea-là mǝno ka, sǝm pwania kǝla gǝna-lwa, à pǝlǝ ma'sǝm.
\p 
\v 8 A bàkú mǝno ka, sǝm ak anzali a bù amurǝma ɓari mala amǝ'Amor, mǝnana à nda a nkaring Nggeasala Jodan ngga, twal a Ɓangŋaban Arnon aban ká Nkono Hamon.
\v 9 (Amǝ'Sidon tunǝ nkono Hamon ama Siriyon, sǝ amǝ'Amor ka à tunǝi ama Senir.)
\v 10 Sǝm ak anggea-là kat aɓa nzali-murǝm mala Og a Bashan; anggea-là male mǝnana a ɓawan-mgbangban, andǝ bu-nzali Gilǝyat kat, andǝ bu-nzali Bashan kat, yi puro a Saleka andǝ Edǝri.
\v 11 (Og murǝm Bashan ngga, nda masǝlǝata ɓwa'Refa mǝnana ue nǝmurǝi atà acili amǝ'Refa ka. Gyangŋan-nongŋo male ka à pè nǝ bolo-candǝa. Nda kam più a Rabba, là mala amǝ'Amon. Sauwa mala mǝnia yì gyangŋan-nongŋo ka ɓakusǝ lum-nong-tàrú nǝ gauwa-tsùrú na, sǝ tangŋa male ka ɓakusǝu tongno-nong-mwashat na.)
\s1 Gaki nzali
\r (Ɓal 32:1-42)
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 12 Lang sǝm ak nzali mǝnia sǝ pǝlǝ ma'sǝm a bàkú mǝno ka, ǝn pê atau mala Ruben andǝ Gad bu-nzali mǝnana tite a là Aruwa, mǝnana nda a kún Ɓangŋaban Arnon ngga, andǝ gauwa-tsùrú mala Gilǝyat, nzali múr ankono andǝ alá mǝnana aɓalǝi ka.
\v 13 Cili nzali Gilǝyat, andǝ nzali Bashan kat, yì nzali-murǝm mala Og, mǝnana nda a bu-nzali Argop kat ka, ǝn pê gauwa-tsùrú mala tàu mala Manasa. (Bu-nzali mǝno kat aɓa Bashan ngga, à kǝ tunǝi ɗiɗyal ama nzali mala amǝ'Refa.
\v 14 Sǝ ɓè ɓwa mana à tunǝi ama Jayar, a tàu mala Manasa ka, lî mǝno yì bu-nzali Argop kat aɓa Bashan ngga nǝ lwa yi pur a nzong-nzali mala amǝ'Geshur andǝ amǝ'Ma'aka. Pǝlǝa yì Jayar ka, nggaɗi lullǝ Bashan, tunǝi nǝ lullǝì ama Havot Jayar.\f + \fr 3:14 \fq Havot Jayar \ft ka ɓalǝi nda <<Alá mala Jayar.>>\f* Yalung ngga anggo sǝ à kǝ tunǝ banì.)
\v 15 Nzali Gilǝyat ka ǝn pê amǝ'kà Makir.
\v 16 Bu-nzali mǝnana tite a Gilǝyat sǝ sarǝa aban ká Ɓangŋaban Arnon ngga, ǝn pê tàu mala Ruben andǝ tàu mala Gad. Tsùrú mala ɓangŋaban man ngga nda nzong-nzali malea mǝnana kutio kya go a kún Nggeasala Jabok, mǝnana nda nzong-nzali mala amǝ'Amon ngga.
\v 17 Ɗǝm ngga ǝn pea wia Araba sarǝa yi go a kún Nggeasala Jodan kǝla nzong-nzali, sǝ lo a kún Nggeamùr Chineret sarǝa aban yiu a kún nggeamùr mala Araba, mana à kǝ tunǝi gbal ama Nggeamùr Tuɓamur ka, a kusǝ abum Nkono Pisga a bù-njartakuli.
\p 
\v 18 A bàkú mǝno ka ǝn kwarkir wun ani nǝma:
\pi1 Kat andǝ amani ama Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pana wun mǝnia yì nzali ama ɓǝ̀ wu duk kam ngga, dumǝna púp wun mǝnana kat wu nda ka aburana, amǝ'lwa ma'wun ngga, wun nǝ̀ aki amǝ'eam wun amǝ Isǝrayila dǝmba, à nǝ̀ yàlî nkaring Nggeasala Jodan, aɓa kùrrǝu andǝ gilǝrǝu ace bwalia wia kàm.
\v 19 Sǝama amālá wun, andǝ amuna ma'wun, andǝ agirkusǝu ma'wun (mǝnana ǝn sǝlǝna ama à nda pas ka), à nǝ̀ gandǝ ue kani aɓalǝ anggea-là mǝnana ǝn pana wun ngga.
\v 20 Dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ lwa-lwa sheɓǝ̀ Yahweh pànî amǝ'eam wun amǝ Isǝrayila limurǝm, kǝla mǝnana pà wun ngga, ɓǝà ak nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pea wia a nkaring Nggeasala Jodan nǝ njar-nzali ka, ɓǝà duk kam. Anzǝm mǝno ka sǝ wun nǝ̀ nyare aɓa nzali ma'wun mǝnana ǝn pana wun ngga.
\p 
\v 21 A bákuì mǝno ka, ǝn banggi Jesǝwa nǝma, <<We nǝ nggearǝo ka a sǝnǝna agir mǝnana kat Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pàngnǝ Murǝm Sihon andǝ Murǝm Og ka. Anggo sǝ yì ka nǝ̀ pàngnǝ anzali-murǝm kat mǝno wun nǝ̀ yàlî nkaring Nggeasala Jodan nǝ njar-nzali, wun nǝ̀ ká kàm ngga.
\v 22 Cè ɓangciu pàkka wun arǝia ɗàng, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga, nǝ̀ munǝ ace wun.>>
\s1 Ɓakuli ɓinǝì Musa kutio a Nzali Kan'ana
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ banggi amǝ Isǝrayila cau ama:
\p 
\v 23 Akǝ bákuì mǝno ɗǝm ngga, Ən ɓuaki arǝ Yahweh nǝma,
\v 24 <<Yahweh Ɓakuli, ado ka a tinata lǝmdǝàm, mim guro mò, gulo mô andǝ rǝcandǝa mò; ya ɓakuli nani a kùli ko a nzali, mǝnana nǝ̀ gandǝ pakkî agir andǝ atúró mǝgulke kǝla mò ka?
\v 25 Ən nggǝ zǝmbô, earâm ɓǝ̀n yálì Nggeasala Jodan, ace mǝnana mǝ kya sǝn nzali mǝɓoarne mǝno a nkaring, yì nzali múr ankono mǝɓoarne andǝ Lebano ka.>>
\p 
\v 26 Sǝ Yahweh ka bumi lúllô arǝàm atàcau ma'wun sǝ eare nǝ̀ kwakikiri arǝàm ɗàng. A kún mani ka, banggam ama, <<Cau mǝna ka kārǝ́na! Kǝa nyare a banggam kǝ cau ɗǝm amur cau mǝna ka ɗàng.
\v 27 Sǝama eau a ɓong Nkono Pisga, sǝ wu sǝnban nǝ njar-nzali, andǝ njar-nza, andǝ njar-kunmur, andǝ njar-takuli. Pelǝban wu sǝn nzalinì nǝ mǝsǝo, acemǝnana we ka, a pà nǝ yàlî Nggeasala Jodan mǝnia ace ká a nzali mǝno ka ɗàng.
\v 28 Jesǝwa ka, nda ɓwa mǝnana nǝ̀ kánǝ amǝ Isǝrayila ɓǝà yàllî Nggeasala Jodan ɓǝà kya ak mǝno yì nzali awu nǝ sǝni ka. Acemani ka, ɓakɓabumi ɓǝ̀ dum nǝ rǝcandǝa andǝ mǝsǝkàng-kàngŋa, sǝ wu banggi wi gìr mǝnana nǝ̀ pàk ka.>>
\p 
\v 29 Anzǝm mǝno ka sǝm ue kanó aɓa ɓangŋaban mǝnana a nkāɓe Bet-Piyor\f + \fr 3:29 \fq Bet-Piyor \ft ɓè ban tù aban Nkono Pisga, mǝnana yakǝla a kàm sǝ Bil'am ɓariki nǝ̀ sú amǝ Isǝrayila ka (\xt Ɓal 23:28\xt*\ft ). Amǝ'Moap gbal ka à peri aban Ba'al abanì nǝ lullǝu mǝnana ama <<Ba'al [mala] Piyor>> ka (\xt Ɓal 25:1-5\xt*\ft .)\f* ka.
\c 4
\s1 Musa ɓakɓabum amǝ Isǝrayila ɓǝà okî Ɓakuli
\sp Musa bang ama:
\p 
\v 1 Wun amǝ Isǝrayila, wu kwakikir wun arǝ amǝnia yì anê andǝ akasǝcau mana mǝ ndo mǝ nǝ kània wun ngga. Wu kpatea ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu dum nǝyilǝmu, sǝ ɓǝ̀ wu kutio wu kya ak nzali mǝnana Yahweh, yì Ɓakuli mala aká wun, kǝ pà wun ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga.
\v 2 Wu kǝa tsǝk kǝgìr amur gìr mǝnana ǝn tsǝka wun nzongcau arǝì ka ɗàng, sǝ wu kǝa amsǝ kǝgìr aɓalǝi ɗàng. Wun ngga wu kpata anzongcau mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, amǝnia ǝn nggǝ bangga wun cau malea ka.
\p 
\v 3 Wun ngga, mǝsǝ wun, sǝnǝna gìr mǝnana Yahweh pè a Ba'al-Piyor,\f + \fr 4:3 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Ɓal 25:1-9\xt*\ft .\f* mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun twalta aɓwana kat aɓalǝ wun mǝnana à peri aban Ba'al, yì ɓakuli mala Piyor ka.
\v 4 Sǝama wun mǝnana kat wu dumnǝ mǝsǝcau aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga, wu ndakam più nǝyilǝmu ba yalung.
\v 5 Wu sǝni, ǝn kanina wun anê andǝ akasǝcau kǝla mana Yahweh tsǝkam nzongcau ama ɓǝ̀n pê, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu kpatea aɓa nzali mǝnana wun ndo wun nǝ̀ kútí kam ace e ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga.
\v 6 Wu tsǝkir wun wu kpatea acemǝnana pě ma'wun anggo ka nǝ̀ lǝmdǝ kwaro andǝ bwaltagir ma'wun aban aɓwapǝndǝa mǝnana à kàrì wun ngga. Yià ka à nǝ̀ ok cau mala amǝnia yì anê ka, sǝ à nǝ̀ bang ama:
\pi1 Mǝsǝcau mǝnia yì nzali mǝgule ka, nzali mala amǝ'kwaro andǝ amǝ'bwaltagir na.
\m 
\v 7 Yàle ya ɓè nzali mǝgule kàm mǝnana ndanǝ ɓekǝ ɓakuli abani tù kǝla Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm, mana nda aban sǝm tù koya pwari lang sǝm ɓua a baní ka?
\v 8 Sǝ ya ɓè nzali mǝgule kàm mǝnana ndanǝ anê andǝ akasǝcau amǝɓoarne ulang mala anggurcau mǝnia kat ǝn nggǝ nongsǝa wunia a ɓadǝm wun yalung ngga?
\s1 Kasǝɓalǝu arǝ kùrcau mana à kùrì a Horep ka
\r (Puro 20:18-21)
\p 
\v 9 Sǝama wu tsǝkir wun arǝ ɓamurǝ wun, sǝ wu yál ɓamurǝ wun pepè, ace mǝnana ɓalǝ wun ɓǝ̀ kǝa lórǝ́ agir mǝnana amǝsǝ wun sǝnǝnia, gandǝa wun nǝ̀ būrǝcea aɓa do-yilǝmu ma'wun kat ka ɗàng. Wu kǝ bang cau malea aban amuna ma'wun andǝ amǝ'kà wun.
\v 10 A pwari mǝno wu cam a ɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun a Horep ka, Yahweh banggam ama, <<Ramba aɓwe abanam, ace mǝnana ɓǝn tsǝia ɓǝà ok acau mem, ace mǝnana ɓǝà kàni ɓanggam aɓalǝ anonggio mala do-yilǝmu malea kat aɓa nzali man, sǝ ɗǝm ngga ɓǝà kànî amuna malea anggo.>>
\p 
\v 11 Sǝ wu sung tù wu yi came a kusǝ nkono, sǝ nkono kǝ earki nǝ bǝsa aban ká kùli. Pǝrɓang mǝpǝndǝe andǝ pǝndǝa mǝcikcikì yi zuppi amur nkono.
\v 12 Pǝlǝa Yahweh bangcau nǝ wun nǝ ɓá bǝsa. Wu ok gì acau, sǝama wu sǝn pǎ male ɗàng.
\v 13 Sǝ Yahweh hamba wun kùrcau male sǝ bangga wun ama ɓǝ̀ wu kpata Anzongcau Lum mǝnana lǝmdǝa wun ngga. Yahweh gilǝ amǝnia yì Anzongcau ka amur akpamgbǝlang tali ɓari.
\v 14 A bàkú mǝno ka Yahweh banggam ama mǝ kania wun anê andǝ akasǝcau mǝnana wun nǝ̀ kpatea aɓa nzali mana ado wun nǝ̀ yàllî Nggeasala Jodan wun nǝ̀ nggá e ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga.
\s1 À pǝrban arǝ peri atà ankul
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 15 A pwari mǝno Yahweh bangcau nǝ wun nǝ ɓá bǝsa a Horep ka, wu sǝn pǎ male ɗàng. Acemani ka, wu yál rǝ wun pepè,
\v 16 wu tsǝkir wun cè wu pàk cauɓikea mala shàrî ɓamurǝ wun ɓekǝ ɓǝ̀nzál mǝnana pùr ɓekǝ gìr, ko ɓwapǝndǝa ɓwabura ko ɓwama,
\v 17 ko koya ulang girkusǝu mǝnana kǝ gya a nzali, ko nyal mǝnana kǝ yal a kùli,
\v 18 ko ɓekǝ giryilǝmu mǝnana kǝ ging nǝ múrbumi a nzali, ko ɓekǝ nji mǝnana a tàmùr ka ɗàng.
\v 19 Lang wu loasǝ mǝsǝ wun a kùli sǝ wu sǝn pwari, andǝ zongŋo, andǝ anlero, andǝ acili agir mǝnana a kùli ka, cè ɓekǝ gìr swarki wun ama wun nǝ̀ ɓunno a nzali aɓa peri abania, ko wun nǝ̀ kpata acau malea ɗàng. Yahweh tsǝia akanó ace aɓwana kat a koya ban a ɓanza.
\v 20 Sǝ wun ngga, Yahweh twalna wun sǝ pusǝna wun wu purni ɓá nzali Masar, mǝno yì ndà-bǝsa mala panzǝ bolo-candǝa ka,\f + \fr 4:20 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Amur 8:51; Ir 11:4\xt*\ft .\f* ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu duk aɓwana mala liɓala male, kǝla mǝnana wu pàk yalung ngga.
\p 
\v 21 Bum Yahweh lúllô arǝàm atàcau ma'wun. Nda bangcau nǝ kángìr ama pà mǝ nǝ yàllî Nggeasala Jodan ɗàng, sǝ pà mǝ nǝ kúti aɓa nzali mǝɓoarne mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ɓǝ̀ duk girkuma ma'wun ngga ɗàng.
\v 22 Acemani ka, mǝ nǝ wù akaní aɓa nzali mǝnia; pà mǝ nǝ yàllî Nggeasala Jodan ɗàng; sǝ wun ngga, wun ndo wun nǝ̀ yàllî Nggeasala Jodan, wun nǝ̀ nggá ak nzali mǝɓoarne mǝno ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun.
\v 23 Wu tsǝkir wun cè ɓalǝ wun lórǝ́ kùrcau mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun mǝnana kùr nǝ wun ngga ɗàng. Sǝ wu kǝa shàrî ɓamur rǝ wun ɓekǝ ɓǝ̀nzál mala ɓè ɓakuli, mǝnana ndanǝ purban mala ɓekǝ gìr, koɓǝ̀ mǝye nani le ka ɗàng, acemǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pǝrna wun arǝ pak gìr kǝla mǝno.
\v 24 Mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga bǝsa mǝtwalta gìr na,\f + \fr 4:24 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Pur 24:17; Nggur 9:3; Isha 29:6; Ib 12:29\xt*\ft .\f* sǝ yì ka Ɓakuli mǝ'nɓali na.\f + \fr 4:24 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Pur 20:5; 34:14; Nggur 5:9; 6:15; Jes 24:19\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 25 Anzǝm mana wu ɓǝlkina amuna andǝ amǝ'kau, sǝ ban wun sauna nǝ do aɓa nzali Kan'ana ka, ɓǝ̀ wu kiɗiki ɓamur rǝ wun nǝ kutia pàk ɓekǝ ɓǝ̀nzál mala ɓè ɓakuli mana pùr koya ulang gìr nani le ka, sǝ wu pàk gìr mǝnana mǝɓike na aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, mǝnana nǝ̀ loasǝ bumlulla male ka,
\v 26 mǝ ndya ǝn nggǝ tunǝ kùli andǝ nzali ɓǝà duk amǝ'nakún arǝ wun yalung ama, mǝsǝcau wun nǝ̀ kìɗìkì akaurǝa, tà wun nǝ̀ twalî ɓá nzali mǝno wun ndo wun nǝ̀ yàlî Nggeasala Jodan wun nǝ̀ ká é ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga. Do ma'wun pà nǝ̀ sau a banì ɗàng, tà wun nǝ̀ twal kàng.
\v 27 Yahweh nǝ̀ mesǝki wun aɓalǝ anzali mala aɓwapǝndǝa, sǝ làkkì ma'wun nǝ̀ ueo kpokyak aɓalǝ anzali mǝnana Yahweh nǝ̀ pǝr wun, wun nǝ̀ u kam ngga.
\v 28 Akano ka wun nǝ̀ duk amǝ kpata aɓakuli mǝnana aɓwana pea nǝ abuia, nǝ nggun andǝ tali ka, ankúl mǝnana à kǝ sǝnban ɗang, à kǝ okban ɗang, à kǝ lili ɗang, sǝ à kǝ ok rǝmban raka.
\v 29 Sǝama ɓǝ̀ wu alta Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun a ban mǝno ka, wun nǝ̀ kumi, ɓǝ̀ wu alte nǝ ɓabum wun kat sǝ nǝ yilǝmi wun kat ka.\f + \fr 4:29 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa: \xt Ir 29:13\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 30 Lang wu kutina aɓata parban mala tanni a masǝlǝata apwari,\f + \fr 4:30 \fq a masǝlǝata apwari \ft ko <<nǝnzǝ́mò>>\f* sǝ amǝnia yì agir kat à yina múr wun ngga, wun nǝ̀ nyare aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun sǝ wun nǝ̀ kwakikir wun arǝ gi.
\v 31 Mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga Ɓakuli mǝ'sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr na.\f + \fr 4:31 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Pur 34:6\xt*\ft .\f* Pà nǝ̀ vwakibuì arǝ wun ɗàng, sǝ pà nǝ̀ kiɗiki wun, ko ɓālǝi nǝ̀ lórǝ́ kùrcau mǝnana pè nǝ kángìr aban aká wun ngga ɗàng.
\p 
\v 32 Wu ɗiban amur anza mana ɓara-ɓara, tite a pwari mǝnana Ɓakuli pusǝ ɓwapǝndǝa a ɓanza ka, sǝ wu ɗiban tite a ɓè nzong kuli aban ká ɓè nzong kuli: Ɓekǝ gìr kàm gulo bwalta mǝnia kumban ngga le, ko kǝɓwa ongŋǝna cè ɓekǝ gìr kǝla manì le?
\v 33 Kǝ ɓè nzali mala aɓwapǝndǝa ok gì Ɓakuli a kǝ fara aban banggia wia cau nǝ ɓá bǝsa, kǝla mǝnana wun ngga wu o, sǝ wu ndakam più nǝyilǝmu ka le?
\v 34 Ko ɓǝ̀ mǝno na raka, ɓekǝ ɓakuli mwami a kǝ fara ama nǝ̀ ká sǝ nǝ̀ ak aɓwapǝndǝa mala ɓè nzali nǝ̀ pusǝia ɓǝà purî ɓá ɓè nzali, nǝ̀ nyesǝia ɓǝà duk amale, kǝla mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pakka wun a Masar ka le? Nǝ nggearǝ mǝsǝ wun sǝ wu sǝni pàktúró nǝ kaɓa rǝcandǝa male andǝ mazo mala nggwarbui; sulǝ ɓashi male andǝ lwa, sǝ pàkki agir-lǝmdǝa, agir-gyambǝliban andǝ agir kàrmúrû mǝgulke.
\v 35 À lǝmdǝa wun amǝnia yì agir ka ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu sǝlǝa ama Yahweh ka nda Ɓakuli. Kǝ ɓè pà kàm ɗàng she kǝ yi.
\v 36 Eara wun ɓǝ̀ wu ok gì nǝ kuli ace mǝnana nǝ̀ kwarkir wun ngga; sǝ akani a nzali ka eara wun wu sǝn bǝsa male mǝgule, sǝ wu ok acau male nǝ ɓá bǝsa mǝno.
\v 37 Ace earcearǝu mǝnana ndanǝi arǝ aká wun ngga, tàr wun, wun amǝ'keà mǝnana à ɓǝl wun anzǝmia ka. Yì nǝ nggearǝì ka pàktúró nǝ rǝcandǝa male mǝgule sǝ pusǝ wun ɓǝ̀ wu purî ɓá nzali Masar.
\v 38 Aɓa ká ma'wun ngga, loasǝtà aɓwapǝndǝa aɓalǝ anzali mǝnana à kútì wun nǝ gulo andǝ rǝcandǝa ka, ace mǝnana nǝ̀ yinǝ wun ɓǝ̀ wu yi kúti aɓa nzali malea sǝ nǝ̀ pà wuni ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun, kǝla mǝno yalung nzalinì dumǝna ma'wun ngga.
\v 39 Acemani ka, wu sǝlǝ yalung, sǝ wu tsǝì a ɓabum wun ama Yahweh ka, nda Ɓakuli a kùli sǝ a nzali. Ɓè kǝ ɓakuli pa kàm ɗàng.
\v 40 Wu kpata anggurcau andǝ anzongcau male, mǝnana ǝn nggǝ pà wun yalung ngga, ace mǝnana wun wunǝ amuna ma'wun andǝ amǝ'kà wun ngga, agir ɓǝà upa wun a kǝkarì aɓa lidǝmba. Sǝ ɗǝm ngga ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu lidǝmba nǝ do a nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun, málá male pà kàm raka.
\s1 Anggea-là mala kum-àwá
\p 
\v 41 Pǝlǝa Musa tàr anggea-là tàrú, ɗàng a njartakuli mala Nggeasala Jodan,
\v 42 ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ ɓwa wal-lú ɓi mǝmurkala sǝ pà kpakpak ɗàng, sǝ ɓekǝ ɓinǝmǝsǝu pa kàm a nrea ɗiɗyal raka, ɓwe nǝ̀ gandǝ ɓangŋa nǝ̀ kùtí aɓa mwashat atà amǝnia yì anggea-là ka, sǝ nǝ̀ amsǝ yilǝmi.
\v 43 Anggea-lê ka à nda ka Beza, a ɓawan-mgbangban a ɓabondo, ace aɓwana a tàu mala Ruben; Ramot a nzali Gilǝyat ace aɓwana a tàu mala Gad; sǝ Golan aɓa nzali Bashan ace aɓwana a tàu mala Manasa.
\s1 Isǝrayila a Bet-Piyor
\p 
\v 44 Mǝnia ka nda nggurcau mǝnana Musa pè amǝ Isǝrayila ka.
\v 45 Musa hambî amǝ Isǝrayila amǝnia yì anzongcau, andǝ anê andǝ akwarkiru, lang à purni ɓá nzali Masar,
\v 46 sǝ à yina a nkaring a ɓangŋaban mala Nggeasala Jodan, ban mǝnana à kǝ sǝn ɓamǝsǝarǝia andǝ Bet-Piyor ka. Nzali mǝnia ɗiɗyal ka mala Sihon murǝm mala amǝ'Amor mǝnana do a Heshbon ngga nda. Sǝama Musa andǝ amǝ Isǝrayila gandǝi a lwa lang à purî nzali Masar ka.
\v 47 À ak nzali mǝnia ka arǝì andǝ nzali mala Og, murǝm mala Bashan. Amǝnia yì amurǝma ɓari mala amǝ'Amor ka, à yálmúr aɓwana a nzali mana a nkaring Nggeasala Jodan a takuli ka.
\v 48 Amǝ Isǝrayila ak nzali arǝia, tite a Aruwa mǝnana nda a nkanggari ɓangŋaban Arnon ngga aban ká a Nkono Siriyon (mana à tunǝi gbal ama Hamon ngga),
\v 49 andǝ Araba kat, mǝnana nong a bù takuli mala Nggeasala Jodan aban ká a kún Nggeamùr mala yì Araba, a kusǝ abum Nkono Pisga ka.
\c 5
\s1 Anzongcau Lum
\r (Puro 20:1-17)
\p 
\v 1 Pǝlǝa Musa tunǝ amǝ Isǝrayila kat, sǝ nea wia ama: Wun amǝ Isǝrayila, wu ok anzongcau andǝ angguracau mana ǝn nggǝ hamnǝia yalung aban wun ngga. Wu kània sǝ wu tsǝkir wun arǝ kpatea.
\v 2 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm kùrcau nǝ sǝm a Horep, yì Nkono Saina.
\v 3 Mǝnia yì kùrcau ka Yahweh kùrì nǝ aká-sǝm ɗàng. Sǝm nda mǝnana kùrcau nǝ sǝm, sǝm mǝnana sǝm nda kani ado sǝm ndanǝ yilǝmu yalung ngga.
\v 4 Yahweh nacau nǝ wun nǝ ɓamúrì aɓa bǝsa amur nkono.
\v 5 A pwari mǝno ka, mǝ nda ban came a nre wun wunǝa Yahweh ɓǝ̀n bangga wun cau male yi Yahweh, acemǝnana ɓangciu pàkka wun arǝ bǝsa, sǝ wu eau a nkono ɗang. Sǝ bang ama:
\li1 
\v 6 Mǝ nda Yahweh Ɓakuli mô, mana pusǝo a nzali Masar, a purì ɓala doguro ka.\f + \fr 5:6 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 20:2-17; Nggur 8:14\xt*\ft .\f*
\li1 
\v 7 A pà wunǝ pàngnǝ kǝ ɓè ɓakuli ɗang she mim.
\li1 
\v 8 A pà wunǝ pàkkî ɓamúrò ɓekǝ ɓǝ̀nzál mana pur koya gìr mǝnana nda a kùli kano ɓong-ɓong, ko mǝnana nda a ɓanza kani a nzali, ko mǝnana nda a mùr a tà-nzali ka ɗàng.
\v 9 A pà wunǝ ɓun a nzali abania, ko awu nǝ eare ɓǝà swárǒ wu kpata acau malea ɗàng; mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana Mim, Yahweh Ɓakuli mô ka, mǝ nda Ɓakuli mǝ'mɓali. Ən nggǝ ɗice cauɓikea mala atárrú amur amunia, andǝ amǝ'keà aban ká tàruià andǝ inea nza mala aɓwana mǝnana à ɓinǝmǝsǝàm ngga.\f + \fr 5:9 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 34:7; Ɓal 14:18; Nggur 7:10\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 10 Sǝama ǝn nggǝ lǝmdǝ earcearǝu mǝnana kǝ gǝshi raka aban ká arǝ anza á-pas mala aɓwana mǝnana à earcem sǝ à kǝ kpata anzongcau mem ngga.
\li1 
\v 11 A pà wunǝ paktúró nǝ lullǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli mô aɓa pàkkiagir ɓana ɗang, acemǝnana Yahweh pà nǝ̀ nying ɓwa mǝnana paktúró nǝ lullǝì aɓa pàkkiagir ɓana ka ɓǝ̀ o anggo atàrǝì ɗàng.\f + \fr 5:11 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 3:13; 6:3; 33:19\xt*\ft .\f*
\li1 
\v 12 Tsǝkiro wu ɗenyinǝ pwari Sabbat, wu tárì ace Yahweh, kǝla mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli mô tsǝko ka.
\v 13 Aɓalǝ anongŋo tongno-nong-mwashat ka awu nǝ pak atúró mô,
\v 14 sǝ tongno-nong-ɓaria nongŋo ka pwari mem na Mim Yahweh Ɓakuli mô. Aɓalǝi ka a pà wunǝ pàk kǝ túró ɗang, we sǝ amunio, andǝ aguro-ɓala mò, andǝ andá mò, andǝ amǝdambǝriso mò, ko komǝye atà agir-lǝsǝa mò, ko bǝri mô mǝnana do atò a lá mò ka. Mǝnia ka nda ace mǝnana aguro ma'wun ɓǝà usǝlǝo kǝla wun ngga.
\v 15 Ɗenyi ama ɗiɗyal ka a nda guro a nzali Masar, sǝ Mim Yahweh Ɓakuli mô ka, ǝn amsǝo nǝ kaɓa rǝcandǝa andǝ mazo mala nggwarbu. Nda gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ Ən banggo nǝma wu tsǝkiro arǝ pwari Sabbat ka.
\li1 
\v 16 Pè tárró andǝ nggo gulo, kǝla mana Mim Yahweh Ɓakuli mô Ən tsǝka wun ngga, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ yilǝmo ɓǝ̀ sauwa a ɓanza sǝ ɓǝ̀ banɓoaro a nzali mana Mim Yahweh Ɓakuli mô ǝn nggǝ po ka.\f + \fr 5:16 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Mat 15:4; Mar 7:10; Afi 6:2-3\xt*\ft .\f*
\li1 
\v 17 A pà wunǝ wal-lú ɗàng.\f + \fr 5:17 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Mat 5:21; Jem 2:11\xt*\ft .\f*
\li1 
\v 18 A pà wunǝ nongnǝ ɓwa mǝnana wu pa alban wunǝi raka ɗàng.\f + \fr 5:18 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 20:14; Mat 5:27\xt*\ft .\f*
\li1 
\v 19 A pà wunǝ iun'í ɗang.
\li1 
\v 20 A pà wunǝ nakún nyir arǝ ɓio mǝmurkala ɗang.\f + \fr 5:20 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pas 25:18\xt*\ft .\f*
\li1 
\v 21 A pà wunǝ sham mālá ɓio mǝmurkala ɗang, sǝ a pà wunǝ earce ak ɓala mala ɓio mǝmurkala, ko nzali male, ko guro male, ko ndǎ male, ko mǝdambǝriso male, andǝ koya gìr mǝnana mala ɓio mǝmurkala na ka arǝì ɗàng.\f + \fr 5:21 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Mat 19:18-19; Mar 10:19; Luk 18:20; Rom 13:9\xt*\ft .\f*
\s1 Pà eare mala aɓwe
\sp Musa ne amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 22 Yahweh bangga wun amǝnia yì anzongcau ka a ban ramba ma'wun kat a banɓwáná. Na wun cau nǝ giu mǝcandǝe aɓa bǝsa andǝ ɓá pǝrɓang andǝ ɓá pǝndǝa mǝcikciki amúr nkono; bang amǝnia yì anzongcau ka sǝ tsǝk kǝ ɓe amurí ɗang. Osso gilǝia amur akpamgbǝlang tali ɓari sǝ pamia.
\v 23 Lang wu ok giu pur nǝ ɓá pǝndǝa, sǝ bǝsa na arǝ earke amur nkono ka, wun amúr-là andǝ aɓwana-mǝgule ma'wun kat wu yiu abanam.
\v 24 Wu bang ama:
\pi1 Sǝni, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm lǝmdǝna sǝm ɓoarɓwa andǝ gulo male, sǝ sǝm ongŋǝna gì pur nǝ ɓá bǝsa. Yalung ngga sǝm sǝnǝni ama Ɓakuli kǝ nacau nǝ aɓwapǝndǝa sǝ à nǝ̀ dum nǝyilǝmu.
\v 25 Sǝ ado ka, ace mana sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ wǔ le? Mǝnia yì nggea bǝsa ka nǝ̀ lì sǝm, sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ wukio ɓǝ̀ sǝm lidǝmba nǝ ok gì Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm ngga.
\v 26 Yana ɓwe kàm aɓalǝ aɓwapǝndǝa mǝnana kat ok gì Ɓakuli mǝ'yilǝmui aban nacau nǝ ɓá bǝsa, kǝla mǝnana sǝm oè, sǝ ɓwe au ka?
\v 27 Musa, kyane gbashì ban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm, sǝ kwakikiro arǝ cau mǝnana kat nǝ̀ bang ngga. Sǝ wu yiu wu, wu bangga sǝm; sǝm nǝ̀ kwakikir sǝm sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ kpate.
\p 
\v 28 Lang Yahweh ok cau mǝno wu banggam ngga, banggam ama:
\pi1 Ən ongŋǝna cau mana aɓwana mǝnia nô ka. Cau mǝnana kat à na ka nda pepè.
\v 29 Ɓǝ̀ duk wuni ama à ndanǝ ulang ɓabum kǝla mǝnia ka aɓalǝia, mǝnana à nǝ̀ ɓanggam sǝ à nǝ̀ kpata anzongcau mem kat koya pwari, ace mǝnana yià andǝ amuna malea ka ɓǝà kum banɓoarnado mala do-yilǝmu mana málá male pà kàm raka.
\v 30 Kyane sǝ wu nea wia ama, <<Koyan ngga ɓǝ̀ nyare aɓa ndà-gumli male.>>
\v 31 Sǝ we Musa ka cam kani atàm, mǝ nǝ po anzongcau puppup, andǝ angguracau, andǝ akwarkiru mǝnana awu nǝ kània wia, ace mǝnana ɓǝà kpatea aɓa nzali mǝnana Mǝ nda ban pea wia ɓǝ̀ duk malea ka.
\sp Musa bang ama:
\p 
\v 32 Acemani ka, wu tsǝkir wun wu pàk gìr kǝla mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun bangga wun ngga. Cè wu kyanggi wi atà bù wun mǝlì ko mǝ'nggare ɗàng.
\v 33 Wu kpata acau mǝnana kat Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun bangga wun ngga, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu dum nǝyilǝmu, sǝ ace mǝnana agir ɓǝà gingga wun a kǝkarì, sǝ ɓǝ̀ yilǝmi wun sauwa aɓa nzali mǝnana wun nǝ̀ ká ê ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga.
\c 6
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 1 Ado ka amǝnia ka à nda ka anzongcau andǝ anê andǝ angguracau mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun banggam ama ɓǝ̀n kania wun, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu kpatea aɓa nzali mana wun nda rǝ ká kútí kam, wun nǝ̀ é ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga,
\v 2 ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu ɓanggi Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, wu kpata angguracau andǝ anzongcau male mǝnana ǝn nggǝ pa wun, wunǝ amuna wun andǝ amǝkà wun kat aɓalǝ anonggio mala do yilǝmu ma'wun kat ka, sǝ ɓǝ̀ yilǝmi wun ɓǝ̀ sauwa.
\v 3 Wu kwakikir wun, wun amǝ Isǝrayila, sǝ wu tsǝkir wun wu kpatea. Mǝnia ka nǝ̀ tsǝk agir à nǝ̀ camba wun a kǝkarì, sǝ wun nǝ̀ būndǝ kǝ̀rkǝ́r a nzali mǝnana kiura andǝ mur'nyi kǝ ɓang kàm, kǝla mana Yahweh Ɓakuli mala aká wun pà wun cau ace ka.
\p 
\v 4 Wu ǒ, wun amǝ Isǝrayila: Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm ngga, Yahweh na mwashat.
\v 5 Wu earce Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ ɓabum wun kat, andǝ yilǝmi wun kat, andǝ koman ma'wun kat.
\v 6 Amǝnia yì anzongcau mana ǝn nggǝ hamba wun nǝia yalung ngga, dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ tsǝia a ɓabum wun.
\v 7 Wu kànî amuna ma'wun nǝ tsǝkiru. Wun nǝ̀ nggǝ bangcau amúrià lang wu dumnǝdo a ɓala, sǝ aban gya amur njar, sǝ a ban nongŋo ma'wun, sǝ lang wu loapi ntulo ka.
\v 8 Wu kùria a myalbu wun kǝla gìr'lǝmdǝa, sǝ a kúndǝm wun a nre ka amǝsǝ wun.
\v 9 Wu gilǝia amur anggun-kúnakurǝm mala aɓala ma'wun sǝ arǝ akunɓala ma'wun.
\s1 Nunkiru amur ɗwanyi okiru
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ ne amǝ Isǝrayila cau ama:
\p 
\v 10 Lang Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun warinanǝ wun a nzali mǝnana kánbì aká wun, aban Ibǝrayim, aban Ishaku, sǝ aban Yakupu ama nǝ̀ pa wun; yì nzali mǝnana ndanǝ alá mǝgulke, amǝɓoarkijamì mǝnana wun nda mǝnana wu ɓeǎ raka,
\v 11 andǝ aɓala mana à lumsǝ nǝ koya gìr mǝɓoarne mǝnana wun nda wu tsǝia raka, andǝ atūli-mùr mǝnana wun nda wu tǝmia ka ɗàng, andǝ aɓaban-anap andǝ anggun olif mana wun nda wu pandǝia raka, sǝ lang wu li sǝ wu ɗǝmǝna ka,
\v 12 wu tsǝkir wun cè wu lórǝ́ Yahweh mana pusǝ wun a nzali Masar, nzali guro ka ɗàng.
\v 13 Wu ɓanggi Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun; kǝ yi na nǝmurǝì wun nǝ̀ kpate ka, sǝ nǝ lullǝì sǝ wun nǝ̀ kángìr.
\v 14 Wu kǝa kpata aɓea aɓakuli, yì aɓakuli mala aɓwana mana à gumbǝli wun ngga ɗàng.
\v 15 Mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli mana aɓalǝ wun ngga Ɓakuli mǝ'mɓali na;\f + \fr 6:15 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pur 20:5\xt*\ft .\f* ɓǝ̀ ana raka bumlulla mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ earke amur wun, sǝ nǝ̀ twalta wun ɗǝɗak aɓa ɓanza.
\v 16 Wu kǝa kārǝki Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, kǝla mana wu kārǝki a Massa ka ɗàng.\f + \fr 6:16 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Pur 17:1-7; Nggur 9:22; 33:8; Ang 95:8-9\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 17 Wun nǝ̀ bwal anzongcau mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ tsǝkiru, andǝ anê andǝ angguracau mǝnana tsǝka wun ngga.
\v 18 Dumǝna púp ama wun nǝ̀ pàk gìr mǝnana nda jik sǝ mǝɓoarne na a mǝsǝ Yahweh ka, ace mǝnana agir ɓǝà kyanba wun pepè, sǝ ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu kyane wu kya ak nzali mǝɓoarne ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun, yì nzali mana Yahweh kánbi aká wun ama nǝ̀ pea wia,
\v 19 ama nǝ̀ pǝ̀r aɓiwun amǝbura kat a ɓadǝm wun, kǝla mana yì Yahweh bang ngga.
\p 
\v 20 Ɓǝ̀ a dǝmba sǝ amuna ma'wun nǝ̀ ɗì wun ama, <<Mana nda ɓalǝ anê, andǝ angguracau andǝ anzongcau mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm tsǝka wunia ka?>>
\v 21 Pǝlǝa wun nǝ̀ nea wia ama:
\pi1 Ɗiɗyal ka sǝm nda ka aguro mala Firona a nzali Masar, sǝ Yahweh pusǝ sǝm, sǝm purî ɓá nzali Masar nǝ rǝcandǝa mǝgule.
\v 22 A mǝsǝ sǝm ngguont sǝ Yahweh tasǝ agir-lǝmdǝa amǝpa'ndali, andǝ agir-gyambǝliban mǝgulke andǝ amǝɓike amur amǝ Masar, sǝ amur Firona murǝm malea andǝ amǝɓala male puppup.
\v 23 Sǝ sǝm ngga pusǝ sǝm kano ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ yinǝ sǝm aɓa nzali mǝnia mǝnana kángìr ama nǝ̀ pè aká sǝm ngga, ace pà sǝmi.
\v 24 Yahweh tsǝk sǝm ama ɓǝ̀ sǝm kpata angguracau mǝnia ka, sǝ ɓǝ̀ sǝm ɓanggi Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm, a koya pwari, ace yal do ma'sǝm nǝyilǝmu, kǝla mana sǝm ndanǝi yalung ngga.
\v 25 Ɓǝ̀ sǝm tsǝkir sǝm arǝ kpata anzongcau mǝnia kat aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm, kǝla mana tsǝka sǝmi ka, nǝ̀ dupa sǝm cauɓoarna.
\c 7
\s1 Aɓwana mala Ɓakuli
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila cau ama:
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ kánǝ wun aɓa nzali mǝno wun ndo wun nǝ̀ ká é ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga. Yahweh nǝ̀ pǝr aɓwapǝndǝa mala anzali pas ɓǝà nyingga wun ban; nǝ̀ pǝr amǝ'Hitti, andǝ amǝ'Girgash, andǝ amǝ'Amor, andǝ amǝ'Kan'ana, andǝ amǝ'Periz, andǝ amǝ'Hivi, andǝ amǝ'Jebus; anzali tongno-nong-ɓari mǝnana à làkkì à kútì wun, sǝ à kútì wun nǝ rǝcandǝa ka.
\v 2 Sǝ lang Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pànà aɓwana man a ɓabù wun, sǝ wu linamurǝm amúrià ka, wu tària aban Yahweh ace twaltea kat-kat.\f + \fr 7:2 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa: \xt Nggur 20:17; Pur 22:20; Pǝris 27:29; Ɓal 21:2-3\xt*\f* Wu kǝa kùrcau wunǝia, ko wun nǝ̀ lǝmdǝia wia mǝsǝswatǝr ɗàng.
\v 3 Wu kǝa kútí a alban wunǝia ɗàng. Wu kǝa pà amuna-mamǝna ma'wun ɓǝà al amuna-burana malea ɗàng, sǝ wu kǝa eare ɓǝ̀ amuna-burana ma'wun al atà amuna-mamǝna malea ɗàng,
\v 4 acemǝnana à nǝ̀ pwan ɓabum amuna ma'wun arǝ kpata Yahweh ace peri aban aɓea aɓakuli. Sǝ ɓǝ̀ pa anggo ka, bumlulla mala Yahweh nǝ̀ earke amur wun, nǝ̀ kiɗiki wun akaurǝa.
\v 5 Acemani ka, mǝnia nda gìr mǝnana wun nǝ̀ pang nǝia ka: Wu bǝbbǝriki agyangŋan malea, wu arki akúnamúrú malea, wu tsauwiki atondong mala Ashera,\f + \fr 7:5 \fq atondong mala Ashera: \ft anggun mǝsake mǝnana à shària ace pángŋǝ̀nà-túró nǝia lang à nǝ̀ peri aban Ashera, yì mā-ɓakuli malea ka.\f* sǝ wu pisǝ aɓǝ̀nzál malea a bǝsa.
\v 6 Wu pàk mǝnia yì gìr ka acemǝnana wu nda ka aɓwana amǝfele aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun. Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga tàr wun aɓalǝ aɓwapǝndǝa mǝnana kat a ɓanza ka ɓǝ̀ wu duk girkuma male mǝnana earkiyi acea raka.
\s1 Tǝr tàrban mala amǝ Isǝrayila
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ nacau ama:
\p 
\v 7 Earban mana Yahweh earmúr wun sǝ tàr wun ngga, pà acemǝnana wu làkkì wu kútì acili aɓwapǝndǝa ka ɗàng; yàle wun nda kǝ nzali mǝnana làkkì ma'wun gatti acili anzali kat ka.
\v 8 Sǝama Yahweh ka tàr wun acemǝnana earce wun; sǝ ace domǝsǝcau male arǝ pacau mǝnana pà aban aká wun nǝ kángìr ka, pusǝ wun nǝ rǝcandǝa mǝgule, akmúr wun a ɓala guro, a ɓabù rǝcandǝa mala Firona murǝm Masar.
\v 9 Acemani ka, wu sǝlǝa ama Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga nda Ɓakuli. Yì ka nda Ɓakuli mǝ'domǝsǝcaunì mǝnana kǝ kpata kùrcau male, sǝ kǝ lǝmdǝ earcearǝu male mǝnana kǝ gǝshi raka aban aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ earce, sǝ à kǝ bwal anzongcau male ka, aban ká arǝ anza malea á-pas.
\v 10 Sǝama aɓwana mǝnana à ɓinǝmǝsǝì ka, nǝ̀ mbwea akǝ mǝsǝia nǝ́ twaltea; amǝ ɓinǝmǝsǝì ka, pà nǝ̀ dǝndi arǝ mbwea akǝ mǝsǝia nǝ gìr mǝnana karǝ arǝia ka ɗàng.
\v 11 Acemani ka, wu tsǝkir wun arǝ kpata anzongcau, andǝ anê, andǝ angguracau mǝnana ǝn nggǝ pa wun yalung ngga.
\s1 Tsǝkbu mǝnana kǝ gyata okiru ka
\r (Ɓǝs Nggur 28:1-14; Ace Apǝris 26:3-13)
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ cau aban amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 12 Ɓǝ̀ wu kwakikir wun arǝ amǝnia yì anggurcau sǝ wu kpatea nǝ mǝsǝcau ka, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ bwal kùrcau mala earcearǝu male mǝnana kǝ gǝshi raka aban wun, kǝla mǝnana kánbì aká wun ngga.
\v 13 Yì ka nǝ̀ earce wun, nǝ̀ tsǝka wun bù, sǝ nǝ̀ hatǝki wun. Ɗǝm ngga nǝ̀ tsǝka wun bù mala ɓǝl amuna pas, sǝ mala kum girlina kpǝm a nzali ma'wun; wun nǝ̀ kum mǝsǝsa, andǝ mùr-anap, andǝ mùrú olif arǝ aɓaban ma'wun; amuna-ndá andǝ amuna-mbùl arǝ adomwan ma'wun nǝ̀ lakkì aɓa nzali mǝnana kánbì aká wun nǝ̀ pà wun ngga.
\v 14 Kǝ nzali mala aɓwapǝndǝa pa kàm a ɓanza nǝ̀ kum ulang tsǝkbu ma'wun ɗàng. Kǝ ɓwa pa atà wun, ko ɓwabura ko ɓwama, ko kǝ girkusǝu ma'wun nǝ̀ duk nkombi ɗang.
\v 15 Yahweh nǝ̀ yál wun arǝ akwánó kat, sǝ pà nǝ̀ nying kǝ kwánó-ɓikea mala Masar, mǝnana wu súrǝ̀ia ka ɓǝ̀ yiu amúr wun ɗàng; a kún mani ka, nǝ̀ sulǝia amúr aɓwana mǝnana kat à kǝ ɓinǝmǝsǝ wun ngga.
\s1 Wu kiɗiki anzali andǝ aɓakuli malea
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 16 Wu twalta aɓwapǝndǝa mala anzali mǝnana kat Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pàna wunia a ɓabù wun ngga. Wu kǝa sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr malea ɗàng. Wu kǝa kpata acau mala aɓakuli malea ɗàng, acemǝnana mǝno ka nǝ̀ dupa wun gbǝ́lî.
\p 
\v 17 Wu kǝa ne a ɓabum wun ama, <<Aɓwapǝndǝa man kútì sǝm, lang sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ gandǝ pǝria, sǝm nǝ̀ ak nzali arǝia?>>
\v 18 Wu kǝa ɓanggia wia ɗàng. Wu ɗenyinǝ gir mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pakkî Firona andǝ aɓwana mala nzali Masar kat ka.
\v 19 Mǝsǝ wun sǝnǝna anggea gìr'mur'mwana, yì agir-lǝmdǝa, andǝ agir-ndǝlǝki, mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun peǎ nǝ rǝcandǝa male andǝ mazo mala nggwarbui sǝ pusǝ wun a nzali Masar ka. Anggo sǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ pàkkî aɓwapǝndǝa mǝnana kat wu kǝ ɓanggia wia ka.
\v 20 Ɗǝm ngga, acilia mǝnana à ueo sǝ à ɓangŋa à sǝmbǝrǝki ka, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tasǝia wia amǝ'ta-nta aɓalǝia ɓǝà tàkia, ɓǝà twaltea kat.
\v 21 Acemani ka, múr wun ɓǝkǝa kàr wún arǝ aɓwana mǝnia ka ɗàng, acemǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, yì Ɓakuli mǝgule, mǝpandali ka, nda atà wun.
\v 22 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ nggǝ pǝr aɓwapǝndǝa mala anzali mǝnia ka bǝti-bǝti. Pà nǝ̀ eara wun ɓǝ̀ wu twaltea atārǝia kat ɗàng; ɓǝ̀ eara wun ngga, anyam-bondo nǝ̀ ɓiki lákkià wun.
\v 23 Yahweh nǝ̀ tasǝ aɓiwun amǝbura a ɓabù wun; nǝ̀ túriá aɓa zùrǝki mǝgule, she ɓǝà kiɗikina ka.
\v 24 Nǝ̀ tasǝ amurǝma malea a ɓabù wun. Lullǝia pà nǝ̀ nyare nǝ̀ pà a ɗenyicau mala aɓwana a ɓanza ɗǝm ɗàng. Kǝ ɓwa pà kàm nǝ̀ gandǝ came a kún wun ɗàng; wun nǝ̀ kiɗikia kat.
\v 25 Wu pisǝ aɓǝ̀nzál mala aɓakuli malea mana à shària ka, a bǝsa. Wu kǝa sham bolo-azǝrfa ko bolo-njengǝlan mǝnana à gìrna rǝ aɓǝ̀nzál mala aɓakuli malea nǝi ka ɗàng, sǝ kǝɓwa atà wun ɓǝ̀ kǝa earce ama nǝ̀ twali ɓǝ̀ pǝlǝ male ɗàng. Ɓǝ̀ wu pàk ka, nǝ̀ nggá pǝlǝà wun gbǝ́lî, acemǝnana bwal gìr mala aɓea aɓakuli ka, gìr na mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ɓinǝce ka.
\v 26 Wu kǝa yinǝ ɓekǝ gìr'ɓeami arǝ aɓala ma'wun ɗàng, ɓǝ̀ ana raka wun nǝ̀ duk gìr mǝnana à tàrni ace kiɗike ka, kǝla gìrnî. Wu ɓinǝkia sǝ wu ginǝkicea, acemǝnana agir na mǝnana à tàrnia ace kiɗikia ka.
\c 8
\s1 Wu ɗenyinǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila cau ama:
\p 
\v 1 Anzongcau mǝnia ǝn nggǝ pà wun yalung puppup ka, wu kpatea nǝ mǝsǝcau, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu dum nǝyilǝmu sǝ wu hatǝki, sǝ ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu kutio wu kya ak nzali mǝnana Yahweh kánbì aká wun ama nǝ̀ pea wia ka.
\v 2 Wu ɗenyinǝ njar mǝnana kat Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun gingnǝ wun kàm a ɓabondo aɓalǝ apǝlǝa lumi-ine, sǝ yinǝ wun akaní ace kània wun nongsǝmúrû ka. Mwam wun ace súrǝ̀ gir mǝnana a ɓabum wun ngga, ko wun nǝ̀ kpata anzongcau male, ko pà wun nǝ̀ kpatea ɗàng.
\v 3 Kània wun nongsǝmúrû nǝ tsǝk nzala ɓǝ̀ wal wun, sǝ yi pa wun manna wu lì; yì girlina mǝnana wun, wunǝ aká wun ngga wu súrǝì raka, ace kània wun ama pà nǝ girlina nǝmurǝi sǝ ɓwa nǝ̀ dum nǝyilǝmu ɗang; nda andǝ koya cau mǝnana kǝ pur a kún Yahweh ka.\f + \fr 8:3 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa: \xt Mat 4:4; Luk 4:4\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 4 Aɓalǝ apǝlǝa lumi-ine man ngga, agir-nggūrǝu ma'wun tsǝuri ɗang, sǝ akusǝ wun mwarki gbal ɗàng.
\v 5 Wu tsǝk man a ɗenyicau ma'wun ama, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ kwarkir wun ace tsǝk wun a njar, kǝla mǝnana tár muna kǝ kwarkiri ace tsǝie a njar ka.
\v 6 Acemani ka, wu bwal anzongcau mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, wu gya atà angguracau male sǝ wu ɓanggi wi.
\v 7 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga nǝ̀ kánǝ wun aɓa nzali mǝɓoarne, yì nzali mǝnana ndanǝ amyalmúr, andǝ amáɗí-mùr, andǝ amgbeɗe mǝnana mùr malea kǝ ɓangŋa aɓalǝ aɓangŋaban andǝ múr ankono ka;
\v 8 nzali na mǝnana kǝ pusǝ mǝssa-alkama andǝ mǝssa-bálì, andǝ aɓǝla-anggun anap, andǝ vwari, andǝ mɓǝring, andǝ mùrú olif, andǝ mùr-nyì ka;
\v 9 nzali na mǝnana pà wu nǝ̀ pak tǝla girlina mǝnana wun nǝ̀ li ka ɗàng, sǝ pà wun nǝ̀ ɗwanyi kǝgir kàm ɗàng; nzali na mǝnana à kǝ kum bolo-candǝa aɓalǝ atali male, sǝ à kǝ tǝm bolo-bángŋá amúr ankono male ka.
\s1 Cè wu lórǝ́ Yahweh ɗàng
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 10 Lang wu lina girlina sǝ wu ɗǝmǝna ka, wu ɓwangsǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ace nzali mǝɓoarne mǝnana pà wun ngga.
\v 11 Wu parkir wun, cè wu lórǝ́ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, wu ginǝ kpata anzongcau, andǝ akwarkiru, andǝ angguracau male mǝnana ǝn nggǝ pà wun yalung ngga ɗàng;
\v 12 ɓǝ̀ ana raka, lang wu lina sǝ wu ɗǝmgina, sǝ wu ɓakkina aɓala amǝɓoarne, wu dumǝna aɓalǝia,
\v 13 sǝ lang andá andǝ ambul ma'wun hatǝkina, sǝ bolo-azǝrfa, andǝ bolo-njengǝlan, andǝ agir mǝnana kat wu ndanǝia ka, à hatǝkina ka,
\v 14 wu tsǝkir wun, wu kǝa dum nǝ twàlɓamúrû, sǝ wun nǝ̀ lorǝ́ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun mǝnana amsǝ wun a Masar, wu purî nzali guro ka ɗàng.
\v 15 Yì nda mǝnana gingnǝ wun nǝɓa nggea ɓabondo mǝpà ɓangciunì, mǝnana nǝ an'yau barya andǝ agenye aɓalǝi ka, sǝ nǝɓa nzali-ima mǝnana mùr pà kàm raka, sǝ tsǝk mùr pur aɓa tali mǝcandǝe ace wun ngga.
\v 16 Yì nda mǝnana pà wun manna wu li a ɓabondo ka, yì girlina mǝnana aká wun súrǝì raka, ace kània wun nongsǝmúrû sǝ ɓǝ̀ mwam wun, ace mǝnana a masǝlǝate ka nǝ̀ pàkka wun mǝɓoarne ka.
\v 17 Wu parkir wun, cè wu ne a ɓabum wun ama, <<Rǝcandǝa mem andǝ gandǝpe mala buam nda mǝnana kumbam man yì gǝna ka>> ɗang.
\v 18 A kún mani ka, wun nǝ̀ ɗenyinǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, acemǝnana yì nda ɓwa mǝnana pākiyia wun rǝcandǝa mala kum gǝna ka. Kǝ pak mǝnia ka anggo ace lǝmdǝ ama domǝsǝcau male arǝ kùrcau male mǝnana pang nǝ aká wun nǝ kángìr ka, ndakam piu.
\v 19 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ yi do ama a koya bàkú wu lórǝ́ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, sǝ wun nǝ̀ pǝlǝa atà aɓea aɓakuli ace kpata acau malea, sǝ wun nǝ̀ ɓun a ɓadǝmbia ka, mǝ nda aban nunkir wun yalung ama mbak-kàngkàng wun nǝ̀ kìɗìkì.
\v 20 Kǝla mǝnana Yahweh malanǝ̀ kìɗìki anzali mǝno wun nǝ̀ kánǝ munǝo arǝia ka, anggo sǝ wun nǝ̀ kìɗìkì, kǝla bafe mala ɗwanyi kwakikiru arǝ gi Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun.
\c 9
\s1 Gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ Ɓakuli nǝ̀ bwali amǝ Isǝrayila ɓǝà limurǝm ngga
\r (Puro 32:1-35)
\sp Musa bang ama:
\p 
\v 1 Wu ǒ, wun amǝ Isǝrayila! Yalung ngga wun nda wun nǝ̀ yàlî Nggeasala Jodan wun nǝ̀ ká ak nzali arǝ aɓwapǝndǝa mala anzali mǝnana à kútì wun nǝ gulo andǝ rǝcandǝa ka, sǝ anggea-là malea ka amǝgulke na sǝ à kàriá nǝ asheran mǝ'dāh'rike a kùli.
\v 2 Aɓwana mala anzalinì ka akaɓa aɓwana na, amǝ'dāh'rike, amuna-burana mala amǝ'Anak, mana wu súrǝ̀ia sǝ wu ongŋǝna cau amúrià ama, <<Yana ɓwe nǝ̀ gandǝ came a kún amǝ'Anak>> ka?
\v 3 Sǝama yalung ngga wu sǝlǝa ama ɓwa mǝnana nǝ̀ aka wun dǝmba aban ká dǝm wun kǝla bǝsa mǝ'earke ka nda Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun. Yì ka nǝ̀ gandǝia, sǝ nǝ̀ kiɗikia aɓadǝm wun. Anggo sǝ wun nǝ̀ pǝria sǝ wun nǝ̀ twaltea akaurǝa, kǝla mana Yahweh pà wun cau ace ka.
\p 
\v 4 Anzǝm mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pǝrnia aɓadǝm wun ngga, cè wu na aɓa ɗenyicau ma'wun ama, <<Nda ace cauɓoarna ma'sǝm sǝ Yahweh yinǝ sǝm aɓa nzali mǝnia ace ê ɓǝ̀ duk ma'sǝm>> ngga ɗàng. Mǝsǝcau ka nda mǝnana ama nda ace ɓealɓikea mala aɓwapǝndǝa mala anzali mǝnia ka sǝ Yahweh kǝ pǝria aɓadǝm wun.
\v 5 Pà ace ɓealɓoarna ma'wun ko pepè mala ɓabum wun sǝ wun nǝ̀ kutio wun nǝ̀ ak nzali malea ɓǝ̀ pǝlǝ girkuma ma'wun ngga ɗàng. Nda acemǝnana aɓwapǝndǝa mala amǝno yì anzali ka amǝ'ɓealɓikea na ka, sǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pǝria aɓadǝm wun, sǝ ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ lùmsǝ pacau male mǝnana kánbi aká wun, yia Ibǝrayim, andǝ Ishaku, sǝ Yakupu ka.
\p 
\v 6 Acemani ka, wu sǝlǝa ama Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pà aban pa wun nzali mǝɓoarne man ɓǝ̀ duk girkuma ma'wun ace ɓealɓoarna ma'wun ɗàng; wun ngga wu nda ka amǝ'murcandǝa.
\v 7 Wu ɗenyi sǝ ɓalǝ wun ɓǝkǝa lórǝ́ lúllô mana wu lulbum Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun a ɓabondo ka ɗàng. Lo a pwari mana wu nyìngŋǝ̀nà nzali Masar nǝi, bà yiu ma'wun a ban mǝnia ka, wu camarǝ mgbicau arǝ Yahweh.
\v 8 Ko a Horep ka, wu tsǝk Yahweh pàk bumlulla. Bumi-lullo arǝ wun, ue bǝti nǝ̀ twalta wun.
\v 9 Lang ǝn eau amur nkono ace ká ak akpamgbǝlang tali mǝnana Yahweh nyoulǝ kùrcau male amúrià, yì kùrcau mǝnana pang nǝ wun ngga, ǝn ue kano amur nkono nongŋo lumi-ine, du andǝ pwari; ǝn li kǝ girlina ɗàng sǝ ǝn nu mùr ɗàng.
\v 10 Pǝlǝa Yahweh pam akpamgbǝlang tali ɓari mǝnana nyoulǝ cau amúrià nǝ munabuì ka. Acau mǝno nyoulǝia ka à nda ka cau mǝnana kat Yahweh hamba wunia nǝɓa bǝsa amur nkono, a pwari ramba ma'wun abanɓwáná ka.
\v 11 A masǝlǝata anongŋo mǝno lumi-ine, du andǝ pwari ka, Yahweh pam amǝno yì akpamgbǝlang tali ɓari mǝnana nyoulǝna kùrcau amúrià ka.
\v 12 Osso Yahweh banggam cau ama:
\pi1 Lo, sulǝo a nzali akaurǝa, acemǝnana aɓwana mô mana a pusǝia a Masar ka, à kìɗìkìnà rǝia. À kyanggini njar akaurǝa, à nyìngŋǝ̀nà nzongcau mana ǝn tsǝkia wia ka; à ɓàngŋǝ́nì ɓamuria ɓǝ̀nzál nǝ bolo.
\s1 Muna-jamnda bolo-njengǝlan
\p 
\v 13 Ɗǝm ngga Yahweh bang ama:
\pi1 Ən sǝnǝni, aɓwana mǝnia ka amǝ'murcandǝa na.
\v 14 Ɗekiam, mǝ nǝ twaltea, mǝ esǝki lullǝia ɗǝɗak aɓa ɓanza. Sǝ mǝ nǝ nyesǝo awu nǝ duk nzali mǝnana kútiǎ nǝ lakkì andǝ rǝcandǝa ka.
\sp Sǝ Musa bang ama:
\p 
\v 15 Pǝlǝa ǝn wúliô ǝn sulǝì múr nkono sǝ nkonoe ka nda più aban earke nǝ lasǝ bǝsa; akpamgbǝlang tali ɓari mala kùrcau ka à nda arǝ abuam ɓari.
\v 16 Lang ǝn sǝni ka, ɓafo wu pàngŋǝ́nì Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun cauɓikea; wu ɓàngŋǝ́nì ɓamurǝ wun ɓǝ̀nzál mala muna-ndá. Wu pǝlǝna nzǝm wun akaurǝa arǝ njar mana Yahweh tsǝka wun ngga.
\v 17 Akǝ mǝsǝ sǝ wun ǝn nyesǝ akpamgbǝlang tali mǝno ɓari arǝ abuam ngga ǝn sukkia, à arkya.
\v 18 Osso ǝn sárǝ́ amur bumam aɓadǝm Yahweh kǝla mana a dǝmba ka, nongŋo lumi-ine, du andǝ pwari, ǝn li kǝgir ɗàng sǝ ǝn nu mùr ɗàng. Ən pak mǝnia ka ace cauɓikea mana kat wu pè, nǝ pak ɓealɓikea aɓadǝm Yahweh sǝ wu tsǝì bumi lul ka.
\v 19 Ɓangciu pakkam arǝ lúllô mǝnana bum Yahweh lul nǝ bumlulla mǝpìne mǝnana tàsǝì arǝ wun nǝ̀ twalta wun ngga. Sǝama Yahweh ok ɓua mem a pwari mǝno.
\v 20 Bum Yahweh lul arǝ Haruna kǝ̀rkǝ́r ɓǝ́ nǝ̀ kiɗiki. Sǝama ǝn pakhiwi ace Haruna gbal akǝ bu-pwarinì.
\v 21 Pǝlǝa ǝn twal mǝno yì gìr cauɓikea, yì muna-ndá wu pè ka, ǝn pisǝì a bǝsa sǝ ǝn goe pǝlǝ mukuì lǝkǝt-lǝkǝt kǝla tú, sǝ tuí ka ǝn sukki a myalmúr mǝnana sùlǝî múr nkono ka.
\p 
\v 22 Ɗǝm ngga wu lulbum Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun a Tabera,\f + \fr 9:22 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Ɓal 11:1-3\xt*\ft .\f* sǝ a Massa,\f + \fr 9:22 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pur 17:7\xt*\ft .\f* sǝ a Kibǝrot-hatava.\f + \fr 9:22 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Ɓal 11:34\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 23 Sǝ lang wu nda a Kadesh Bania ka, Yahweh tasǝ wun sǝ bangga wun ama, <<Wu eauwe wu kya ak nzali mǝnana ǝn pana wun ɓǝ̀ duk girkuma ma'wun ngga.>> Sǝ wun ngga wu mgbicau arǝ nzongcau mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun. Wu earnǝi ɗàng, sǝ wu oki wi ɗàng.
\v 24 Twal a pwari mǝdǝmbe mana ǝn súrǝ̀ wun nǝi ka, wun nda ka amǝgbikiru arǝ Yahweh.
\p 
\v 25 Ən sárǝ́ amur bumam pǝrapǝra a nzali aɓadǝm Yahweh aɓalǝ anonggio mǝno lumi-ine ka du andǝ pwari, acemǝnana Yahweh bangŋǝna ama nǝ̀ twalta wun.
\v 26 Ən pakhiwi aban Yahweh, ama:
\pi1 Yahweh Ɓakuli, kǝa twalta aɓwana mô ɗàng, yì girkuma mò mana a akmúria nǝ gulo mô, sǝ a pusǝia à purî ɓá nzali Masar nǝ nggea buo mǝ'rǝcandǝe ka.
\v 27 Ɗenyinǝ aguro mò, a Ibǝrayim, andǝ Ishaku, andǝ Yakupu. Kǝa pa hakkilo mô arǝ murcandǝa mala aɓwana mǝnia ka ɗàng, ko ɓealɓikea malea, ko cauɓikea malea ɗàng.
\v 28 Ɓǝ̀ ana raka aɓwana mala nzali mana a pusǝ sǝm, sǝm purî ɓalǝia ka à nǝ̀ na ama, <<Yahweh gandǝ warinǝia a nzali mana pàcau ace abania ka ɗàng, sǝ acemǝnana ɓinǝmǝsǝia ka, nda pusǝia sǝ kya wal-luia a ɓabondo ka.>>
\v 29 Kat andǝ amani ka, yia ka aɓwana mô na, girkuma mò mana a pusǝia à purî ɓá nzali Masar nǝ kaɓa rǝcandǝa mò andǝ mazo mala nggwarbuo ka.
\c 10
\s1 Bǝsa akpamgbǝlang tali ace anzongcau ɗǝm
\r (Puro 34:1-10)
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ banggi amǝ Isǝrayila cau ama:
\p 
\v 1 A bàkú mǝno ka, Yahweh banggam ama, <<Ɓun akpamgbǝlang tali ɓari kǝla mana a dǝmbe ka, sǝ wu eauwe wu yinǝia abanam amur nkono. Ɗǝm ngga gbàllì akwati nggun ace tsǝia.
\v 2 Acau mǝnana amur akpamgbǝlang tali mǝdǝmbe mana a arkia ka mǝ nǝ gilǝia amur akpamgbǝlang tali mǝnia ka, sǝ awu nǝ tsǝia aɓa akwatini.>>
\p 
\v 3 Nda ǝn gbàllì akwati nǝ nggun-akasiya, sǝ ǝn ɓun akpamgbǝlang tali ɓari kǝla mana a dǝmbe ka, sǝ ǝn eau nǝ akpamgbǝlang tali ɓari mǝnia ka a buam amur nkono.\f + \fr 10:3 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pur 25:10; 37:1\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 4 Pǝlǝa Yahweh gilǝ acau amur akpamgbǝlang tali mǝnia ka, kǝ acau mǝnana gilǝia ɗiɗyal a tadǝmbe ka, yì anzongcau lum mǝnana Yahweh pa wun nǝ nacau amur nkono aɓa bǝsa, a pwari mǝno wu ramba abani ka. Yahweh pam akpamgbǝlang talinì,
\v 5 pǝlǝa ǝn wulio ǝn súlǝì mùr nkono, sǝ ǝn yi tsǝia aɓa akwati mana ǝn gbàllì ka; à ndakam aɓalǝi kǝla mǝnana Yahweh banggam ngga.
\s1 Lú mala Haruna andǝ atúró mala apǝris
\r (Ɓal 20:22-29)
\p 
\v 6 (Amǝ Isǝrayila loapi ban Beerot Bene-Jaakan,\f + \fr 10:6 \fq Beerot Bene-Jaakan: \ft Ko <<atūli-mùr mala amǝ Jaakan.>>\f* sǝ à twal gya à yi sulǝo a Mosera. Abanì sǝ Haruna paklú sǝ à tsǝì kàm. Muna-ɓwabura male Eleaza ak bancame male aɓa túró pǝris.\f + \fr 10:6 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ɓal 20:22-29\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 7 Amǝ Isǝrayila lo gya ɗǝm ngga, à yi sulǝo a Gudgoda; à loapi Gudgoda ka à yi sulǝo a Jotbata, ban mala amyalmúr.\f + \fr 10:7 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Ɓal 33:31-33\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 8 A bákuì mǝno ka Yahweh tàr tau mala Lawi ɓǝà duk amǝ twal akwati kùrcau mala Yahweh, ɓǝà kǝ came aɓadǝm Yahweh ace pàk túró pǝris a ban peri, sǝ ɓǝà kǝ bang tsǝkbu male amur acili atau nǝ lullǝì, kǝla mǝnana ndakam bà yalung ngga.
\v 9 Acemani ka, aɓwana mǝnana a tàu mala Lawi ka, à pànǝ ɓekǝ nzali liɓala ko kǝ bare atà acili atau mala amǝ Isǝrayila ɗàng. Yahweh nda gir liɓala malea, kǝla mǝnana yì Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun banggia wia ka.)\f + \fr 10:9 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pǝris 25:32-34; Ɓal 18:20; 26:62; Nggur 18:1-2; Jes 13:14,33; Ezǝk 44:28-30\xt*\ft .\f*
\s1 Yahweh ok ahiwi mala Musa
\r (Puro 34:9,10,27-29)
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ cau aban amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 10 Sǝ mim ngga ǝn ueo amur nkono nongŋo lumi-ine du andǝ pwari, kǝla mǝnana ǝn pak atadǝmbe ka. A bàkú mǝno ka Yahweh ok hiwi mem gbal; earce ama nǝ̀ twalta wun ɗàng.
\v 11 Pǝlǝa Yahweh banggam ama, <<Lo, bwal njar akì aɓwana dǝmba ace mǝnana ɓǝà kya ak nzali mǝnana ǝn kánbi akeâ ama mǝ nǝ pea wia ka.>>
\s1 Gìr mǝnana Yahweh earkiyice ka
\sp Musa ne amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 12 Ado ka wun amǝ Isǝrayila, gìr mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun earkiyice nǝ wun ngga, nda mǝnana wu ɓanggi Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, wu duk amǝ gya arǝ anjar male kat, wu earceì, sǝ wu kpata Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ ɓabum wun kat andǝ ɓápǎ ma'wun kat,
\v 13 sǝ wu bwal anzongcau andǝ anê mala Yahweh, mǝnana ǝn nggǝ pà wun yalung ngga, ace mǝnana agir ɓǝà kyanba wun pepè.
\v 14 Wu sǝni, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga nda mǝtala kùli andǝ kùli mǝnana amur kùli ka, sǝ nzali gbal andǝ agir mǝnana kat aɓalǝi ka amale na.
\v 15 Sǝ kat andǝ amani ka, aká wun nǝmurǝia na lǝmdǝia wia earmúrú, sǝ tàr wun, wun amǝ'keà amur acili aɓwapǝndǝa, kǝla mǝno wu nda ka aɓwana male mǝnana tària più ka.
\v 16 Acemani ka, wu lak ɓabum wun, sǝ wu vwakibu wun arǝ pak ɓamúr-candǝa.
\v 17 Acemǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga, nda Ɓakuli mana kàrmúr acili aɓakuli kat, sǝ nda Murǝm amur amǝ'tala anzali kat ka. Yi nda Ɓakuli mǝgulo, mǝ'rǝcandǝa, andǝ mǝpa'ndali, mana lǝmdǝkiyi tàrban raka, sǝ kǝ ak pàbunǝnzali ɗang.
\v 18 Kǝ camata akáwá andǝ amā-lú aɓa pak ɓashi mǝ'mǝsǝcaunì. Kǝ ɗenyinǝ abǝri, kǝ pea wia girlina andǝ agir-nggūrǝu.
\v 19 Nda gìr mana tsǝa sǝ dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ earce abǝri, acemǝnana ɗiɗyal ka wun nda ka abǝri aɓa nzali Masar.
\v 20 Wu ɓanggî Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun. Wu kpata acau male, wu lanzǝ arǝì, sǝ apacau ma'wun ngga wu pea nǝ lullǝì.
\v 21 Yì nda nggori ma'wun, sǝ nda Ɓakuli ma'wun mana pakka wun amǝnia yì atúró mǝgulke, andǝ agir kàrmúrû mǝnana amǝsǝ wun sǝnia ka.
\v 22 Aká wun mǝnana à wari a Masar ka, à nda lumi-tongno-nong-ɓari yia kat. Sǝ adyan ngga, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nà wun wu làkkìna pas kǝla anlero mana a kùli ka.
\c 11
\s1 Wu earce Yahweh sǝ wu kpata cau male
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ ne amǝ Isǝrayila cau ama:
\p 
\v 1 Acemani ka, wun nǝ̀ earce Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, sǝ wun nǝ̀ kpata akwarkiru male; wu bwal anê andǝ anggurcau, andǝ anzongcau male koya pwari.
\v 2 Ɓǝ̀ ɓalǝ wun kasǝ yalung ama, ǝn pa aban nacau nǝ amuna ma'wun mǝnana à súrǝ̀ ko à sǝn anunkiru mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun raka ɗàng. Wun, nda mǝnana wu sùrǝ́nà rǝ gulo male, andǝ kaɓa rǝcandǝa male andǝ mazo mala nggwarbui,
\v 3 yì agir-lǝmdǝa andǝ atúró male mǝnana peǎ aɓa Masar, arǝ Firona murǝm Masar andǝ nzali male kat ka;
\v 4 andǝ gìr mǝnana pàkkî amǝ'lwa mala Masar, andǝ apǝr andǝ awaru-pǝr malea, andǝ nyesǝe mana nyesǝ Nggeamùr Nzuno yi kongsǝ múrià lang à nda rǝ pǝrta wun, sǝ Yahweh kiɗikia ba yalung ngga,
\v 5 andǝ gir mǝnana pakka wun a ɓabondo ba yiu ma'wun kani ka;
\v 6 andǝ gìr mǝnana Yahweh pàkkî Datan andǝ Abiram, amuna-burana mala Eliyap a tàu mala Ruben, mǝnana nzali mǝn kúní sǝ myalia, yià andǝ amǝ'ɓala malea, agumli malea, andǝ agir mǝnana kat à ndanǝ yilǝmu sǝ à kpatea, aɓalǝ amǝ Isǝrayila kat ka.
\v 7 Mǝ ndarǝ nacau nǝ wun mǝnana mǝsǝ wun sǝn agir mǝgule mǝnia Yahweh peǎ ka.
\s1 Atsǝkbu mala nzali mǝnana Ɓakuli pacau ace ka
\p 
\v 8 Acemani ka, wu tsǝkir wun, wu bwal anzongcau puppup mǝnana ǝn nggǝ pà wun yalung ngga. Ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu dum nǝ rǝcandǝa, sǝ wu kutio ace ak mǝno yì nzali wun nǝ̀ yàlî nkaring ace ê ɓǝ̀ duk girkuma ma'wun ngga;
\v 9 sǝ ɗǝm ngga ace mǝnana anonggio ma'wun ɓǝà sauwa aɓa mǝno yì nzali mǝnana Yahweh ak dǝmba kángìr aban aká wun ama nǝ̀ pea wia andǝ amǝ'keà, yì nzali mǝnana kiura andǝ mur'nyi kǝ ɓang kàm ngga.
\v 10 Nzali mana wu kǝ ká ê ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga, pà kǝla nzali Masar mǝnana wu purî ɓalǝi ka ɗang, mǝnana aɓalǝi ka wu ɓeal ɓeale sǝ wu kǝ gyate wu kǝ pà mùr nǝ bu wun, kǝla mana à kǝ pê a ɓaban ambukagir ka ɗàng.
\v 11 Sǝama, nzali mǝno wun nǝ̀ yàlî nkaring wun nǝ̀ nggá ê ka, nzali mala ankono na andǝ aɓangŋaban, mǝnana mùr-mbulo kǝ sulǝ nǝ kuli, kǝ pe wi mùr ka.
\v 12 Nzali na mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ ɗenyinǝi ka. Amǝsǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun na arǝì koya pwari, twal a tita pǝlǝa aban ká masǝlǝata pǝlǝa.
\p 
\v 13 Nǝ̀ do ama, ɓǝ̀ wun nǝ̀ kpata anzongcau mǝnana ǝn nggǝ pà wun yalung nǝ mǝsǝcau, ace earce Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, sǝ wun nǝ̀ kpate nǝ ɓabum wun kat, andǝ yilǝmi ma'wun kat ka,
\v 14 yì ka panacau male ama, <<Mǝ nǝ tasǝa wun mbulo a nzali ma'wun a kúnì male, yì mbulo mǝdǝmbe andǝ masǝlǝata mbulo, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu pwan gìrɓaban mala mǝsǝsa, andǝ bǝsa mùr-anap, andǝ mùrú ma'wun.
\v 15 Mǝ nǝ pà wun bondo a nzali ace agirkusǝu ma'wun. Wun nǝ̀ lì girlina wun nǝ̀ ɗǝmbo.>>
\p 
\v 16 Wu tsǝkir wun, cè ɓabum wun swarki wun, mǝnana wun nǝ̀ pǝlǝ atà aɓea aɓakuli, wun nǝ̀ kpata acau malea sǝ wun nǝ̀ peri abania ka ɗang.
\v 17 Ɓǝ̀ wu pàk anggo ka, bumlulla mala Yahweh nǝ̀ earbǝsa amur wun, sǝ nǝ̀ gìr kuli, mbulo pà nǝ̀ nya ɗang, sǝ nzali pa nǝ̀ pà gìrɓaban ɗang; anggo ka, wun nǝ̀ kìɗìkì akaurǝa, wun nǝ̀ malì ɓá nzali mǝɓoarne mǝnana Yahweh kǝ pà wun ngga.
\p 
\v 18 Acemani ka, wun nǝ̀ bwal acau mǝnia ka a ɓabum wun, sǝ a yilǝmi wun. Wun nǝ̀ kùria arǝ abu wun kǝla gìr'lǝmdǝa, sǝ wun nǝ̀ gyaria a kúndǝm wun.
\v 19 Wu kànî amuna ma'wun acê. Wu bang cau malea aban do arǝ aɓala ma'wun, sǝ aban gya amur njargula, sǝ aban nongŋo nǝ du, andǝ lo ma'wun nǝ bari.
\v 20 Wu gilǝì arǝ anggun-kúnakurǝm andǝ akúnɓala ma'wun,
\v 21 ace mana anonggio ma'wun, andǝ mala amuna wun, ɓǝà hatǝki kǝla anonggio mala kuli amur ɓanza, aɓa nzali mǝnana Yahweh kánbì aká wun ama nǝ̀ pea wia ka.
\v 22 Ɓǝ̀ wun nǝ̀ tsǝkir wun, wun nǝ̀ bwal anzongcau mǝnia kat ǝn nggǝ pà wun ɓǝ̀ wu kpatea, sǝ wun nǝ̀ earce Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, wun nǝ̀ gya aɓalǝ anjar male kat, sǝ wun nǝ̀ lanzǝ arǝì ka,
\v 23 Yahweh nǝ̀ pǝr aɓwapǝndǝa mala anzali mǝnia kat ka a dǝm wun, sǝ wun nǝ̀ ak nzali arǝ aɓwapǝndǝa mǝnana à kútì wun nǝ gulo andǝ rǝcandǝa ka.
\v 24 Ban mǝnana kat wu tsǝk kusǝ wun kàm ngga nǝ̀ duk ma'wun; nzong-nzali ma'wun nǝ̀ twal a pǝɗanban aban ká Lebano, sǝ nǝ̀ twal a nggeasala, yì Nggeasala Yiufǝretis a njar-takuli aban ká a kún Nggeamùr nǝ njar-nzali.
\v 25 Kǝ ɓwa pà nǝ̀ gandǝ cam a kún wun ɗàng. Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tsǝk ɓangciu ma'wun amur anzali, sǝ nǝ̀ gǝggǝli anzali mana kat wu tsǝk kusǝ wun kàm ngga, kǝla mǝnana bangga wun ngga.
\s1 Tsǝkbu andǝ súban
\p 
\v 26 Wu sǝni, yalung aɓadǝm wun ngga, mǝ ndaban tsǝk, tsǝkbu andǝ súban:
\v 27 wun nǝ̀ kum tsǝkbu ɓǝ̀ wu kpata anzongcau mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, amǝnana ǝn nggǝ pà wunia yalung ngga;
\v 28 sǝ súban nǝ̀ sulǝ amur wun, ɓǝ̀ wu ɓinǝ kpata anzongcau mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, sǝ wu pǝlǝa wu kyanggî njar mǝnia ǝn nggǝ tsǝka wunì yalung, sǝ wu kùtí a kpata aɓea aɓakuli mǝnana wu súrǝ̀ia raka.
\v 29 Nǝ̀ yia do ama, lang Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun yinanǝ wun aɓa nzali mǝno wun ndo wun nǝ̀ kutio wun nǝ̀ é ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga, wun nǝ̀ ham atsǝkbu amur Nkono Gerizim, sǝ wun nǝ̀ ham asúban amur Nkono Ebal.
\v 30 Kǝla mana wu sǝlǝ ka, ankono mǝnia ɓari ka à nda a nkaring Nggeasala Jodan, nǝ njar-nzali a bu kpa mala pwari, aɓa bu-nzali mala amǝ'Kan'ana mǝno à do a Araba, a mgbasho nǝ Gilgal, a nkanggari anggun mǝgulke mala More ka.
\p 
\v 31 Wu málá wun nǝ̀ yàllî Nggeasala Jodan, wun nǝ̀ kùtí ace ak nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ngga. Lang wu angŋǝ́nì wu dumǝna aɓalǝi ka,
\v 32 wu tsǝkir wun wu kpata anê andǝ angguracau mǝnana ǝn nggǝ tsǝka wunia aɓadǝm wun yalung ngga.
\c 12
\s1 Ban mwashat mala peri
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ ne amǝ Isǝrayila cau ama:
\p 
\v 1 Mǝnia ka à nda ka anê andǝ akasǝcau mǝnana dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ tsǝkir wun, wun nǝ̀ kpatea a do ma'wun aɓa nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli mala aká wun pana wun ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ba do ma'wun a ɓanza ka.
\v 2 Aɓwapǝndǝa mala anzali mǝnana wun nǝ̀ ak nzali arǝia ka, wu kiɗiki abân mana à kǝ peri kàm aban aɓakuli malea ka, amúr ankono andǝ amgbangban, andǝ tǝrta koya nggun mǝpwale.
\v 3 Wu kwarki agyangŋan malea. Wu arki akúnamúrú malea, sǝ wu pisǝ atondong peri aban Ashera,\f + \fr 12:3 \fq atondong peri aban Ashera: \ft anggun mǝsake mǝnana à shària ace pángŋǝ̀nà-túró nǝia lang à nǝ̀ peri aban Ashera, yì mā-ɓakuli malea ka.\f* a bǝsa. Wu tsauwiki aɓǝ̀nzál mala aɓakuli malea mǝnana à shària ka, sǝ wu esǝki lullǝia ɓǝà kǝa ɗenyinǝia ɗǝm arǝ abân mǝno ɗàng.
\p 
\v 4 Pà wun nǝ̀ peri aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ulang pě malea ɗàng.
\v 5 Wu alta ban mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tàrrì aɓalǝ atau ma'wun kat, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ tsǝk lùllǝì kàm ɓǝ̀ duk bando male ka; a banì sǝ wun nǝ̀ ká.
\v 6 A banì sǝ wun nǝ̀ kánǝ apagir ma'wun mala pisǝe kǝring andǝ agir'nkila ma'wun, akāmbe mwashat aɓa lum mala akume ma'wun, andǝ akāmbe mala aɓoro mǝnana wun nǝ̀ pa, andǝ apagir mala lùmsǝ apacau nǝ-shambum ma'wun, andǝ apagir ma'wun mala eare mala ɓabum wun, andǝ amuna-dǝmba mala andá andǝ mala ambul andǝ mala anzur ma'wun.
\v 7 Akanó aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, wun wunǝ amǝɓala ma'wun, wun nǝ̀ lì girlina, sǝ wun nǝ̀ pàk banɓoarnado arǝ atúró mala bù wun, acemǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun tsǝ́ngŋǝ̀nà wun bù.
\p 
\v 8 Pà wu nǝ̀ pǎ kǝla mǝnana kat sǝm nggǝ pak kani yalung ngga ɗàng. Yalung ngga koya ɓwa ka kǝ pak gìr mǝnana ɓoari wi a mǝsǝi ka.
\v 9 Mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana wu malaká kútí peatu a ban mǝnana wun nǝ̀ usǝlǝ kam, andǝ ban liɓala mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ngga ɗàng.
\v 10 Sǝama lang wu yalnì nkaring Nggeasala Jodan, sǝ wu dumǝna a nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ace liɓala, sǝ lang pàna wun usǝlǝo aban aɓiwun amǝbura mǝnana kat à kàrì wun, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu do aɓa rǝpwala ka,
\v 11 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tàr bando ace lùllǝì. A banì sǝ wun nǝ̀ yinǝ agir mǝnana kat ǝn bangga wun cau acea ama ɓǝ̀ wu yinǝia ka: apagir ma'wun mala pisǝe kǝring andǝ agir'nkila ma'wun, akāmbe mwashat aɓa lum mala akume ma'wun, andǝ aɓoro mǝnana wu tària wun nǝ̀ pa, andǝ agir nggea-mǝɓoarne mǝnana kat wu pàcau nǝ-shambum ama wun nǝ̀ pè Yahweh ka.
\v 12 Sǝ a banì sǝ wun nǝ̀ pàk banɓoarnado aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, wun wunǝ amuna ma'wun aburana andǝ amamǝna, andǝ amǝ'túró-ɓala ma'wun aburana andǝ amamǝna; wun nǝ̀ pè atarǝ wun wunǝ amǝ'kà Lawi mǝnana à do arǝ alá ma'wun ngga, acemǝnana yià ka à pànǝ kǝ nzali ace liɓala ko kǝ bare ace ɓamuria kǝla wun ɗàng.
\v 13 Wu tsǝkir wun wu kǝa pà apagir ma'wun mala pisǝe kǝring a koya ban mǝnana wu sǝn ngga ɗàng.
\v 14 Ban mǝnana Yahweh nǝ̀ tàrì aɓa nzali mala ɓè tàu ma'wun ngga, akanó sǝ wun nǝ̀ pà apagir ma'wun mala pisǝe kǝring, sǝ akanó sǝ wun nǝ̀ pak agir mǝnana kat ǝn bangga wun ngga.
\p 
\v 15 Kat andǝ amani ka, wun nǝ̀ gandǝ pwanmyal agirkusǝu ma'wun sǝ wun nǝ̀ shak nyamia aɓa komǝye atà alá ma'wun, kǝla mana kat wu earkiyice, sǝ kǝla mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tsǝka wun bù arǝ alá ma'wun kat ka. Koɓǝ̀ ɓwa ka nda aɓa ɓeami ko aɓa ɓoarnsari ka, nǝ̀ gandǝ shak nyame, kǝla mana wun nǝ̀ shak nyam ɓwacembe ko keran ngga.
\v 16 Sǝama wu kǝa lì nkila ɗàng; wu ɗārǝí a nzali kǝla mùr.
\v 17 Pà wun nǝ̀ lì kāmbe mwashat aɓa gauwe lum mala mǝssa ma'wun, ko mala bǝsa mùr-anap ma'wun, ko mala mùrú olif ma'wun aɓalǝ alá ma'wun ɗàng. Anggo gbal, koya ndǎ ko mbul ma'wun mǝnana tita puro a bum ngge, ko koya gìr mana kat wu pàcau ace nǝ-shambum ama wun nǝ̀ pè Yahweh, ko aɓoro mala eare mala ɓabum wun, ko amǝnana wu tària wun nǝ̀ pà gbal ka, wu kǝa liǎ ɗàng.
\v 18 Amǝno yì aɓoro kat ka, aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun sǝ wun nǝ̀ liǎ, a ban mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tàrî ɓamúrì ka. A kàm sǝ wun, wunǝ amuna ma'wun aburana andǝ amamǝna, andǝ amǝ'túró-ɓala ma'wun aburana andǝ amamǝna, andǝ amǝ'kà Lawi mǝnana arǝ alá ma'wun ngga, wun nǝ̀ lì. Akǝ ban mǝno wun nǝ̀ pàk banɓoarnado aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ koya gir mana kat túró ma'wun kumba wun ngga.
\v 19 Wu tsǝkir wun, wu kǝa ɗwanyi falǝ nǝ amǝ'kà Lawi a do ma'wun kat aɓa nzali ma'wun ɗàng.
\p 
\v 20 Lang Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun tangsǝna nzong-nzali ma'wun, kǝla mana pàcau ama nǝ̀ pè, sǝ nzal nyama wal wun, wu na ama wu earce shak nyama ka, wun nǝ̀ gandǝ shak nyama kǝla mana kat wu earce shě ka.
\v 21 Ɓǝ̀ ban mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tàrì ace tsǝk lùllǝì ka, ɓiki sappì ban mǝnana wu ndakam ngga, wun nǝ̀ gandǝ wal ndá ko mbul mǝnana Yahweh pà wun ngga, kǝla mǝnana ǝn bangga wun ngga, sǝ wu shak nyame a là ma'wun a pwari mǝnana kat wu earce ka.
\v 22 Kǝla mana wun nǝ̀ shak nyam ɓwacembe ko keran ngga, anggo sǝ wun nǝ̀ shak nyame. Koɓǝ̀ ɓwa ka nda aɓa ɓeami ko aɓa ɓoarnsari ka, yia kǝm à nǝ̀ gandǝ shak nyame.
\v 23 Sǝ wu tsǝkir wún wu kǝa lì nkila ɗàng, acemǝnana yilǝmu ka nda aɓa nkila sǝ dumǝna ama, pà wu nǝ̀ shak nyama andǝ yilǝmu ɗang.
\v 24 Wu kǝa lì nkila ɗàng; wu ɗārǝi a nzali kǝla mùr.
\v 25 Pà wun nǝ̀ lì nkile ɗàng, ace mǝnana wun wunǝ amuna ma'wun ngga, ɓǝ̀ agir kat ɓoara wun, sǝ anggo gbal ka wu pàngŋǝ̀nà gìr mǝnana nda jik ka, aɓadǝm Yahweh.
\v 26 Sǝama agir mǝnana wu tària ace Ɓakuli andǝ agir mǝnana wu pàcau acea nǝ-shambum ama wun nǝ̀ pè Yahweh ka, wu umnǝia a ban mǝnana Yahweh nǝ̀ tàrì ka.
\v 27 Wu pà apagir ma'wun mala pisǝe kǝring, nyama andǝ nkila kǝm, amur gyangŋan mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun. Nkila mala agir'nkila ma'wun ngga wun nǝ̀ solǝi amúr gyangŋan mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, sǝama nyame ka, wun nǝ̀ gandǝ shè.
\v 28 Wu tsǝkir wun, wu kpata mǝnia yì angguracau ǝn nggǝ pà wun ngga. Lang wu pàk mǝno ka, wun nda aban pak gir mǝnana nda jik aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga. Sǝ anggo ka wun wunǝ amuna ma'wun andǝ amǝkà wun ngga agir nǝ̀ kyanba wun pepè tàtǝ́k.
\s1 Nunkiru arǝ peri atà ankúl
\sp Musa ne amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 29 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga nǝ̀ kìɗìki aɓwapǝndǝa mala anzali mǝnana wun nda aban ká ak nzali arǝia ka. Sǝ lang wu pǝrnia, wu dumǝna a nzali malea ka,
\v 30 wu tsǝkir wun wu kǝa kpa aɓa gbǝ́lî mala kànì anjar malea, anzǝm mana à kìɗìkìnia ka ɗàng. Wu kǝa kútiá ɗìbancau amur aɓakuli malea ama, <<Lang sǝ aɓwapǝndǝa man kǝ kpata aɓakuli malea, ace mǝnana sǝm nǝ̀ pàk ulang malea ka>> ɗàng.
\v 31 Wu kǝa peri aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝla mana à kǝ peri aban aɓakuli malea ka ɗàng, acemǝnana koya gìr'ɓeami mǝnana Yahweh ɓinǝce ka nda à pàkkiyi aban peri aban aɓakuli malea ka. Yià ka à kǝ gandǝ pisǝ amunia a bǝsa ace pà gir'nkila aban aɓakuli malea.
\p 
\v 32 Wu kpata anzongcau andǝ akanìgìr mǝnana kat ǝn nggǝ pà wun ngga, sǝ wu peǎ nǝ tsǝkiru; cè wu tsǝk ɓè amurí ko wu amsǝ ɓè aɓalǝi ɗàng.
\c 13
\s1 Nunkiru arǝ peri aban aɓǝ̀nzál
\p 
\v 1 Ɓǝ̀ ɓekǝ mǝɓangnǝa, ko mǝ'lorǝki alorǝo amur gìr mǝnana nǝ̀ kumban ngga, lo aɓalǝ wun sǝ lǝmdǝa wun ɓekǝ gir'lǝmdǝa ko ɓekǝ gìr'ndali,
\v 2 sǝ bangga wun ama, <<Wu yiu ɓǝ̀ sǝm kpata aɓea aɓakuli sǝ ɓǝ̀ sǝm peri abania,>> aɓakuli mǝnana wu súrǝ̀ia raka, sǝ ko ɓǝ̀ mǝno yì gir'lǝmdǝa ko gìr'ndali hamce ka yi lumsǝ ka,
\v 3 wu kǝa kwakikir wun arǝ acau mala mǝno yì mǝɓangnǝa ko mǝ'lorǝki alorǝo ka ɗàng! Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga ndarǝ mwam wun nǝ̀ sǝnì ko wun nǝ̀ earce Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ ɓabum wun kat andǝ yilǝmi wun kat.
\v 4 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝmurǝi nda mǝnana wun nǝ̀ kpatè sǝ wun nǝ̀ ɓanggi wi ka. Wu bwal anzongcau male sǝ wu oki wi. Wu peri a baní sǝ wu lanzǝ arǝì kàngkàng.
\v 5 Sǝ dumǝna púp mǝno yì mǝɓangnǝa ko mǝ'lorǝki alorǝo ka ɓǝà wal-luí, acemǝnana hamna mgbicau arǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun mǝnana pusǝ wun aɓa nzali Masar, sǝ akmúr wun a ɓata doguro ka; yì ka ɓarikina nǝ̀ swár wun ɓǝ̀ wu kyanggî njar mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pà wun nzongcau ace ama ɓǝ̀ wu kpatè ka. Anggo sǝ wun nǝ̀ esǝki ɓealɓikea ɓǝ̀ malì ɓalǝ wun.
\p 
\v 6 Ɓǝ̀ mǝ'eambo, muna-ɓwabura mala nggo, ko laggaleo ko ɓoarnsarileo, ko māmó mǝnana a earkiyi ace raka, ko gyajam-ndà mò swárǒ zàng ama, <<Fá sǝm nggá peri aban aɓea aɓakuli>> ka, kǝa ear ɗàng. Acemǝnana amǝno yì aɓakuli ka, we ko akeô ka wu súrǝ̀ia ɗàng.
\v 7 À nda ka aɓakuli mala aɓwana mala anzali mǝnana à gumbǝli wun ngga, amǝnana tù aban wun, andǝ amǝnana à nda zak nǝ wun, lo a ɓè bum ɓanza aban ká ɓè bum ɓanza ka.
\v 8 Kǝa ear nǝ mǝno yì ɓwa, ko awu nǝ kwakikiro arǝì ɗàng. Kǝa sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr male ɗàng. Kǝa nyì ɓǝ̀ àwá ko awu nǝ kùmsǝ̀te ɗàng.
\v 9 Dumǝna púp ama a nda mǝnana awu nǝ tita lo arǝì ace wal-luí, sǝ nǝnzǝ́mò ka bu aɓwana kat nǝ̀ yiu atò ka.
\v 10 Wun nǝ̀ ɓukki nǝ atali ɓǝ̀ wú, acemǝnana yì ka alte nǝ̀ pǝlǝǒ, ama wu nying kpata Yahweh Ɓakuli mô, mǝnana pusǝo aɓa nzali Masar sǝ a purì ɓala guro ka.
\v 11 Sǝ amǝ Isǝrayila kat nǝ̀ okce, ɓangciu nǝ̀ bwalia, sǝ kǝ ɓwa aɓalǝ wun pà nǝ̀ nyare nǝ̀ pàk ulang mǝno yì ɓealɓikea ka ɗàng.
\p 
\v 12 Ɓǝ̀ wu ok ɓekǝ cau nggùr-nggùr amur mwashat atà alá mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ɓǝ̀ wu duk kam,
\v 13 ama amǝ'ɓealɓikea longŋǝ́nà aɓalǝ aɓwana ma'wun, sǝ à ɓosǝkina aɓwana mala là malea nǝ nea wia ama, <<Wu fa sǝm nǝ̀ ká ace peri aban aɓea aɓakuli,>> aɓakuli mǝnana wu súrǝ̀ia ɗiɗyal raka,
\v 14 dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ ɗìkìban, wun nǝ̀ bǝlkiɓa cê ɓukɓuk, wu súrǝ̀ mǝsǝcau male pepè. Ɓǝ̀ cê ka mǝsǝcau na, sǝ à bwalatè mbak-kàngkàng ama mǝnia yì gìr'ɓeami ka à pàngnǝ̀nì aɓalǝ aɓwana ma'wun ngga,
\v 15 dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ wal-lú aɓwana mǝnana kat à do a mǝno yì là ka. Wu kiɗiki lě kat-kat; wu kǝa nying kǝ ɓwa ko agirkusǝu mana aɓalǝi ka ɗàng.
\v 16 Wu ramba agirkuma mala lě kat a patal; sǝ wu pisǝ lě andǝ agirkume kat-kat a bǝsa, kǝla pàgir mana à pìsǝì kǝring ace Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga. Mǝno yì là ka ɓǝà nyi ɓǝ̀ ue anggo gìgí tàtǝ́k, ɓǝà kǝa nyare ɓǝà ɓè ɗǝm ɗàng.
\v 17 Kǝɓè pà kàm atà amǝno yì agir mana à kasǝna ɓashi amúrià ɓǝà kiɗikia ka, à nǝ̀ kumi a bu wun ɗàng, ace mǝnana Yahweh ɓǝ̀ nying bumlulla mǝpìne male, sǝ ɓǝ̀ lǝmdǝa wun ɓwamuru ka. Yì ka nǝ̀ sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr ma'wun, sǝ nǝ̀ hatǝki wun, kǝla mǝnana kánbì aká wun ngga,
\v 18 ɓǝ̀ wu nǝ̀ okî Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, wun nǝ̀ kpata anzongcau male mǝnana kat ǝn nggǝ pà wun yalung ngga, sǝ wun nǝ̀ pàk gìr mana nda jik a mǝsǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga.
\c 14
\s1 Agir mǝnana Ɓakuli earnǝia andǝ amana pǝrban arǝia ka
\sp Musa bang ama:
\p 
\v 1 Wun nda ka amuna mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun. Pà wu nǝ̀ cangi nggūrǝ wun, ko wun nǝ̀ mwa nyang kúndǝm wun ace ɓua lú ɗàng.
\v 2 Wun ngga wu nda ka aɓwana amǝfele aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, sǝ Yahweh tàrna wun ɓǝ̀ wu duk aɓwana male, mǝnana kǝ twal wun nǝ dǝmbǝrya amur acili aɓwana kat aɓa ɓanza ka.
\v 3 Pà wun nǝ̀ lì kǝgìr mǝnana à ɓinǝce ka ɗàng.
\v 4 Amǝnia ka, à nda ka nyama mǝnana wun nǝ̀ lì ka:
\li1 ndǎ, andǝ nzur, andǝ mbulpǝndǝa,
\li1 
\v 5 andǝ keran, andǝ mbamba, andǝ lùrú,
\li1 andǝ mbul-ɓa'nkono, andǝ ɓwachembe, andǝ lyaran,
\li1 sǝ nzur-ɓa'nkono.
\m 
\v 6 Koya girkusǝu mǝnana ndanǝ nkaulakusǝi ɓulkǝt sǝ gau ɓari, sǝ kǝ ɓǝsǝlǝshe ka, nǝ̀ pà atà agirkusǝu mǝnana wun nǝ lì ka.
\v 7 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ girkusǝu panǝ amǝnia yì agir kǝm raka, wu kǝa lì ɗàng. Acemani ka wu kǝa lì:
\li1 kalakadambi, ko mpkalang, ko nsong ɗang. Kat andǝ amani ama à kǝ ɓǝsǝlǝshe ka, à pànǝ nkaulakusǝu ɓulkǝt mana gau ɓari ka ɗàng. Agir'ɓeami na aban wun.
\li1 
\v 8 Anggo gbal, pà wun nǝ̀ lì tǝmbǝrǝm ɗàng. Kat andǝ amani ama ndanǝ nkaulakusǝu ɓulkǝt mana gau ɓari ka, kǝ ɓǝsǝlǝshe ɗàng. Gìr'ɓeami na aban wun.
\p 
\v 9 Atà agir mǝnana à nda a tàmùr ka, amǝnia ka à nda ka mǝnana wun nǝ̀ lì ka: gìr mǝnana kat ndanǝ abú-omùr andǝ nggwate ka.
\v 10 Gìr mǝnana pànǝ abú-omùr andǝ nggwate raka, wu kǝa lì ɗàng; gìr'ɓeami na aban wun.
\p 
\v 11 Wun nǝ̀ gandǝ li koya nyal mǝnana nggurcau ear ama mǝɓoarne na ɓǝà lì ka,
\v 12 sǝama amǝnia ka à nda ka mǝnana pà wun nǝ̀ lia raka:
\li1 nkwang, andǝ baula, andǝ dǝkǝlaki,
\li1 
\v 13 andǝ kùnggúm, andǝ mǝ'nzǝkarka, andǝ koya ulang gìrfwanji,
\v 14 andǝ koya ulang gang'lang,
\li1 
\v 15 andǝ ndaù, andǝ gihi, andǝ nyal-nggeamùr, andǝ koya nyal mǝnana nda kǝla mǝ'nzǝkarka ka,
\li1 
\v 16 gihi mǝkyauwe, andǝ gihi mǝgule, andǝ gihi mǝpwasǝe,
\li1 
\v 17 andǝ gir-nkeli, andǝ kungum, andǝ npyauwar,
\v 18 andǝ nyal-la, andǝ koya ulang nyal mǝ'garakusǝsakya,
\li1 andǝ nzaɓako sǝ mǝkyengkyeng.
\m 
\v 19 Ankūngga mǝnana kat nǝ mburu ka agir'ɓeami na aban wun. Pà wu nǝ̀ liǎ ɗàng.
\v 20 Wun nǝ̀ gandǝ li koya nyal mǝnana nggurcau ear ama mǝɓoarne na ɓǝà lì ka.
\p 
\v 21 Wun ngga wu nda ka amǝfele aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun. Pà wun nǝ̀ lì nyam gir mǝnana kasǝa wǔ atarǝì ka ɗàng. Wun nǝ̀ gandǝ pê abǝri mǝnana à yiua do bǝti arǝ alá ma'wun ngga, sǝ à nǝ̀ gandǝ li, ko awu nǝ makkì ɓwa-kúnɗàngna.
\p A pà wu nǝ̀ lam muna-mbul aɓa kiura nggè ɗàng.
\s1 Kāmbe mwashat aɓa gauwe lum // mala agirɓaban ace Yahweh
\p 
\v 22 Gìrɓaban mǝnana kat pùr aɓa mǝsǝɓeale mǝnana a ɓeal a aɓaban mô koya pǝlǝa ka, dumǝna púp awu nǝ̀ pà kāmbe mwashat aɓa lum male.
\v 23 A wu nǝ yinǝ kāmbe mala mǝsǝsa mò, andǝ mala bǝsa mùr-anap mò, andǝ mala mùrú olif mò, andǝ mala amuna-dǝmba mala andá, andǝ ambul, andǝ anzur mô, aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli mô, a ban mǝnana nǝ̀ tàrì, nǝ̀ tsǝk lùllǝì kàm ɓǝ̀ duk bando male ka; akanó sǝ awu nǝ lì ka akāmbe man aɓadǝm Yahweh, ace mǝnana wu kànì ɓanggi Yahweh Ɓakuli mô koya pwari.
\p 
\v 24 Lang Yahweh Ɓakuli mô tsǝ̀ngŋǝ́nò bù, à kumǝna gìrɓaban kǝ̀rkǝ́r, sǝ a pà nǝ gandǝ twal kāmbe male wu kyan nǝi a ban mǝnana Yahweh nǝ̀ tàrì ace tsǝk lùllǝì kàm raka, acemǝnana banì ɓiki sappì ban là mò ka,
\v 25 awu nǝ gandǝ me a kún bolo-azǝrfa. Sǝ wu twal boale a buo, wu kyan nǝi a ban mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tàrì ka.
\v 26 A wu nǝ gandǝ kasǝ boale ace kúr komana kat bumo earce ka: ndǎ, ko nzur, ko mbul, ko mùr-anap, ko ɓekǝ girnùná mǝhangŋe, andǝ koya gìr mǝnana kat a pàk nzalè ka. Pǝlǝa we wunǝ amǝ'ɓala mò, wun nǝ̀ lì girlina akanó aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, sǝ wun nǝ̀ pàk banɓoarnado.
\v 27 Sǝ awu nǝ ɗenyinǝ ɓwa'Lawi mǝnana do a là mò ka, acemǝnana yì ka pànǝ ɓekǝ nzali liɓala ko kǝ bare atà wun ɗàng.
\p 
\v 28 A masǝlǝata koya tàruià pǝlǝa ka, koya gìr mǝnana kat a pwan a ɓaban mô a pǝlǝa mǝno ka, awu nǝ̀ yinǝ kāmbe mwashat aɓa lum malea wu yi tsǝi aɓa ndà ram girlina mǝnana a là ma'wun ngga.
\v 29 Mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana ɓwa'Lawi, mana pànǝ ɓekǝ nzali liɓala ko kǝ bare atà wun raka, andǝ abǝri mana à do aɓalǝ wun, andǝ akáwá, andǝ amā-lú, mǝnana arǝ alá ma'wun ngga, ɓǝà yiu ɓǝà kum girlina a mǝnia yì ndà ram girlina ka, ɓǝà li ɓǝà ɗǝmbo. Sǝ anggo ka Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tsǝka wun bù arǝ atúró ma'wun mǝnana kat wu kǝ peǎ ka.
\c 15
\s1 Twalban atangna
\p 
\v 1 A masǝlǝata koya tongno-nong-ɓaria pǝlǝa ka, dumǝna púp awu nǝ twalban atangna mǝnana a kǝ kpata aɓwana ka.
\v 2 Ani sǝ wun nǝ̀ pè: ɓwa mǝnana kat pè mǝ'eambi ko ɓwa Isǝrayila tangna ka, nǝ̀ twalbanì. Ɓǝ̀ kǝa na ama nǝ̀ tsǝa ɓǝà mbwè púp ɗang, acemǝnana à hamǝna nǝ pwari mala Yahweh ace twalban tangna.
\v 3 Mǝnia yì nzongcau mala twalban tangna ka nda ace amǝ Isǝrayila nǝmurǝia. Ɓǝ̀ ɓwa ka ɓwa-kúnɗàngna na ka, nǝ̀ mbwè tangna mǝnana amurí ka.
\p 
\v 4 Yàle kǝɓwa pà atà wun nǝ̀ duk mǝ'tǝ̀r ɗàng, acemǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga, nǝ̀ tsǝka wun bù a nzali mǝnana kǝ pà wun ɓǝ̀ wu duk kam ace liɓala ka.
\v 5 A wu nǝ kum mǝnia yì tsǝkbu ka, yì mana ɓǝ̀ a tsǝkiro pepè a kpata anzongcau mǝnia mǝnana kat ǝn nggǝ pà wun yalung ngga.
\v 6 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga nǝ̀ tsǝka wun bù kǝla mǝnana pàcau ama nǝ̀ pè ka. Wun nǝ̀ pà tangna aban anzali pas, sǝ wun ngga, pà wun nǝ̀ ak tangna a bù kǝɓwa ɗàng; wun nǝ̀ duk amǝ'yálmúr anzali pas, sǝ kǝ nzali pa nǝ̀ duk mǝ'yálmúr wun ɗàng.
\p 
\v 7 Ɓǝ̀ kǝ mǝ'tǝ̀r nakam aɓalǝ amǝ'eam wun aɓa ɓekǝ là, aɓa nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ngga, wu kǝa dumnǝ ɓabumtǝra, ko wun nǝ̀ kùr bu wun arǝ mǝ'eam wun mǝtǝ̀r ɗàng.
\v 8 Awu nǝ mǝn buo a baní, awu pè wi tangna mala gìr mǝnana nǝ̀ karǝ tǝle male ka, koɓǝ̀ mana gir na ka.
\v 9 Wu tsǝkir wun wu kǝa twal ɓabum ɓikea mǝnana wun nǝ̀ na ama, <<Tongno-nong-ɓaria pǝlǝa, yì pǝlǝa mala twalban atangna ka gbàshìnà,>> gandǝa nǝ̀ tsǝo, wu lǝmdǝ ɓike arǝ mǝ'eambo mǝnana nda aɓa tǝle, sǝ awu nǝ gìrìnǝ tangna ka. Sǝ yì ka, nǝ̀ ɓua nǝ we aban Yahweh, sǝ anggo ka awu nǝ̀ kúmcàu mala pàk mǝɓane aban Ɓakuli.
\v 10 Awu nǝ pe wi nǝ nyingbù, nǝ eare mala ɓabum, nggwani pà atè ɗàng, acemǝnana nda ace mǝno ka sǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tsǝko bù arǝ atúró mô kat andǝ agir mǝnana kat a tsǝa a dǝmbo, awu nǝ peǎ ka.
\v 11 A koya pwari ka, à pà nǝ̀ ɗwanyi kum amǝ'tǝ̀r aɓa nzali ma'wun ɗàng; nda gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ ǝn nggǝ na wun ama, wu mǝn bù wun aban amǝ'eam wun, andǝ amǝ'tǝ̀r andǝ amǝ'tǝlè aɓa nzali ma'wun.
\s1 Pè aguro kumɓamuru
\r (Puro 21:1-11)
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ nê amǝ Isǝrayila cau ama:
\p 
\v 12 Ɓǝ̀ ɓiò ɓwa Isǝrayila, ɓwama ko ɓwabura, makkò ɓamúrì, ko à makkò wi ɓǝ̀ duk guro mò, sǝ pàkkô túró pǝlǝa tongno-nong-mwashat ka, a tongno-nong-ɓaria pǝlǝa ka, awu nǝ nying buo arǝì ɓǝ̀ kum ɓamúrì.
\v 13 Sǝ lang a panzǝni ka, kǝa tasǝte ɓǝ̀ o anggo nǝ ɓabui ɓà ɗàng.
\v 14 Pè wi gìr kpǝm nǝ mǝnbù atà agirkusǝu mala domwan mò, sǝ aɓa mǝsǝsa andǝ mùr-anap mò. Pè wi kǝla mana Yahweh Ɓakuli mô tsǝko bù ka.
\v 15 Ɓǝ̀ ɓalǝo kasǝa ama we gbal ɗiɗyal ka, a nda guro a nzali Masar, sǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli mô akmuro. Nda gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ ǝn tsǝko mǝnia yì nzongcau yalung ngga.
\v 16 Sǝama yakǝla ɓè guro, mǝtúró-ɓala mò, nǝ̀ banggo ama earce nǝ̀ o nǝ̀ nyio ɗang, acemǝnana kǝ earceo wunǝ amǝ'ɓala mò ka, sǝ we gbal ka a sǝni ka do male a bano ka ɓoarǝ́nò.
\v 17 Twal mundi sǝ wu tusǝ mburkiri arǝ kunkurǝm; mǝno ka nǝ̀ lǝmdǝ ama nǝ̀ duk guro mò bà lú male. Kǝ gìr mǝ'mwashati na awu nǝ pàngnǝi ko yì guro ka ɓwabura ko ɓwama na ka.
\p 
\v 18 Lang awu nǝ panzǝ guro ɓǝ̀ kum ɓamúrì ka, cê ɓǝ̀kǝa dupô nǝ kwánó ɗang, acemǝnana túró male mana pàkkô aɓa pǝlǝa tongno-nong-mwashat, ɓǝ̀ túró-boalo na ka, awu nǝ mbwe boale kusǝ ɓari. Pè anggo sǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli mô nǝ̀ tsǝkô bù arǝ agir mǝnana kat a pàkkiyi ka.
\s1 Pè Ɓakuli gìr mǝnana ɓoaro kutibanì ka
\r (Ace Apǝris 27:26,27; Ɓal 18:15-18)
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 19 Ɓǝ̀ ndǎ, ko nzur, ko mbulpǝndǝa mô ɓǝl jamne a dǝmba ka, mǝno yì jamgir ka dumǝna mala Yahweh Ɓakuli mô. Ndǎ mǝnana à ɓǝli a dǝmba ka, ɓǝà kǝa tsǝì ɓǝ̀ duk ndà-rya ɗang, sǝ ɓǝà kǝa mwa nyang rǝ nzur mǝnana à ɓǝlì a dǝmba ka ɗàng.
\v 20 Koya pǝlǝa ka, we wunǝ amǝ'ɓala mò ka, wun nǝ̀ shak nyamia aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun a ban mǝnana Yahweh nǝ̀ tàrì ka.
\v 21 Sǝama ɓǝ̀ girkusǝunì ka ndanǝ ɓekǝ gìr mǝɓane arǝì, gbakǝre na, ko nte na, ko ndanǝ koya ulang gìr-ɓàná arǝì ka, kǝa pana gir'nkila nǝi aban Yahweh Ɓakuli mò ɗàng.
\v 22 Wu lì a là mǝnana wu ndakam ngga. Ko ɓwa ka nda aɓa ɓeami ko ɓoarnsari ka, nǝ̀ gandǝ li nyame, kǝla mana à nǝ̀ lì nyam ɓwachembe ko keran ngga.
\v 23 Sǝama wu kǝa lì nkile ɗàng; wu ɗārǝí a nzali kǝla mùr.
\c 16
\s1 Lamsan Yàlîmurû
\r (Puro 12:1-20; Ace Apǝris 23:4-8; Ɓal 28:16-25)
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ nacau ama:
\p 
\v 1 Wu tàr zongŋo Abip,\f + \fr 16:1 \fq zongŋo Abip: \ft (mana à tunǝi ɗǝm ama zongŋo Nisan ngga) nda zongŋo mǝdǝmbe a pǝlǝa aɓa tsadya mala azongŋo mala amǝ Ibǝru. Nda a kún gungpì; \xt Nehe 2:1; Est 3:7\xt*\f* mǝnana aɓalǝi ka wun nǝ̀ pàk Lamsan Yàlîmurû ace pè Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun gulo ka, acemǝnana aɓa zongŋo Abip sǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pusǝ wun aɓa Masar nǝ dú.\f + \fr 16:1 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pur 13:4; 23:15; 34:18\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 2 Dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ pà gìr'nkila mala Yàlîmurû aban Yahweh, Ɓakuli ma'wun, atà girkusǝu mǝnana a \f + \fr 16:2 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Ɓal 28:19\xt*\ft .\f*domwan mala andá, ko anzur, ko ambulpǝndǝa ka, a ban mǝnana Yahweh nǝ̀ tàrì ace tsǝk lùllǝì ɓǝ̀ duk kam ngga.
\v 3 Wu kǝa lì girlina mala Yàlîmurû nǝ bǝredi mǝnana à pè nǝ burè ka ɗàng. Wun nǝ̀ twal anongŋo tongno-nong-ɓari, wun nǝ̀ nggǝ li girline nǝ bǝredi mǝnana pànǝ burè arǝì raka; mǝno yì ulang bǝredi mana wu li lang wu nda aɓa tanni kǝla aguro a Masar, sǝ kǝla mana wu lì, lang wu ndarǝ puro wun nǝ̀ apî nzali Masar akaurǝa ka.\f + \fr 16:3 \ft Sǝni a: \xt Pur 12:11\xt*\ft .\f* Wu kǝ pak mǝnia yì gìr ka, ace mǝnana aɓa cili do-yilǝmu ma'wun ngga, ɓǝ̀ wu kǝ ɗenyinǝ pwari mǝnana wu nyingŋǝ̀nà nzali Masar nǝi ka.
\v 4 Ɓǝà kǝa kum kǝ bura mala kǝgir ko bǝti aɓa nzali ma'wun aɓalǝ nongŋo tongno-nong-ɓari mǝno ka ɗàng, sǝ pà wu nǝ̀ nying kǝ nyam girkusǝu mǝnana wu pana gir'nkila nǝi a pwarikpǝra mala pwari mǝdǝmbe mala Yàlîmurû ka, ɓǝ̀ nongŋo ban ɓǝ̀ kwarí ɗàng.
\v 5 Wu kǝa pà gir'nkila mala Yàlîmurû a koya là mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ɓǝ̀ wu duk kam ngga ɗàng.
\v 6 Ban mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tàrì, ace tsǝk lùllǝì ɓǝ̀ duk kam ngga, a kàm sǝ wun nǝ̀ pà gir'nkila mala Yàlîmurû, nǝ pwarikpǝra, a pwari-ká-ndwent, a kǝ bù-pwari mǝnana wu nyingŋǝ̀nà Masar nǝi ka.
\v 7 Nyame ka wu lambi, wu shè akǝ ban mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tàrì ka. Sǝ lang banfana ka wu nyare arǝ agumli ma'wun.
\v 8 Aɓalǝ anongŋo tongno-nong-mwashat ka, wun nǝ̀ lì bǝredi mǝnana à pe nǝ̀ burè raka. Tongno-nong-ɓaria pwari ka, nda pwari mǝnana wun nǝ̀ ramba a banɓwáná ace perì aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga; wu kǝa pàk kǝ túró a mǝno yì pwari ka ɗàng.
\s1 Lamsan mala Pwan Girɓaban
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ ne amǝ Isǝrayila cau ama:
\p 
\v 9 Wu ɓal alimo tongno-nong-ɓari, twal a pwari mǝnana wu tinata wal-mǝsa nǝi ka.
\v 10 Sǝ wun nǝ̀ pak lamsan mala Alimo aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ pagir mǝnana wu twalî ɓamur rǝwun wun nǝ̀ pá, sǝ karǝ arǝ tsǝkbu mana wu kúmô a ban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga.
\v 11 Sǝ wun nǝ̀ pàk banɓoarnado aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun atarǝ wun wunǝ amuna-burana andǝ amuna-mamǝna ma'wun, amǝ'túró-ɓala ma'wun aburana andǝ amamǝna. Sǝ amǝ'kà Lawi mǝnana arǝ alá ma'wun, andǝ amǝ'kúnɗàngna, andǝ akáwá andǝ amā-lú mǝnana aɓalǝ wun ngga, ɓǝà pàk banɓoarnado atà wun a mǝno yì lamsan, a ban mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tàrì ace tsǝk lùllǝì ɓǝ̀ duk kam ngga.
\v 12 Ɓalǝ wun ɓǝ̀ kasǝ ama, wu nda ka aguro ɗiɗyal a Masar, acemani ka wu tsǝkir wun, wu kpata amǝnia yì angguracau ka.
\s1 Lamsan mala Do aɓalǝ Agumli
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ nacau ama:
\p 
\v 13 Wun nǝ̀ pak Lamsan mala Do aɓalǝ Agumli aɓa nongŋo tongno-nong-ɓari, anzǝm mǝnana wu nyána mǝssa sǝ wu kàmna ɓǝlanggun anap, yì agirɓaban ma'wun mǝnana wu kum ngga.
\v 14 Wun nǝ̀ pak banɓoarnado aɓa lamsan ma'wun, wun wunǝ amuna-burana andǝ amuna-mamǝna ma'wun, andǝ amǝ'túró-ɓala ma'wun aburana andǝ amamǝna, andǝ amǝ'kà Lawi, andǝ amǝ'kúnɗàngna, andǝ akáwá andǝ amā-lú mǝnana aɓalǝ wun ngga.
\v 15 Wun nǝ̀ pak mǝnia yì lamsan ngga ace Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun aɓa nongŋo tongno-nong-ɓari a ban mǝnana Yahweh nǝ̀ tàrì ka. Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga nǝ̀ tsǝka wun bù aɓa kum girɓaban ma'wun kat, sǝ aɓalǝ atúró abú wun kat, sǝ banɓoarnado ma'wun ngga nǝ̀ lùmsǝo.
\p 
\v 16 Kusǝ tàrú a koya pǝlǝa, aburana ma'wun kat nǝ̀ yiu púp aɓadǝm Yahweh, yì Ɓakuli ma'wun, a ban mǝnana nǝ̀ tàrì ka; à nǝ̀ yiu ace Lamsan mala Bǝredi mǝnana Yis pà arǝì raka, ace Lamsan mala Alimo, sǝ ace Lamsan mala Do aɓalǝ Agumli. Kǝɓwa ɓǝkǝa yiua aɓadǝm Yahweh nǝ ɓabui atarǝì ɗàng.
\v 17 Koyan atà wun ngga, dumǝna púp nǝ̀ pà gìr mǝnana nǝ̀ gandǝi ka, kǝla mana karǝa arǝ tsǝkbu mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun mǝnana pà wun ngga.
\s1 Lǝmdǝ mǝsǝcau aɓa do wunǝ aɓwana
\sp Musa ne amǝ Isǝrayila cau ama:
\p 
\v 18 Wun nǝ̀ twal amǝ'ɓashi andǝ amǝbuno aɓa koya là ma'wun mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ngga, sǝ yià ka ɓǝà kǝ ɓashì aɓwana nǝ ɓashi mǝ'mǝsǝcaunì.
\v 19 Pà wu nǝ̀ pūrǝ ɓashi ɗàng. Pà wu nǝ̀ lǝmdǝ tàrban ɗang. Pà wu nǝ̀ ak pàbunǝnzali ɗang, acemǝnana pàbunǝnzali ka, kǝ gir mǝsǝ amǝ'sǝlǝe, sǝ kǝ pūrǝ acau mala amǝ'ɓealɓoarna.
\v 20 Wu ɓangŋatà pàk gìr mǝnana kat nǝ mǝsǝcau ka, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu dum nǝyilǝmu, sǝ wu lidǝmba nǝ do aɓa nzali liɓala mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ngga.
\s1 Peri mǝnana Ɓakuli pǝrban arǝì ka
\p 
\v 21 Wu kǝa pandǝî ɓamur rǝ wun kǝ nggun kǝla tondong mala Ashera,\f + \fr 16:21 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pur 34:13; Akas 6:25; 1Amur 14:15; 16:33; 2Amur 13:6; 17:16; 2Kpa 33:3\xt*\ft .\f* a nkanggari gyangŋan mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, mǝnana wun nǝ̀ ɓakkî ɓamur rǝ wun ngga ɗàng.
\v 22 Sǝ wu kǝa tsǝk kǝ kúnamúrú ace peri ɗàng! Yahweh ka kǝ ginǝce agir kǝla mǝnia.
\c 17
\s1 Apa'girnkila mǝnana Ɓakuli ɓinǝcea ka
\sp Musa pǝlǝa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 1 Pà wu nǝ̀ pà gìr'nkila aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, nǝ jamnda, ko nzur mana kum kǝ mǝɓane arǝì ko ɓè bare rǝì kiɗiki ka ɗàng; mǝno ka gìr'ɓeami na aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun.\f + \fr 17:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pǝris 3:1,6; 9:2-3; 21:17-23; 22:17-25; 23:12; Ɓal 19:2; Nggur 15:21; Mal 1:8; Ib 9:14; 1Bit 1:19; 2Bit 3:14\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 2 Ɓǝ̀ à kum ɓwabura ko ɓwama aɓalǝ wun a là mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun, aban pak gìr mǝɓike a sǝne mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, sǝ ɓunce Kùrcau male,\f + \fr 17:2 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Nggur 31:16\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 3 sǝ ɓwe warina a kpata aɓea aɓakuli andǝ peri aban pwari, andǝ zongŋo, ko anlero a bumkuli, mana ǝn pǝrban nǝma ɓǝà kǝa pè ɗàng,\f + \fr 17:3 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Nggur 4:19; 2Amur 23:5; Ayu 31:26-28; Ang 148:3-6\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 4 sǝ wu okce, ko à bangga wun ama ɓeɓwa pàk ulang amǝnia yì agir ka, wu bǝlkiɓalǝ acê pepè. Ɓǝ̀ do ama mǝsǝcau na, sǝ mbak-kàngkàng à pàngŋǝ̀nà ulang gìr ɓeami kǝla mǝno a Isǝrayila ka,
\v 5 wu twal ɓwabure, ko ɓwame, mǝnana pàk mǝnia yì túró-ɓikea ka, wu pusǝì a kun-nggealà, wu ɓukki nǝ atali, ɓǝ̀ wǔ.
\v 6 Ɓwa mǝnana à kasǝi wi ɓashi-lú ka, à nǝ̀ wal-luí ɓǝ̀ aɓwana ɓari ko tàrú nakun amur cê ama anggo sǝ gìrnî pàk ka; sǝama à pà nǝ̀ wal-lú ɓwa aɓa kpata nakun mala ɓwa mwashat ɗàng.
\v 7 Amǝ'nakún ngga à nda mǝnana à nǝ̀ tita ɓukki mǝno yì ɓwa ka ace wal-luí, sǝ nǝnzǝ́mò ka acili aɓwana kat nǝ̀ dapi andǝia aban ɓukki, ace wal-luí. Anggo sǝ wun nǝ̀ pusǝ ɓealɓikea ɓǝ̀ purî ɓalǝ wun.
\s1 Acau mǝkwane
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 8 Ɓǝ̀ ɓè cau lo mǝnana kasǝ ɓashi male kwanba wun, kǝla cau wal-lú mǝnana à gandǝ gaute ama à pè kpakpak ko à pè sǝ pà nǝ eare mala ɓwa ɗàng; ko mala kasǝ ɓashi a nre ka aɓwana ɓari amur yana ateà mwashat nda mǝtala ɓè gìr mana koyan ateà kǝ na ama male na; ko cau mala tsǝk npenye na sǝ kasǝ ɓashi mala cê kwanba wun ama ko turturo na ko à pè kpakpak ka, wu lo wu kyan nǝi a ban mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ bang ama ɓǝ̀ wu kyan nǝi kàm ngga.
\v 9 Akano ka wun nǝ̀ nggá nongsǝ cê aban apǝris, amǝ'kà Lawi, sǝ aban ɓwa mǝnana nda murǝm-ɓashi a bàkú mǝno ka. Yia na à nǝ̀ ok ɓá cê, sǝ à nǝ̀ kasǝ ɓashi ka.
\v 10 Dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ pàk nggearǝ gìr mǝnana ɓashi kasǝa a ban mǝnana Yahweh tsǝk ama, ɓǝà pàk ɓashi kàm ngga. Sǝ wun nǝ̀ dum nǝ tsǝkiru arǝ kpata cau mana kat à kània wun ngga.
\v 11 Wu pàk koman ka amur gìr mǝnana à kània wun, ko à ear amurí, à kasǝcau ama ɓǝà pè ka. Wu kǝa na ama, wun nǝ̀ nggaɗi kasǝ-ɓashi mǝnana à hamba wun ngga a koya njar ka ɗàng.
\v 12 Ɓwa mǝnana kat lǝmdǝ múrcandǝa, ɓinǝ okî pǝris mana kǝ cam aban pak túró ace aɓwana aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga, dumǝna púp ɓǝà wal ɓwe ɓǝ̀ wǔ. Anggo sǝ wun nǝ pusǝ gir ɓealɓikea aɓalǝ amǝ Isǝrayila.
\v 13 Anggo sǝ koyana mǝnana kat okce mǝnia yì gìr ka, ɓangciu nǝ̀ pàkki wi sǝ pà nǝ̀ lǝmdǝ múrcandǝa ɗang.
\s1 Anzongcau mala twal murǝm
\sp Musa pǝlǝa banggia wia ama:
\p 
\v 14 Lang wu kutina aɓa nzali mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun, wu angŋǝni pǝlǝna ma'wun, sǝ wu dumǝna kàm, sǝ wu pàk ɗenyicau ama, <<Sǝm nǝ̀ twal ɓwa ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm amur sǝm, kǝla mana anzali mǝnana kat à kàrì sǝm à pakkiyi ka,>>
\v 15 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ eara wun ɓǝ̀ wu kum murǝm, sǝama wu sǝlǝ ama, ɓwa mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ twal ka, nda wun nǝ̀ tsǝì ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm amur wun ngga. Ɓwa mǝnana wun nǝ̀ tsǝì ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm amur wun ngga nǝ̀ duk mwashat atà amǝ'eam wun, ɓwa Isǝrayila. Wu kǝa twal bǝri-ɓwa mǝnana ɓwa Isǝrayila na raka ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm amur wun ɗàng.
\v 16 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ do ama, murǝm ngga pà nǝ̀ ramba apǝr pas ace ɓamúrì, ko nǝ̀ tasǝ aɓwana ɓǝà nyar a Masar ɓǝà kya yinǝ apǝr pas kàm ɗàng. Yahweh ka bangŋǝ́nà wun ama, <<Wu kǝa na ama, wun nǝ̀ nyar a njar mǝno ɗǝm ɗàng.>>
\v 17 Sǝ yì murǝm ngga, ɓǝkǝa na ama, nǝ̀ alita ɓamúrì amamǝna pas ɗàng. Acemǝnana, alki amamǝna pas ka nǝ̀ twal ɓabumi, nǝ̀ nying okî Yahweh. Sǝ ɓǝ̀kǝa na gbal ama, nǝ̀ rambì ɓamúrì gǝna kpǝm mala bolo-zǝnariya andǝ bolo-njengǝlan ɗàng.
\p 
\v 18 Sǝ lang murǝm yi eauna, dumǝna amúr buno mala domurǝm male ka, nǝ̀ tsǝa ɓǝà pwan cau mala mǝnia yì Nggurcau mana nda a bu apǝris amǝkà Lawi ka, ɓǝà gilǝî wi aɓa malǝmce, ɓǝ̀ duk male.
\v 19 Nǝ̀ pà a baní sǝ nǝ̀ nggâ ɓalli a koya pwari, bà masǝlǝata do male nǝyilǝmu, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ kànì ɓanggi Yahweh Ɓakuli male, ɓǝ̀ kpata acau mala mǝnia yì nggurcau andǝ anzongcau ka, sǝ ɓǝ̀ kǝ peǎ;
\v 20 anggo ka pà nǝ̀ dum nǝ gusǝlǝmúrû, ko nǝ̀ twal ɓamúrì kǝla kútì acili aɓwana male ɗàng, sǝ pà nǝ̀ nying kpata anzongcau mala Ɓakuli aɓa koya njar ɗàng, ace mǝnana yì andǝ amǝkè ka ɓǝà lidǝmba nǝ yálban kǝla amurǝma arǝ anza pas aɓa Isǝrayila.
\c 18
\s1 Apagir ace apǝris andǝ amǝ'lawi
\r (Ɓal 18:8-32)
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 1 Apǝris, mana yia kat à nda a tàu mala Lawi ka, à pànǝ kum ɓekǝ nzali liɓala ko kǝ bare mana à kasǝia wia ɓǝ̀ duk girkuma malea aɓa Isǝrayila ka ɗàng. Yià ka à nǝ̀ lì apagir girlina mǝnana aɓwana yinǝia ace Yahweh ka.
\v 2 À pà nǝ̀ kum ɓè kǝgìr liɓala atà amǝ'eambia ɗàng. Yahweh ka nda gìr'liɓala malea, kǝla mana bangŋǝnia wia ka.
\p 
\v 3 Lang aɓwana yinǝ agir'nkila kǝla jamnda, ko nzur andǝ mbulpǝndǝa ka, abare nyama mǝnana nda ace apǝris ka, à nda ka: nkpamtari, andǝ atakiri ɓari, andǝ agir-bumi.
\v 4 Aɓǝlagir mǝdǝmbe mala mǝssa ma'wun, andǝ bǝsa mùr-anap ma'wun, andǝ bǝsa mùrú olif ma'wun, andǝ nyang nzur mana wu tita mwe arǝ anzur ma'wun ngga, wun nǝ̀ pè pǝris.
\v 5 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga tarna Lawi, andǝ amuni, andǝ amǝkè aɓalǝ atau mala amǝ Isǝrayila kat, ace mǝnana ɓǝà duk amǝ'lidǝmba nǝ aɓwana a ban-peri, aɓa lullǝ Yahweh a koya pwari ka.
\p 
\v 6 Ɓǝ̀ Ɓwa'Lawi nying là male aɓalǝ alá mana aɓa Isǝrayila, sǝ earce nǝ̀ ká a koya là mǝnana kat Yahweh nǝ̀ tàr ka,
\v 7 yì ka nǝ̀ gandǝ pak túróperi aɓa lullǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli male, kǝla mana aɓî amǝ'Lawi mǝnana akano à kǝ pak túróperi aɓadǝm Yahweh ka.
\v 8 Yì ɗǝm ngga, nǝ̀ gandǝ kum kāmbe mǝmwashati atà aɓî, mala gìr mǝnana nǝ̀ lì ka, kat andǝ amani ama kumǝna boalo aɓa makki agirkuma mala tárria ka.
\s1 Nunkiru arǝ pakkiagir mala amǝ'kpata-alú
\sp Musa pǝlǝa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 9 Lang wu yina, wu kutina a nzali mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ngga, pà wun nǝ̀ kànì pàkkiagir ɓeami mala aɓwapǝndǝa mala anzali mǝno ka ɗàng.
\v 10 Ɓǝà kǝa kum kǝɓwa aɓalǝ wun mana nǝ̀ kánǝ muni muna-ɓwabura ko muna-ɓwama ɓǝà pisǝi a bǝsa ace pagìr, ko mǝ'ɓángnǝ́-ɓángna, ko mǝ'sǝna nǝ bangŋo mala akukwar, ko mǝ'na gìr mǝnana nǝ̀ kumban ngga, ko mǝ'pàkki agir nggár,
\v 11 ko mǝ'pàkki aɓuri, ko mǝ'tunǝ akukwar, ko mǝ'monzǝo, ko mǝɗikalú ka ɗàng.
\v 12 Ɓwa mǝnana kat kǝ pak amǝnia yì agir ka, ɓwe dumǝna gìr'ɓeami aban Yahweh. Nda atàcau mala pàkki amǝnia yì agir'ɓeami malea ka, sǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ bwala wun kàm, wun nǝ̀ pǝr aɓwapǝndǝa mǝno ka, à nǝ̀ nyingga wun nzali.
\v 13 Sǝama, dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ duk amǝ'ɗwanyicau arǝu aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun.
\v 14 Aɓwapǝndǝa mǝnana wun nǝ̀ ak nzali arǝia ka, à kǝ kpata acau mala amǝ'pakki agir nggár, andǝ ɓángnǝ́-ɓángna. Sǝama wun ngga, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun eara wun ama ɓǝ̀ wu pàk anggo ɗàng.
\s1 Bǝsa mǝɓangnǝa kǝla Musa
\p 
\v 15 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ loasǝ ɓwa aɓalǝ wun, ɓè mǝɓangnǝa kǝla mim, akǝ ɓalǝ aɓwana ma'wun, amǝ Isǝrayila. Dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ oki wi.
\v 16 Mǝnia ka nda gìr mǝnana wu ɗice aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, a Horep ka, a pwari ramba abanɓwáná lang wu bang ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ sǝm kǝa ok gi Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm ɗǝm, ko ɓǝ̀ sǝm ɓǝsǝlǝ sǝn nggea bǝsa mǝnia ɗǝm ɗàng, ɓǝ̀ ana raka sǝm nǝ̀ wǔ.>>
\p 
\v 17 Pǝlǝa Yahweh banggam ama, <<Cau mǝno à ne ka, ceni ka ɓoaro.
\v 18 Mǝ nǝ loasǝia wia mǝɓangnǝa kǝla we, àkǝ ɓalǝ aɓwana malea, yia amǝ Isǝrayila, sǝ mǝ nǝ tsǝk acau mem a kúni, sǝ nǝ̀ banggia wia gìr mǝnana kat mǝ nǝ ne wi nǝma, ɓǝ̀ banggi wia ka.
\v 19 Ɓwa mǝnana kat ɓinǝ kpata acau mem mǝnana mǝɓangnǝa man nǝ̀ bang aɓa lullǝàm ngga, mim nǝ nggearǝam, mǝ nǝ tsǝì ɓǝ̀ banggam tǝr ɓinǝ okiru male.
\v 20 Sǝama, mǝɓangnǝa mǝnana twalî ɓamúrì nǝ̀ nacau aɓa lullǝàm, cau mana mǝ nda ǝn tasǝi ɓǝ̀ ne raka, ko nacau aɓa lullǝ aɓea aɓakuli ka, mǝno yì mǝɓangnǝa ka dumǝna púp ɓǝà wal-luí.>>
\sp Musa pǝlǝa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 21 Yakǝla wun nǝ̀ ɗì ɓamur rǝ wun ama, <<Lang sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ sǝlǝ ama, cau mana mǝɓangnǝa na ka, pur nǝban Yahweh ɗàng?>>
\v 22 Ɓǝ̀ mǝɓangnǝa nacau aɓa lullǝ Yahweh, sǝ ceni yiu yi lumsǝ ɗang, ko duk mǝsǝcau raka, wun nǝ̀ sǝlǝa ma Yahweh, nama kǝ cau anggo ɗàng. Lǝmdǝ ama, mǝno yì cau mǝɓangnǝa na ka twalkicau mala ɓamúrì na, acemani ka, wu kǝa ɓanggi wi ɗàng.
\c 19
\s1 Alá mala ban àwá
\sp Musa ne amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 1 Anzǝm mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kiɗikina aɓwapǝndǝa mǝnana malanǝ̀ pà wun nzali malea, sǝ lang wu angŋǝni arǝia, wu dumǝna aɓalǝ alá andǝ aɓala malea ka,
\v 2 dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ tàrrî ɓamur rǝ wun alá tàrú aɓa nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ɓǝ̀ wu duk kam ngga.
\v 3 Dumǝna ama wun nǝ̀ tsǝk anjargula ace ɓamurǝ wun, sǝ wu gau nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pa wun ɓǝ̀ duk girkuma ma'wun ngga, arǝ abanì tàrú, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ kǝɓwa turturo arǝ ɓí sǝ wal-luí ka, ɓǝ̀ ɓangŋa ɓǝ̀ dǝshi ban mǝnana nda tù a baní ka, ace àwá male.
\p 
\v 4 Mǝnia yì nzongcau ka nda ace koya ɓwa mǝnana pè kpak sǝ wal-lú ɓi raka, sǝ ɓinǝmǝsǝi nǝ ɓinǝe ɗiɗyal gbal ɗang; ɓwe ka nǝ̀ gandǝ ɓangŋa nǝ̀ ká aɓa mwashat atà alá mǝnia ka nǝ̀ nggá duk kam ace amsǝ yilǝmi.
\v 5 Nda kǝla ani, ɓǝ̀ ɓwa wari andǝ ɓì, a ndà-nggun à nǝ̀ nggá kasǝki anggun, sǝ lang loasǝ bero nǝ̀ kwar nggun ngga, mǝsǝ bero puro arǝ garè sǝ ɓù ɓì wal-luí. Ɓwê ɓǝ̀ ɓangŋa ɓǝ̀ kùtí aɓa mwashat atà alá mǝno ka ɓǝ̀ amsǝ yilǝmi.
\v 6 Ɓǝ̀ ana raka ɓǝla mala ɓwa mǝno à wal-luí ka, nǝ̀ lo aɓa pǐ mala bumlulla nǝ̀ pǝrta ɓwa mǝno wal-lu ka. Sǝ ɓǝ̀ njargula sau kǝ̀rkǝ́r ka, nǝ̀ nggá kasǝmúrí nǝ̀ wal-luí, kat andǝ amani ama ɓoaro ɓǝà wal-luí raka, acemǝnana yì ka ɓinǝmǝsǝ ɓi ɗiɗyal ɗàng.
\v 7 Nda gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ ǝn bangga wun nǝma ɓǝ̀ wu tàrrî ɓamur rǝ wun alá tàrú ka.
\p 
\v 8 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun tangsǝna nzong-nzali ma'wun gulǝna, kǝla mǝnana kánbì aká wun, sǝ pàna wun nzali mana kat pàcau aban aká wun ama nǝ̀ pea wia,
\v 9 sǝ ɓǝ̀ wu kpanatà anzongcau mǝnia kat ǝn nggǝ pà wun yalung, wun nǝ̀ earce Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, wun nǝ̀ nggǝ kpata anjar male ka, wun nǝ̀ tàr aɓea alá àwá kam ɗǝm tàrú amur amǝno tàrú ka.
\v 10 Anggo ka, nkila mala mǝ'kunpwasǝa pà nǝ̀ sukki a nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga ɗàng, sǝ nkila mala amǝ'kunpwasǝa ka à pà nǝ̀ ɗìce a bu kǝɓwa atà wun ɗàng.
\p 
\v 11 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ do ama nda ace ɓinǝmǝsǝu sǝ ɓwa kùmsǝî ɓì, pǝlǝa lo arǝì wal-luí, sǝ lo nǝ mire o a mwashat atà alá àwá mǝnia ka,
\v 12 aɓwana-mǝgule mala là mala mǝnia yì mǝ'wal-lú ka, ɓǝà tasǝ aɓwana ɓǝà kya bwali ɓǝà pusǝì a ban mǝno, ɓǝà yì ramtè a bu aɓǝla mala ɓwa mǝnana à wal-luí ka; yià gbal ka ɓǝà wal-luí.
\v 13 Wu kǝa sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr male ɗàng. Dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ lak nzali Isǝrayila ɓǝ̀ purî ɓá kúmcàu mala sukki nkila mala amǝ'kunpwasǝa, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ agir kyanba wun pepè.
\s1 Nunkiru arǝ gǝshi nzong
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 14 Lang wu kutina a nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga, a pà wunǝ tusǝ nzong mala nzali mala ɓio mǝmurkala ɗang, yì nzong mǝnana aká wun akdǝmba à pandǝnì ace lǝmdǝ ban nzali liɓala mǝnana à kasǝia wia ka.
\s1 Nggurcau amur amǝ'nakún
\p 
\v 15 Nakún mala ɓwa mwashat kārǝa à nǝ̀ pàktúró nǝi ace kum ɓekǝ ɓwa nǝ pàk mǝɓike ɗàng, ko ɓǝ̀ ya cauɓikea na ɓwe pàk ka. Kaniama à nǝ̀ bwal ɓwa ama pàk mǝɓike ka, dumǝna púp ama amǝ'nakún nakam ɓari ko tàrú.
\v 16 Ɓǝ̀ mǝ'bumkpǝmna yiu nǝ nakún mala tsǝki ɓwa cau arǝì ama pàk mǝɓane ka,
\v 17 aɓwana mǝnia mana makgìr kùtí a nrea ka, yià kǝm à nǝ̀ cam aɓadǝm Yahweh, aɓadǝm apǝris andǝ amǝ'ɓashi mǝnana à nda a buno-túró a bàkú mǝno ka.
\v 18 Amǝ'ɓashi ɓǝà gya atà kusǝ cê pepè, sǝ ɓǝ̀ à bwal mǝ'nakún ama mǝ'nyir na, sǝ yina nǝ nakún nyir amur mǝ'eambi ka,
\v 19 wu pàkki wi gìr mǝnana tsǝa a bumi ama ɓǝà pàkkî ɓwa mǝno tsǝki wi cau arǝì ka. Anggo sǝ wun nǝ̀ esǝki ɓealɓikea aɓalǝ wun.
\v 20 Acili aɓwana nǝ̀ okce, sǝ ɓangciu nǝ̀ pàkkia wia, sǝ à pà nǝ̀ nyare à nǝ̀ pàk ulang mǝno yì ɓealɓikea ka aɓalǝ wun ɗǝm ɗàng.
\v 21 Aɓa ulang cau kǝla mǝnia ka, wu kǝa lǝmdǝ mǝsǝswatǝr ɗàng: yilǝmu a kúnì yilǝmu, mǝsǝu a kúnì mǝsǝu, minǝu a kúnì minǝu, bu a kúnì bu, sǝ kusǝu a kúnì kusǝu.
\c 20
\s1 Anggurcau mala lwa
\sp Musa ne amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 1 Lang wu puro wun nǝ̀ o a lwa arǝ aɓiwun amǝbura, sǝ wu sǝn apǝr, andǝ awaru-pǝr, andǝ amǝ'lwa mǝnana à lakkì à kútì ma'wun ngga, cè ɓangciu pàkka wun arǝia ɗàng; acemǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun mana pusǝ wun wu purî ɓá Masar ka, nda atà wun.
\v 2 Kaniama wun nǝ̀ o a munǝo ka, pǝris nǝ̀ puro nǝ̀ cam aɓadǝm amǝ'lwa sǝ nǝ̀ banggia wia cau.
\v 3 Nǝ̀ bang ama, <<Wu kwakikir wun, wun amǝ Isǝrayila, yalung ngga wu nda wu kǝ sung aban ká munǝo arǝ aɓiwun amǝbura ka; cè ɓabum wun ɓungi ɗang, ɓangciu ɓǝ̀ kǝa pakka wun ɗàng, sǝ wu kǝa dǝurǝo ko múr wun kàr wun acea ɗàng.
\v 4 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga, nda mana nda atà wun nǝ̀ munǝo ace wun arǝ aɓiwun amǝbura, ace pà wun limurǝm ngga.>>
\p 
\v 5 Pǝlǝa amǝ'pagara mala amǝ'lwa nǝ̀ banggi amǝ'lwa cau ama:
\pi1 Ɓǝ̀ kǝɓwa kàm aɓalǝ wun ɓak bǝsa ɓala sǝ malaká pè Ɓakuli a buì raka, ɓwê ɓǝ̀ nyare ɓǝ̀ o a là. Pà nǝ̀ ɓoaro wu wú sǝ ɓeɓwa ɓǝ̀ yi kúti aɓa bǝsa ɓala mò ɗàng.
\pi1 
\v 6 Ɓǝ̀ kǝɓwa pandǝ anggun anap sǝ malaká lì ɓǝle raka, ɓǝ̀ nyare ɓǝ̀ o a là, ace mana ɓǝkǝa wǔ a kún munǝo sǝ ɓeɓwa nǝ̀ yia lì ɓǝle ka ɗàng.
\pi1 
\v 7 Ɓǝ̀ kǝɓwa purna'amur ɓwama sǝ malaká isǝi raka, ɓǝ̀ nyare ɓǝ̀ o a là, ace mana ɓǝkǝa wǔ a kún munǝo sǝ ɓeɓwa nǝ̀ yia twali ka ɗàng.
\p 
\v 8 Amǝ'pagara mala amǝ'lwa nǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ banggi amǝ'lwa cau ama:
\pi1 Ɓǝ̀ ɓangciu kǝ pakkì kǝɓwa ko ɓabumi ɓungi ka, ɓǝ̀ ɓwê nyare ɓǝ̀ o a là, ace mǝnana ɓǝkǝa ɓungi ɓabum acili amǝ'lwa kǝla male ɗàng.
\p 
\v 9 Lang amǝ'pagara mala amǝ'lwa malna ne amǝ'lwa amǝnia yì acau ka, pǝlǝa à nǝ̀ twal amǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mǝnana à nǝ̀ dupî amǝ'lwa a dǝmba ka.
\p 
\v 10 Lang wu bwalna là mǝnana wu kǝ oa munǝo arǝì ka, wu tite nǝ tasǝia wia cau ɓǝà nongsǝmúrià aɓata wun ace dotarǝu.
\v 11 Ɓǝ̀ à eare à nongsǝmúrià aɓata wun sǝ à mǝmba wun kún nggea-là malea ka, aɓwana mǝnana kat a lě ka, à nǝ̀ duk aguro ma'wun.
\v 12 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ à ginǝ nongsǝmúrià aɓata wun aɓa dotarǝu, sǝ a kún mani ka à nǝ̀ lo ace yiu arǝ wun a munǝo ka, wu gumbǝli mǝno yì nggea-là ka nǝ amǝ'lwa ma'wun.
\v 13 Sǝ lang Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pana wun mǝno yì nggea-là a ɓabù wun, wu angŋǝ́nì ka, wu wal-lú koya ɓwabura mǝnana aɓalǝi ka.
\v 14 Sǝama amamǝna, andǝ amuna mǝkeke, andǝ agirkusǝu, andǝ agir mǝnana kat aɓa mǝno yì nggea-là ka, wu pwania ɓǝà duk kume-lwa ace ɓamur wun. Wu ok ta banɓoarnado mala gǝna-lwa mǝnana wu pwani arǝ aɓiwun amǝbura ka. Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pana wunì.
\v 15 Anggo sǝ wun nǝ̀ pangnǝ anggea-là mǝnana kat à nda kuko nǝ wun, à pà aɓalǝ anggea-là mala aɓwapǝndǝa mana akani raka.
\p 
\v 16 Sǝ mala anggea-là mala aɓwana mǝnia mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pa wunia ɓǝà duk gir liɓala ma'wun ngga, pà wun nǝ̀ ɗeki ɓè kǝgir mǝnana kǝ lin'ueo ka ɓǝ̀ au ɗàng;
\v 17 wu tària ace twaltea kat-kat: amǝ'Hitti, andǝ amǝ'Amor, andǝ amǝ'Kan'ana, andǝ amǝ'Periz, andǝ amǝ'Hivi, andǝ amǝ'Jebus, kǝla mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun tsǝka wun ama ɓǝ̀ wu pè ka.
\v 18 Ɓǝ̀ wu ɗekia nǝyilǝmu ka, à nǝ̀ kania wun kpata agir ɓeami mǝnana kat à kǝ pe aɓa peri aban aɓakuli malea ka; sǝ anggo ka wun nǝ̀ pak cauɓikea aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun.
\p 
\v 19 Lang wu gumbǝli nggea-là nǝ munǝo, sǝ ko ɓǝ̀ sau lang wu nda aban munǝo arǝ nggea-lê ace mana wun nǝ̀ é ka, wu kǝa kútí arǝ anggun mala nggea-lê nǝ abero aban kasǝkia ɗàng. Wun nǝ̀ gandǝ tūki aɓǝla anggunì ace lia, sǝama, wu kǝa makkia ɗàng. Anggun aɓa patal ka aɓwapǝndǝa na le, mana wun nǝ̀ ká arǝia nǝ gumbǝliban mala lwa ka?
\v 20 Anggun mǝnana wu sǝlǝ ama à kǝ pa ɓǝlea ɗàng sǝ à kǝ lia raka, kǝ à nda wun nǝ̀ gandǝ kasǝkia ace gballì anggun-eauwe andǝ abancame mǝ'dāhre ace eauwe amur sheran mala nggea-là mǝnana wu gumbǝli nǝ lwa sǝ kǝ munǝ arǝ wun ngga, she ɓǝ̀ kpana ka.
\c 21
\s1 Lú mǝnana à súrǝ̀ mǝ'wàlé raka
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 1 Ɓǝ̀ ndo ama à wal-lú ɓwa sǝ à yi kum luí aban nongŋo a patal, aɓa nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pà wun, sǝ kǝɓwa súrǝ̀ ya ɓwe nani wal-luî raka,
\v 2 aɓwana-mǝgule andǝ amǝ'ɓashi ma'wun ɓǝà yi kārǝki ɓǝà sǝnì, ya là na tù nǝ ban mǝnana à kum mǝno yì lú kàm ngga.
\v 3 Aɓwana-mǝgule mala là mǝnana nda tù nǝ ban mǝnana à kum lú kàm ngga, ɓǝà bwal mǝ'jamnda mǝnana à malaká pàngŋǝ̀nà túró nǝi a rya ko à kùri wi nggun-rya raka,
\v 4 ɓǝà kyan nǝi a ɓangŋaban mǝnana mùr kǝ ɓang kàm, sǝ à rikrya kam ko à ɓealɓeale kam raka, sǝ ɓǝà ɓun myali kàm a mǝno yì ɓangŋaban.
\v 5 Sǝ apǝris, amuna-burana amǝkà Lawi ɓǝà yiu a dǝmba, acemǝnana à nda ka aɓwana mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun tàrnia ɓǝà pàkki wi túró sǝ ɓǝà tsǝkbu aɓa lullǝ Yahweh ka, sǝ ɓǝà ɓashì aɓwana amur acau mala loasǝkiaban andǝ walkiban ngga.
\v 6 Sǝ aɓwana-mǝgule kat mala là mǝnana nda tù a ban mǝno à kum luî kam ngga, à nǝ̀ lak abuia amur mǝ'jamnda mǝnana à ɓun myali a ɓangŋaban ngga,
\v 7 sǝ à nǝ̀ na ama, <<Bù sǝm nǝ̀ sukki mǝnia yì nkila ka ɗàng, sǝ mǝsǝ sǝm sǝn ɓwa mǝnana sukki nkile ka ɗàng.
\v 8 We Yahweh, ak mǝnia yì shawuɗiban ngga a bù aɓwana mô, amǝ Isǝrayila, yia mǝnana a akmúria ka; kǝa tsǝk bafe mala sukki nkila mala mǝ'kunpwasǝa mǝnia ka, ɓǝ̀ ueo aɓalǝ aɓwana mô, amǝ Isǝrayila ɗàng.>> Anggo sǝ sukki nkila mǝnia ka à nǝ̀ shawuɗì.
\v 9 Aɓa pak gìr mǝnana nda jik a sǝne mala Yahweh ka, à nǝ̀ lak wun, wun nǝ̀ gǝshi bafe mala sukki nkila mala mǝ'kunpwasǝa.
\s1 Anzongcau amur amamǝna mǝnana à bwalia a kún munǝo ka
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 10 Lang Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pàna wun limurǝm amúr aɓiwun amǝbura mǝnana wu wari a munǝo arǝia sǝ wu bwalkia kǝla aguro,
\v 11 sǝ we ka, a sǝn ɓwama mǝɓoarnsarì mǝnana ceì ɓoarô sǝ a earce ama awu nǝ twali ɓǝ̀ duk māmó ka,
\v 12 twali umnǝi a ɓala mò; sǝama ɓwame ka à nǝ̀ mwaki wi nyang ɓamúrí, à nǝ̀ kasǝki wi ankaulabui andǝ ankaulakusǝi,
\v 13 sǝ agir-nggūrǝu mǝnana à nda arǝì lang à bwali ka, ɓǝ̀ swária. Yì ka nǝ̀ ueo a ɓala mò, nǝ̀ ɓua-lú tárrí andǝ nggé zongŋo mwashat; anzǝm mǝno ka sǝ awu nǝ kúti abani kǝla burí, sǝ yi ka nǝ̀ duk māmó.
\v 14 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ nǝnzǝ́mò ceì yi shirio ka, ɗeki ɓǝ̀ o a ban mǝnana earkiyice ka. Sǝama a pà wunǝ mé ace kum boalo ɗang, sǝ a pà wunǝ pàngnǝi kǝla guro ɗàng, acemǝnana a súrǝ́nà rǝì kǝla ɓwama.
\s1 Gara mǝnana muna-dǝmba muna-ɓwabura ndanǝi ka
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 15 Ɓǝ̀ ɓwabura ka ndanǝ amamǝna ɓari, man mwashat ka kǝ earce, sǝ ɓè man ngga kǝ earce raka, sǝ yia kǝm ngga à ɓǝlǝni wi amuna, sǝ ɓǝ̀ muna-dǝmba muna-ɓwabura ka nda mala mā-gírí ka,
\v 16 a pwari mana ɓwabure longŋǝna nǝ̀ gapi amuni agirkuma male ace mǝnana koyan ateà ka ɓǝ̀ kum gìr'liɓala ka, ɓǝ̀ kǝa na ama nǝ̀ lǝmdǝ tàrban nǝ̀ twal kāmbe mǝnana mala muna-dǝmba na ka nǝ̀ pè muna mala mā-eare, a kún mǝnana muna mala mā-gírí na nǝ̀ pè wi ka, ɗàng, acemǝnana nda muna-dǝmba.
\v 17 Dumǝna púp nǝ̀ ak muna mala mā-gírí, kǝla muna-dǝmba male, ɓǝ̀ pè wi kāmbe ɓari mala agirkuma male kat. Mǝno yì muna ka nda tita lǝmdǝ rǝcandǝa mala kārǝ́-ɓwa mala tárrí ka. Gìr mǝnana mala muna-dǝmba na ka male na.
\s1 Muna mǝnana kǝ mgbicau ka
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 18 Ɓǝ̀ ɓwa ka ndanǝ muna mǝ'murcandǝe, mǝ'mgbicau mǝnana kǝ okî tárrí andǝ ngge ɗàng, sǝ ko ɓǝ̀ à kwarkiri ka kǝ falǝnǝia raka,
\v 19 tárrí andǝ ngge ɓǝà bwali, ɓǝà kyan nǝi aban aɓwana-mǝgule mala là malea, a kún nggea-là, ban dapi mala là mǝnana ndakam nǝdo ka.
\v 20 À nǝ̀ ne aɓwana-mǝgule mala là male ama, <<Mǝnia yì muna ma'sǝm ngga mǝ'murcandǝa na, sǝ mǝ'mgbicau na; kǝ oaka sǝm ɗàng. Mǝ'lǐgula na, sǝ mǝ'walo-mba na.>>
\v 21 Sǝ aburana kat mala là male nǝ̀ ɓukki nǝ atali ɓǝ̀ wú. Anggo sǝ wun nǝ̀ pusǝ ɓealɓikea a ɓalǝ wun, sǝ amǝ Isǝrayila kat nǝ̀ ǒ, à nǝ̀ dumnǝ ɓangciu.
\s1 Ɓwa mǝnana à gyari a nggun ngga à súni
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 22 Ɓǝ̀ ɓwa pak cauɓikea mǝnana kārǝa ɓǝà wal-luí, sǝ à wal-luí, sǝ wu gyari a nggun ngga,
\v 23 wu kǝa ɗeki luí ɓǝ̀ ueo a nggun ba kwaro mala ban ɗang. Dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ tsǝì akǝ mǝno yi pwari ka, acemǝnana ɓwa mana à gyari a nggun ngga ndanǝ suban mala Ɓakuli amurí. Wu lùmsǝ mǝno yì lú ka, ace mǝnana nzali ma'wun mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pà wun ngga ɓǝkǝa duk gìr'ɓeami ɗàng.
\c 22
\s1 Aɓea anzongcau
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 1 Ɓǝ̀ a sǝn ndá, ko mbul, ko nzur mala ɓio ɓwaro kǝ u ka, cè a burice ɗàng, bwali nyesǝî mǝtale.
\v 2 Ɓǝ̀ mǝtale pà a bano tù ɗàng, ko a súrǝ̀ mǝtale raka, bwal girkusǝunì, yinǝi a ɓala mò, kya kùrì a bano wu kǝ ɗenyinǝi. Lang mǝtale yina aban alte ka, nyesǝì pè wi.
\v 3 Anggo gbal sǝ awu nǝ pangnǝ mǝdambǝriso, ko gìr'nggūrǝu, andǝ koya gìr mala ɓio mǝnana ɓwar arǝì sǝ a kumi ka. Kǝa ɓinǝ pàk gìr mǝnana ɓoaro wu pak ka ɗàng.
\p 
\v 4 Ɓǝ̀ a sǝn mǝdambǝriso ko ndá mala ɓio kpa a njargula ka, cè a burice ɗàng. Bwalì wì wu loasǝi amúr akusǝi.
\p 
\v 5 Ɓwama ɓǝkǝa oasǝ gìr'nggūrǝu mala ɓwabura ɗang, sǝ ɓwabura gbal ka ɓǝkǝa oasǝ gìr'nggūrǝu mala ɓwama ɗàng; mǝnia yì gìr ka gìr'ɓeami na aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun.
\p 
\v 6 Ɓǝ̀ a yakiarǝ ndà-nyal amúr nggun, ko a nzali, nǝ amuni ko ankí aɓalǝi, andǝ nggeâ aban nongŋo amúrià ka, a pà wunǝ san nggeâ andǝ amuni ɗàng;
\v 7 awu nǝ gandǝ san amuna ace ɓamurò, sǝama ɗeki nggeâ ɓǝ̀ o, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ agir kyanbo kporong sǝ ɓǝ̀ yilǝmo sauwa a ɓanza ka.\f + \fr 22:7 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Nggur 4:40\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 8 Lang a ɓak bǝsa kurǝm ngga, dumǝna púp awu nǝ ɓak sheran mǝgbatoki wu kàrì múrí, ace mǝnana wu kǝa yinǝ bafe mala sukkio mala nkila amúr ɓala mò, ɓǝ̀ ɓwa puro amurí sǝ kpa a nzali ka ɗàng.
\p 
\v 9 A pà wunǝ ɓeal ɓaban-anap mò nǝ ambalang amǝsǝɓeale ɓari ɗàng; ɓǝ̀ a pa anggo ka, gìr mǝnana kat a pwano aɓa mǝno yì mǝsǝɓeale a ɓeali, andǝ ɓǝla-anap mǝnana a kumo a ɓabanì ka, à pǝlǝna gìr'ɓeami.
\p 
\v 10 A pà wunǝ tsǝkî mǝdambǝriso andǝ jamnda nggun-rya a myalia ɓǝà rikrya atārǝia ɗàng.
\p 
\v 11 A pà wunǝ oasǝ daura mana à kpapi nkonggúr ɗà'ndíng andǝ nkonggúr linǝn sǝ à tè nǝia ka ɗàng.
\p 
\v 12 Awu nǝ ɓolǝ ankonggúr ɓǝà gyarke a nzali arǝ akunban ine mala nggea-daura mô.
\s1 Anzongcau mala do ɓoarnsari arǝ nongŋo-nda
\p 
\v 13 Ɓǝ̀ ɓwabura al ɓwama, à nong andǝi, sǝ ɓinǝce,
\v 14 tsǝki wi acau kǝsǝkya arǝì, yinǝi wi nǝ lullǝu mǝɓane, kǝ bang ama, <<Ən al ɓwama man sǝ lang ǝn kúti abani ka, ǝn kumi ka à tusǝna tè>> ka,
\v 15 tár muna-ɓwame andǝ nggé ɓǝà twal lagir-pwasǝa mana à sárǝí sǝ muna-ɓwama malea tita nongŋo-nda male andǝ ɓwabure ka, mǝnana dé-nkila na arǝì più ka, ɓǝà yinǝi aban aɓwana-mǝgule a kún nggea-là ɓǝà yi lǝmdǝí.
\v 16 Tár muna-ɓwame ɓǝ̀ ne aɓwana-mǝgule ama, <<Ən twal ɓoarnsarilem ǝn pê mǝnia yì ɓwabura ka ɓǝ̀ duk māmí, sǝ yì ɓwabura ka ɓinǝmǝsǝi.
\v 17 Ado ka ndya kǝ tsǝkî ɓoarnsarilem acau kǝsǝkya arǝì kǝ na ama, yi kumi ka nsari na ɗang. Sǝ lagir-pwasǝa mǝnana à tita nongŋo-nda malea amurí ka ndya ka, nǝ dé-nkila arǝì più, mǝnana lǝmdǝ ama ɓoarnsarilem ngga nsari na ka.>> Sǝ tár muna-ɓwama ka nǝ̀ sárǝ́ lagir nongŋo-ndê aɓadǝm aɓwana-mǝgule mala nggea-lê.
\v 18 Sǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala nggea-là mǝno ka ɓǝà bwal mǝnia yì ɓwabura ka ɓǝà koè nǝ nkamso.
\v 19 Ɓǝà cemi mǝsǝ bolo-azǝrfa, shekel gbǝman-mwashat; sǝ ɓoale ka ɓǝà pè tár muna-ɓwame acemǝnana kiɗikini nsari Isǝrayila lullǝu. Dumǝna púp nǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ do andǝ ɓwama man kǝla māmí; ɓǝà kǝa eari wi ɓǝ̀ nyì ama nǝ̀ pusǝì a ɓala male ɗàng a do-yilǝmu male kat.
\p 
\v 20 Sǝama ɓǝ̀ cau mǝnana ɓwabure na ka mǝsǝcau na, sǝ ɓekǝ gìr pà kàm nǝ̀ lǝmdǝ ama muna-ɓwame ka nsari na raka,
\v 21 ɓǝà bwal muna-ɓwame, ɓǝà umnǝi a kún ɓala mala tárrí, sǝ ɓǝ̀ aburana mala nggea-lê ɓukki nǝ atali ɓǝ̀ wǔ. Mǝnia yì muna-ɓwama ka, pàngŋǝ̀nà gìr kǝsǝkya a Isǝrayila, yì mǝnana nongnǝ bura sǝ nda piu a ɓala mala tárrí ka. Anggo sǝ wun nǝ̀ esǝki ɓealɓikea a ɓalǝ wun.
\p 
\v 22 Ɓǝà kum ɓwabura aban nongnǝ ɓwama mǝnana mālá ɓeɓwa na ka, wu wal-luia yia kǝm, yì ɓwabura mǝnana nongnǝ ɓwame andǝ ɓwame ka. Anggo sǝ wun nǝ̀ esǝki ɓealɓikea a Isǝrayila.
\p 
\v 23 Ɓǝ̀ nsari nakam a nggea-là, mǝnana ɓwabura purna amurí, sǝ ɓè ɓwabura kumi sǝ nongnǝi ka,
\v 24 wu kyan nǝia yia kǝm a nza a kún nggea-là, sǝ wu ɓukkia nǝ atali ɓǝà wu; nsarini ka nda acemǝnana mak'zwalo ɗang, kat andǝa mani ama nda aɓa là. Sǝ ɓwabura ka nda ace nongnǝ mālá ɓwa. Anggo sǝ wun nǝ̀ esǝki ɓealɓikea a ɓalǝ wun.
\p 
\v 25 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ nda a bondo anzǝm là sǝ ɓwabura kum nsari mǝnana à purna amurí sǝ gbárí ka, ɓwabura mǝnia nongnǝi ka nda nǝmurǝi à nǝ̀ wal-luí ka;
\v 26 sǝ mala nsari ka à pà nǝ̀ pakki wi kǝgir ɗàng, acemǝnana pàk kǝgir mǝnana à nǝ̀ wal-luí ace ka ɗàng. Mǝnia yì cau male ka nda kǝla ɓwabura mana lo arǝ ɓi wal-luí ka.
\v 27 Ɓwabura man gbárí nsari mǝnia à pùrnamurí ka anzǝm la, sǝ kat andǝa mani ama nsarini mak'zwalo ɓǝ̀ aɓwana ɓangŋa abani ka, kǝɓwa pà kàm nǝ̀ amsǝi ɗàng.
\p 
\v 28 Ɓǝ̀ kǝ ɓwabura kum nsari mǝnana à malaká pùramurí ɗàng sǝ bwali gbárí, sǝ à yì kumia aɓa pě ka,
\v 29 ɓwabura mǝnia mǝnana gbárí nsarini ka à nǝ̀ tsǝì ɓǝ̀ mbwe tár muna-ɓwame mǝsǝ bolo-azǝrfa lumi-tongno, kǝla gǝna múrí, sǝ muna-ɓwame ka nǝ̀ duk māmí, acemǝnana bwali nǝ rǝcandǝa nongnǝi. À pà nǝ̀ eari wi ɓǝ̀ nyì ama nǝ̀ pusǝì a ɓala male ɗàng a do-yilǝmu male kat.
\p 
\v 30 Ɓwabura pà nǝ̀ al mālá tárrí ɗàng, ace mǝnana ɓǝkǝa ɗwanyi pè tárrí gulo nǝ nongnǝ mālá tárrí ka ɗàng.
\c 23
\s1 Aɓwana mǝnana à pà nǝ̀ ɓallia aɓalǝ // aɓwana mala Yahweh raka
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 1 Ɓwa mǝnana kat à nyaki nkyari, ko à umsǝ ɓate à kasǝi ka, pà nǝ̀ kúti a ban-kpapí mala aɓwana mala Yahweh ɗàng.
\p 
\v 2 Ɓwa mǝnana à ɓǝli muna-twalá na ka pà nǝ̀ kúti a ban-kpapí mala aɓwana mala Yahweh ɗàng; anggo gbal sǝ amuni andǝ amǝkè anzǝmi aban ká arǝ anza lum.
\p 
\v 3 Ɓwa mǝnana ɓwa'Amon na ko ɓwa'Mowap na ka, pà nǝ̀ kúti a ban-kpapí mala aɓwana mala Yahweh ɗàng; anggo gbal sǝ amuni andǝ amǝkè anzǝmi aban ká arǝ anza lum.
\v 4 Mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana à ɓinǝ yiua kúllí wun nǝ girlina andǝ mùrnuna a njar, lang wu purî Masar aban yiu ka; nyar ɗǝm ngga à kya kúr Bil'am muna mala Beyo ɓwa Peto, a nzali Aram-Naharayim, ɓǝ̀ yiu arǝ wun ɓǝ̀ yi sú wun.
\v 5 Kat andǝ amani ka, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kwakikiri arǝ Bil'am ɗàng; Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun yi tsǝk mǝno yì suban ngga pǝlǝ tsǝkbu ace wun, ace ulang earceban mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ndanǝi ace wun ngga.
\v 6 Arǝ anza mǝnana kat à kǝ yiu ka, wu kǝa na ama wun nǝ̀ pàk kǝgìr ace yinǝ dorǝpwala ko kume malea ɗàng.
\p 
\v 7 Wu kǝa ɓǝsǝki ɓwa'Edom ɗàng, acemǝnana yia ka amǝ'eam wun na, sǝ wu kǝa ɓǝsǝki ɓwa'Masar ɗàng, acemǝnana wu dumǝna a nzali malea kǝla abǝri.
\v 8 Amǝkea mǝnana à ɓǝlia tite a tàruià nza malea aban ká dǝmba ka, à nǝ̀ gandǝ ea ɓǝà kùtí aɓa kpapí mala aɓwana mala Yahweh.
\s1 Tsǝk kàttì mala amǝ'lwa ɓǝ̀ do nǝ ɓoarnsari
\p 
\v 9 Lang wu purna ká lwa arǝ aɓiwun amǝbura sǝ wu yi tsǝngŋǝ̀nà agumli a kàttì ka, wu yál rǝwun arǝ koya gìr mǝnana kat mǝɓike na ka.
\v 10 Ɓǝ̀ ɓwa atà wun ngga rǝì pǝndǝkya acemǝnana súkkímùr arǝì nǝ du aban nongŋo ka, ɓǝ̀ purî ɓá kàttì, ɓǝ̀ kya duk kano a nza. Ɓǝ̀ kǝa na ama nǝ̀ nyar aɓa kàttì ɗàng.
\v 11 Sǝama nǝ pwarikpǝra ka, ɓǝ̀ lak rǝì nǝ mur, sǝ ɓǝ̀ pwari kpana ka nǝ̀ gandǝ nyare aɓa kàttì.
\p 
\v 12 Wun nǝ̀ kasǝ ban anzǝm kàttì mǝnana nǝ do nda ban doagung ma'wun ngga.
\v 13 Atà agirtúró mô ka, twal gìr gwam tūli, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ a doagung ngga, awu nǝ gwam tūli nǝi ace lùmsǝ ciuto.
\v 14 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga kǝ gya aɓalǝ wun a kàttì ma'wun, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ amsǝ wun sǝ ɓǝ̀ pà aɓiwun amǝbura a ɓabù wun. Acemani ka, kàttì ma'wun nǝ̀ duk mǝfele, ace mǝnana Yahweh ɓǝ̀ kǝa sǝn kǝ pǝndǝkya aɓalǝ wun, sǝ nǝ̀ pǝlǝ nzǝmi arǝ wun ngga ɗàng.
\s1 Pàk gìr mǝnana nda a njari ka
\sp Musa bang ama:
\p 
\v 15 Guro mǝnana ɓangŋa nying mǝtala-ɓala male sǝ yiu ace kum àwá a bano ka, kǝa nyesǝi ɓǝ̀ nyar aban mǝtala-ɓala male ɗàng.
\v 16 Ɗeki ɓǝ̀ do atò, aɓalǝ wun, aɓa ɓè là ma'wun mǝnana earce nǝ̀ duk kam ngga; wu kǝa lǝmdǝì wi ɓealɓana ɗang.
\p 
\v 17 Ɓǝà kǝa kum ɓwa Isǝrayila, ɓwama ko ɓwabura mǝnana kǝ mak rǝì ɓǝ̀ duk mǝ'nongginǝ-rǝarǝu aɓa ndàka-lú ka ɗàng.
\v 18 Boalo mǝnana à kum arǝ ɓwama ko ɓwabura mǝ'nongginǝban ngga, ɓǝà kǝa yinǝi a ɓala mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ace mbwe gìr mǝnana ɓwa pàcau nǝ-shambum aɓadǝm Ɓakuli ama nǝ̀ pà ka ɗàng. Amǝnia yì agir kǝm ngga Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ ɓinǝcea.
\p 
\v 19 Ɓǝ̀ a pê ɓio ɓwa Isǝrayila tangna boalo, ko girlina, ko ɓekǝ gìr ka, kǝa kasǝi wi kǝ mur ɓǝ̀ mbweo amúr boalo, ko girlina, ko ɓekǝ gìr mǝnana a pa tangna male ka ɗàng.
\v 20 Ɓǝ̀ wu pè ɓwa-kúnɗàngna tangna ka, wun nǝ̀ gandǝ tsǝi ɓǝ̀ mbweka wuni nǝ mur amurí; sǝ ɓǝ̀ mǝ'eam wun ɓwa Isǝrayila na ka, pà wun nǝ̀ ak kǝgir amurí ɗàng, ace mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ɓǝ̀ tsǝka wun bu arǝ gir mǝnana kat wu tsǝk bu wun arǝia ama wun nǝ̀ pea a nzali mǝnana wu kǝ kutio wun nǝ̀ é ɓǝ̀ duk girkuma ma'wun ngga.
\p 
\v 21 Ɓǝ̀ a pàcau nǝ-shambum aban Yahweh ka, kǝa dǝndi arǝ lumsǝe ɗàng, acemǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli mô ka ɓafo nǝ̀ ɗice a buo; sǝ nǝ̀ dupô cauɓikea.
\v 22 Sǝama ɓǝ̀ a bwalrǝò arǝ pàcau nǝ-shambum ngga, pà nǝ̀ dupô cauɓikea ɗàng.
\v 23 Cau mǝnana mburkuno bangŋi ka dumǝna púp awu nǝ tsǝkiro wu pê, acemǝnana nǝ eare mô sǝ a pàcau mò nǝ-shambum aban Yahweh Ɓakuli mô nǝ kuno.
\p 
\v 24 Ɓǝ̀ a kúti a ɓaban-anap mala ɓio mǝmurkala ka, li ɓǝla-anap mǝnana nǝ̀ karǝo ka, sǝama a pà wunǝ tsǝk kǝɓè a luru mô ɗàng.
\v 25 Ɓǝ̀ a kúti a ɓaban mǝssa mala ɓio mǝmurkala ka, awu nǝ gandǝ harki kir mǝssa nǝ buo, wu shê, sǝama a pà wunǝ tsǝk byau ace kasǝ ɓekǝ múr mǝssa mana nda aban came a ɓaban mala ɓio mǝmurkala ka ɗang.
\c 24
\s1 Anggurcau mala gau doɓala
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 1 Lang ɓwabura twal ɓwama sǝ ali, sǝ nǝnzǝ́mò ka cè ɓwame ɓoari wi ɗǝm ɗàng, acemǝnana kum ɓwame nǝ ɓekǝ mǝɓane,\f + \fr 24:1 \fq mǝɓane: \ft ɓealu ko gìr mana à pà nǝ̀ earce ko à nǝ̀ é raka; ko gìr kǝsǝkya mǝnana tè yi pur ka.\f* sǝ gilǝî wi takada mala gau doɓala, pè wi, sǝ pǝri ɓǝ̀ purî ɓala male,
\v 2 sǝ yì ɓwame ka puro o sǝ kya duk mālá ɓè ɓwabura ɗàng,
\v 3 sǝ ɓǝ̀ burí mǝnia mana ali nǝnzǝ́mò ka ɓinǝce, gilǝî wi takada gau doɓala, tsǝki wi a ɓabui, sǝ tasǝ takwari ɓǝ̀ purî ɓala male ka, ko ana raka mǝnia yì burí mana ali nǝnzǝ́mò ka wù ka,
\v 4 burí mǝdǝmbe, mǝnana pǝri ka, pà nǝ̀ twali ɓǝ̀ duk māmí ɗǝm anzǝm mǝnana pǝndǝkina ka ɗàng; mǝno ka gìr'ɓeami na aban Yahweh. Sǝ pà wun nǝ̀ yinǝ mǝno yì cauɓikea ka amur nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pa wun ɓǝ̀ duk nzali liɓala ma'wun ngga ɗàng.
\s1 Ɓwabura mana loa al-ɓwama ka
\p 
\v 5 Ɓwabura mǝnana loa al-ɓwama ka, à pà nǝ̀ tasǝì ɓǝ̀ kya lwa, ko à nǝ̀ pè wi ɓekǝ túró ɗang. Ɓǝà nyì atarǝì ɓǝ̀ do a ɓala pǝlǝa mwashat ace mǝnana māmí mana ali ka ɓǝ̀ kum banɓoarnado andǝi.
\s1 Ak gìr a kún tangna
\p 
\v 6 Ɓwa ɓǝkǝa na ama nǝ̀ ak nggea-taligo ko muna-taligo arǝ ɓeɓwa a kúnì tangna mǝnana ɓwe ak a buì ka ɗàng, acemǝnana mǝno ka nǝ̀ do kǝla twal yilǝmi ɓwa ace tangna.
\s1 Iu ɓwapǝndǝa
\p 
\v 7 Ɓǝ̀ à kum kǝɓwa aban iu ɓi ɓwa Isǝrayila, kǝ pángŋǝ̀nà túró guro nǝi ko kǝ kurkuro nǝi ka, mǝno yì mǝn'í ka ɓǝà wal-luí. Anggo sǝ wun nǝ̀ esǝki ɓealɓikea aɓalǝ wun.
\s1 Kwánó nggû
\p 
\v 8 Ɓǝ̀ kwánó nggû sak aɓalǝ wun ngga, wu yál rǝ'wun nǝ kpata cau kat gǝ̀rgǝ̀r kǝla mǝnana apǝris a tàu mala Lawi nǝ̀ kània wun ngga. Kǝla mǝnana ǝn banggia wia ka, anggo gbal sǝ wun nǝ̀ pa nǝ tsǝkiru.
\v 9 Wu ɗenyinǝ gir mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pàkkî Miriyam a njar, mana wu ndarǝ purì ɓá Masar ka.
\s1 Pà tangna
\p 
\v 10 Lang a pê ɓio mǝmurkala koya ulang tangna ka, a pà wunǝ ká a ɓala male ace ak kǝgir a bui, awu nǝ tsǝì a bano, ama anzǝm mana mbwena tangne ka, sǝ awu nǝ nyesǝi wi gìr male ɗàng;
\v 11 kundǝi a nza, ɓǝ̀ kutio ɓǝ̀ kya twal gìr mǝnana wu ear amurí ka nǝ nggearǝì ɓǝ̀ yinǝi a bano.
\v 12 Ɓǝ̀ ɓwe ka mǝ'tǝ̀r na ka, a pà wunǝ bwal gìrkùmsǝo male mǝnana po ace tangna mǝnana ak ka, ɓǝ̀ nongŋo a bano ban ɓǝ̀ fè ɗàng.
\v 13 Nǝ pwarikpǝra ka, nyesǝi wi gìrkùmsǝo male ace mǝnana ɓio mǝmurkala ɓǝ̀ nongŋo aɓa gìrkùmsǝo male, sǝ yì ka nǝ̀ zǝmbî Ɓakuli ɓǝ̀ tsǝko bu. Mǝno ka nǝ̀ dupô cauɓoarna aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli mô.
\s1 Mbwe amǝ'tǝ̀r tangnakusǝia
\p 
\v 14 Ɓǝ̀ a twal ɓwa mana mǝ'tǝ̀r na ko mǝ'tǝlè na ɓǝ̀ pàkkô túró-boalo ka, kǝa pakcè-ɓa, a nǝ ginǝ mbwe tangnakusǝi ɗàng, ko ɓwe ka nda mwashat atà amǝ'eambo amǝ Isǝrayila, ko nda mwashat atà amǝ'kúnɗàngna mǝnana à ndanǝdo a ɓè la a nzali ma'wun ngga.
\v 15 Koya pwari ka, mbwe ɓwe boalo-túró male sǝ ɓǝkǝa ká kpa mala pwari ɗàng, acemǝnana yì ka mǝ'tǝ̀r na, sǝ ɓalǝi na arǝì ace girlina kúni, ɓǝ̀ ana raka, nǝ̀ ɓua nǝ we aban Yahweh, sǝ mǝno ka nǝ̀ dupô cauɓikea.
\p 
\v 16 À pà nǝ̀ wal-lú atárrú atàcau mala amuna malea ɗang, sǝ amuna gbal ka à pà nǝ̀ wal-luia atàcau mala atárrià ɗang. Ɓǝ̀ yan sǝ pak cauɓikea ka, ɓwe na à nǝ̀ wal-luí ka.
\p 
\v 17 A pà wunǝ pūrǝ ɓashi-mǝsǝcau mǝnana nda ace ɓwa-kúnɗàngna mǝnana do aɓalǝ wun, ko mǝnana nda ace káwá, ko awu nǝ ak gir'nggurǝu mala mā-lú a kúnì tangna ɗàng.
\v 18 Wu ɗenyi ama wun nda ka aguro ɗiɗyal a nzali Masar, sǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun akmúr wun akano; ace mani ka, ǝn nggǝ pà wun mǝnia yì nzongcau ama wu kpate.
\p 
\v 19 Lang wu nda aban pwan mǝssa ma'wun a ɓaban ma'wun, sǝ wu lórǝ́ kùnò a ɓaban ngga, cè wu na ama wun nǝ̀ nyare ace ká twale ɗàng; wu nyi ace abǝri mǝnana à do aɓalǝ wun ngga, andǝ akáwá andǝ amā-lú, ace mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ɓǝ̀ tsǝka wun bù amur atúró ma'wun kat.
\v 20 Lang wun nda rǝ kok ɓǝlanggun arǝ anggun olif ma'wun ngga, wu kǝa na ama wun nǝ̀ basǝ koè arǝ abu-nggunî ɗǝm ɗàng; gìr mǝnana ue ka nda ace abǝri mǝnana à do aɓalǝ wun ngga, andǝ akáwá andǝ amā-lú.
\p 
\v 21 Lang wu nda aban pwan ɓǝla-anap a ɓaban-anap ma'wun ngga, wu kǝa nyar ama wun nǝ̀ tàrki acili mana à ue ka ɗàng; gìr mǝnana ue ka nda ace abǝri mǝnana à do aɓalǝ wun ngga, andǝ akáwá andǝ amā-lú.
\v 22 Wu ɗenyi ama wun nda ka aguro ɗiɗyal a nzali Masar; acemani ka, ǝn nggǝ pà wun mǝnia yì nzongcau ama wu kpate.
\c 25
\s1 Kokban nǝ nkamso amur gìr mǝɓike mana ɓwa pè ka
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 1 Ɓǝ̀ aɓwana ɓari warinǝ rǝia a ban ɓashi, amur cau mana makgir na amurí ka, mǝ'ɓashi na nǝ̀ kasǝcau ama, ɓwa mǝnia ka, nda mǝ'mǝsǝcau, sǝ ɓè ɓwa mǝno ka, nda pànǝ mǝsǝcau raka.
\v 2 Ɓwa mǝnana ɓashi me, sǝ à kasǝ ama ɓǝà koè nǝ nkamso ka, mǝ'ɓashi nǝ̀ tsǝì púp, ɓǝ̀ nongŋo a nzali a ɓadǝmbi, sǝ à nǝ̀ koè làkkì mala kwakban mana karǝ arǝ cau mana ɓashi kasǝi wi ka.
\v 3 Sǝama, làkkì mala kokban nǝ nkamso, ɓǝkǝa kútì lumi-ine ɗang. Acemana, ɓǝ̀ kokban nǝ nkamso kútì kusǝ lumi-ine ka, mǝ'eam wun ɓwa Isǝrayila mǝno à koè ka, nǝ̀ kum kyauwikiban a mǝsǝ ɓwabundǝa.
\s1 Kǝa mārǝ́ kún jamnda ɗàng
\p 
\v 4 A pà wunǝ mārǝ́ kún jamnda, lang a ndaban paktúró nǝi aban nya mǝssa ka ɗàng.\f + \fr 25:4 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Kor 9:9; 1Tim 5:18\xt*\ft .\f*
\s1 Túró mala ɓwabura aban mā-lú mala mǝ'eambi
\p 
\v 5 Ɓǝ̀ amuna-burana, amǝ'eamrǝarǝu do atārǝia, sǝ mwashat aɓalǝia paklú, pànǝ muna-ɓwabura mana nyi raka, mā-lú male ka, pà nǝ̀ al ɓekǝ ɓwabura a nza ɗàng. Mǝ'eam burí muna-ɓwabura na nǝ̀ kùtí a baní nǝ̀ twali ɓǝ̀ duk māmí, ɓǝ̀ pàkki wi gìr mǝnana nda túró mala bura, kǝla mǝ'eam burí ka.
\v 6 Muna-ɓwabura mǝdǝmbe mana à ɓǝli ka, nda mǝnana nǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ lullǝ mǝ'eam tárrí mana paklú ka, ace mǝnana ɓǝà kǝa lórǝ́ lùllǝì a nzali Isǝrayila ɗàng.
\v 7 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ do ama, man yì ɓwabura, mǝ'eam lú, earce nǝ̀ twal mā-lú mala mǝ'eambi raka, ɓwame nǝ̀ gandǝ ká aban aɓwana-mǝgule a kún nggea-là, nǝ̀ nggá bang ama, <<Mǝ'eam burém ɓinǝna lidǝmba nǝ lullǝ mǝ'eambi a nzali Isǝrayila. Yi ka, ear ama nǝ̀ lùmsǝ túró mala bura kǝla mǝ'eam burém, mana nǝ̀ pakkam ngga ɗàng.>>
\p 
\v 8 Sǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala nggea-là male nǝ̀ tunǝi, à nǝ̀ ne wi cau. Sǝ ɓǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ ɓinǝcau, aban bang ama, yì ka earce nǝ̀ twali ɓǝ̀ duk māmí raka,
\v 9 mālá mǝ'eambi, yi mā-lú ka, nǝ̀ ká abanɨ a ɓamǝsǝ aɓwana-mǝgule, nǝ̀ pusǝ nkura mwashat a kusǝ ɓwabure, nǝ̀ tappi wi ntara a ɓamǝsǝi, sǝ nǝ̀ bang ama, <<Mǝnia ka nda gìr mana à kǝ pakki ɓwabura mana pà nǝ̀ eare nǝ̀ kumbi mǝ'eambi amuna andǝ amǝ'kau raka.>>
\v 10 Ɓala mala mǝnia yì ɓwabura ka à nǝ̀ súrǝì aɓa nzali Isǝrayila kat ama, <<Ɓala mala ɓwa mǝnana à pusǝ nkura a kusǝi ka.>>
\s1 Munǝo a nre ka aɓwana ɓari
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 11 Ɓǝ̀ aburana ɓari narǝ munǝo, sǝ mālá ɓwa man mwashat ka, yiu ama nǝ bwalì burí kàm, nǝ̀ amsǝi a bu ɓwabura mǝno kǝ walki ka, sǝ kara sárǝ́ buì gbami ɓata ɓwabura mana à munǝkiyi andǝ burí ka,
\v 12 wu kasǝ bui kpat. Wu kǝa sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr male ɗàng.
\s1 Pàk mǝsǝcau aɓa nggaliki
\p 
\v 13 A pà wunǝ pàngnǝ agir kārǝki dǝmbǝrya mala gìr ulangnì ɓari: mǝgule andǝ mǝkyauwe, aɓa luru mô ɗàng.
\v 14 A pà wunǝ pàngnǝ atasau kārǝkigir ulangnì ɓari: mǝgule andǝ mǝkyauwe, a ɓala mò ɗàng.
\v 15 Gìr kārǝki dǝmbǝrya mala gìr mò andǝ tasau kārǝkigir mò ka, ɓǝà do amǝ'ɓafoe andǝ mǝ'mǝsǝcauni. Mǝnia ka nda ace mǝnana yilǝmo ɓǝ̀ sauwa aɓa nzali mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ngga.
\v 16 Aɓwana mǝnana kat à kǝ pak agir ulang mǝnia, mala ɗwanyi pàk mǝsǝcau ka, agìr'ɓeami na aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun.
\s1 Wu twalta amǝ Amalek
\p 
\v 17 Wu ɗenyinǝ gir mana amǝ'Amalek pàkka wun amur njargula, lang wu purî Masar aban yiu ka.
\v 18 A pwari mǝno wu nda aɓa aulǝa andǝ ganda mala gya ka, à pur anzǝm wun sǝ à yinǝ munǝo arǝ aɓwana ma'wun mana à pànǝ rǝcandǝa ra, sǝ à ueo anzǝ́mò à kǝ yiu atà wun ɓukɓuk ka. Lǝmdǝ ama, yia amǝ'Amalek ka à kǝ ɓanggi Ɓakuli ɗang.
\v 19 Acemani ka, anzǝm mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, pana wun usǝlǝo, wu gandǝna aɓiwun amǝbura kat a koya buì, aɓa nzali mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ɓǝ̀ duk nzali liɓala ma'wun andǝ girkuma ma'wun ngga, wun nǝ̀ twalta amǝ'Amalek kat, mana aɓwana pà nǝ̀ ɗenyinǝia ɗǝm a ɓanza raka.\f + \fr 25:19 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Pur 17:8-14\xt*\ft .\f* Cala ɓalǝ wun lórǝ́ ɗang!
\c 26
\s1 Pè Ɓakuli ɓǝlagir mǝdǝmbe andǝ // kāmbe mwashat aɓa lum mala kume mò
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 1 Anzǝm mana wu kutina aɓa nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ɓǝ̀ duk gìr'liɓala ma'wun, sǝ wu angŋǝ́nì pǝlǝna girkuma ma'wun, wu dumǝna aɓalǝi ka,
\v 2 koyan atà wun ngga nǝ̀ tù aɓa koya ɓǝlagir mǝnana tita ɓǝla sǝ ɓwe pwan a ɓaban male aɓa nzali mana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ngga, ɓǝ̀ tsǝì aɓa ndakade, sǝ ɓǝ̀ kyan nǝi a ban mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tàrì, nǝ̀ tsǝk lùllǝì ɓǝ̀ duk kam ngga.
\v 3 Sǝ wun nǝ̀ ká aban pǝris mana nda a buno-pǝris a bàkú mǝno ka, sǝ wun nǝ̀ banggi wi ama, <<Mǝ nda rǝ ne bwāng yalung aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli mem ama, ǝn yina aɓa\f + \fr 26:3 \fq ǝn yina aɓa \ft ko: ǝn pwani aɓa.\f* nzali mǝnana Yahweh kángìr aban aká sǝm ama nǝ̀ pa sǝm ngga.>>
\v 4 Sǝ pǝris ka nǝ̀ ak ndakade mǝno a buo ka, nǝ̀ tsǝì aɓadǝm gyangŋan mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun.
\v 5 Sǝ awu nǝ na bwāng aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli mô ama, <<Kâ, yì Yakupu ka, ɓwa'Aram, mǝ'gya arǝ abân na, sǝ wari a Masar kya duk kam kǝla bǝri-ɓwa. Amǝɓala male mana à yiu andǝi a Masar ka à nda kpokyak, sǝama akano ka, à yi duk nzali mala ɓwapǝndǝa mǝgule, mǝ'rǝcandǝe andǝ mǝ'làkke.
\v 6 Sǝama amǝ Masar pàkka sǝm gìrkwanban, à tsǝk sǝm a tanni, sǝ à para sǝm atúró mǝkwane amur sǝm.
\v 7 Pǝlǝa sǝm ɓua aban Yahweh, yì Ɓakuli mala aká sǝm. Yahweh ok ɓua ma'sǝm, sǝn ɓike mala do ma'sǝm, andǝ kasǝ piban mana sǝm nda aɓalǝi, andǝ parban mana sǝm nda aɓate ka.
\v 8 Nda sǝ Yahweh pusǝ sǝm, sǝm purî ɓá Masar nǝ kaɓa rǝcandǝa male andǝ mazo mala nggwarbui, nǝ anggea gir-paɓangciu, andǝ agir-lǝmdǝa, andǝ agir-gyambǝliban.
\v 9 Pǝlǝa yinǝ sǝm a ban mǝnia, sǝ pa sǝm mǝnia yì nzali, yì nzali mǝnana kiura andǝ mur'nyi kǝ ɓang aɓalǝi ka.
\v 10 Sǝ adyan ngga, ndya ǝn yinǝ aɓǝlagir mǝdǝmbe mǝnana ǝn pwan a ɓaban aɓa nzali mana we, Yahweh a pami ka.>>
\p Sǝ awu nǝ tamsǝ ndakadeni aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli mô, sǝ awu nǝ ɓun amur ankūnǝo aɓadǝmbi.
\v 11 Anggo sǝ we, atarǝ wun wunǝ amǝ'Lawi, andǝ amǝ'kúnɗàngna mana à ndanǝ do aɓalǝ wun ngga, wun nǝ̀ pàk banɓoarnado nǝ agir mǝɓoarne mana kat Yahweh Ɓakuli mô pò sǝ pè amǝɓala mò ka.
\p 
\v 12 Lang wu malna pusǝki kāmbe mwashat aɓa lum mala akume kat mala aɓaban ma'wun a tàruia pǝlǝa, mǝnana nda pǝlǝa mala pà kāmbe aɓa lum ngga, wun nǝ̀ pè amǝ'Lawi, andǝ amǝ'kúnɗàngna mǝnana à do aɓalǝ wun ngga, andǝ akáwá, andǝ amā-lú, ace mǝnana ɓǝà kum girlina, ɓǝà li, ɓǝà ɗǝmbo aɓalǝ ala ma'wun.
\v 13 Pǝlǝa awu nǝ bang aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli mô ama, <<Mim ngga ǝn pusǝna kāmbe gìr mǝfele\f + \fr 26:13 \fq mǝfele \ft ko mana mala Ɓakuli na ka. \f* a ɓala mem, sǝ ǝn pani amǝ'Lawi, andǝ amǝ'kúnɗàngna mǝnana à do aɓalǝ sǝm ngga, andǝ akáwá, andǝ amā-lú, kǝla mana a tsǝkam nzongcau ama ɓǝn pê ka. Ən yálì ɓekǝ nzongcau mò ɗàng, sǝ ɓalǝam lórǝiǎ ɗàng.
\v 14 Ən li ma kǝ kāmbe gìr mǝfele lang mǝ ndarǝ ɓua-lú ka ɗàng; ǝn pusǝ ma kǝɓè bare aɓalǝi lang mǝ nda aɓa do-ɓeami ka ɗang, sǝ ǝn pa kǝɓè bare ace alú ɗàng. Ən oako we Yahweh Ɓakuli mem, ǝn pángŋǝ̀nà gìr mǝnana kat a tsǝkam nzongcau ama ɓǝ̀ ǝn pê ka.
\v 15 Adyan ngga dili mǝsǝo a ban do mò mǝfele mana a kùli ka, sǝ wu tsǝki aɓwana mò amǝ Isǝrayila bù, andǝ nzali mana a pana sǝm, kǝla mǝnana a kánbì aká sǝm ngga, yi nzali mana kiura andǝ mur'nyi kǝ ɓang kàm ngga.>>
\s1 Masǝlǝata acau kwarkiru
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 16 Yalung ngga Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ tsǝka wun nzongcau, ama ɓǝ̀ wu kpata amǝnia yì anê andǝ akasǝcau ka. Acemani ka, wu kpatea nǝ ɓabum wun kat sǝ nǝ yilǝmi wun kat.
\v 17 Yalung ngga, wu nana bwāng ama, Yahweh nda Ɓakuli ma'wun, sǝ wun nǝ̀ gya aɓalǝ anjar male, wun nǝ̀ kpata anê male, andǝ anzongcau male, andǝ anggurcau male, sǝ wun nǝ̀ oki wi.
\v 18 Sǝ yalung ngga, Yahweh bangŋǝna bwāng ama, angŋǝna wun, wun nda ka aɓwana male, agirkuma male mǝnana earkiyi acea raka, kǝla mana nani aɓa kùrcau ka, sǝ ɗǝm ngga ama, ɓǝ̀ wu bwal anzongcau male kat.
\v 19 Bangŋǝna bwāng ama, nǝ̀ loasǝ wun a kùli ɓǝ̀ wu kum ɓwangsǝban, andǝ lullǝu, andǝ gulo amur acilia anzali mana kat pea ka, sǝ ɗǝm ngga ɓǝ̀ wu duk aɓwana amǝfele a baní, yi Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, kǝla mana bang aɓa kùrcau male ka.
\c 27
\s1 Gyangŋan mǝnana amur Nkono Ebal ka
\p 
\v 1 Musa andǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala amǝ Isǝrayila banggi aɓwe ama, <<Wu bwal anzongcau mǝnana kat ǝn nggǝ pà wun yalung ngga.
\v 2 \f + \fr 27:2 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Jes 8:30-32\xt*\ft .\f* Nǝ̀ do ama pwari mǝnana wu yàlǝ́nì nkaring Nggeasala Jodan aban ká a nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ngga, wun nǝ̀ tàmsǝkì ɓamurǝ wun atali mǝgulke sǝ wun nǝ̀ tasǝ rǝia nǝ nshime-pwasǝa.
\v 3 Wun nǝ̀ gilǝ acau mala mǝnia yì nggurcau kat ka amúrià, lang wu yàlnà a nkaring ace ká kutio aɓa nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pa wun ngga, yì nzali mana kiura andǝ mur'nyi kǝ ɓang kàm, kǝla mǝnana Yahweh, yì Ɓakuli mala aká wun pa wun cau ace ka.
\v 4 Sǝ lang wu yàlnà a nkaring Jodan ngga, wun nǝ̀ tamsǝki amǝnia yì atali, mana ǝn nggǝ pà wun nzongcau amúrià yalung ngga, amúr Nkono Ebal, sǝ wun nǝ̀ tasǝ rǝia nǝ nshime-pwasǝa.
\v 5 \f + \fr 27:5 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 20:25\xt*\f*Abanì ka wun nǝ̀ ɓakkî Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun gyangŋan, gyangŋan mǝnana à pè nǝ atali ka. Pà wun nǝ̀ pàktúró nǝ tali mǝnana à ɓunni ko à gilǝki rǝi nǝ girtúró mala bolo-candǝa ace ɓak gyangŋanì ɗàng.
\v 6 Wun nǝ̀ ɓak gyangŋan mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ atali mǝnana à ɓunnia nǝ ɓunno ko à gilǝki rǝia raka, sǝ wun nǝ̀ pà ɓoro mǝnana à nǝ̀ pisǝi kǝring a bǝsa ka amurí aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun.
\v 7 Wun nǝ̀ pa aɓoro mala gir'nkila ace dotarǝu, wun nǝ̀ lì, sǝ wun nǝ̀ pak bumpwasǝa aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun.
\v 8 Sǝ wun nǝ̀ gilǝ acau mala nggurcau mǝnia kat ka ɓǝà pur pepè amúr amǝnia yì atali ka.>>
\p 
\v 9 Pǝlǝa Musa andǝ apǝris amǝkà Lawi bangcau nǝ amǝ Isǝrayila kat ama, <<Wu duk ɗǝong sǝ wu kwakikir wun, wun amǝ Isǝrayila! Yalung ngga wu dumǝna aɓwana mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun.
\v 10 Acemani ka, wun nǝ̀ ok gi Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun sǝ wun nǝ̀ kpata anzongcau male andǝ ngguracau male, mǝnana ǝn nggǝ pa wun yalung ngga.>>
\s1 Asúban a Nkono Ebal
\p 
\v 11 A kǝ pwari mǝno, Musa kwarkir aɓwe ama,
\v 12 <<Anzǝm mana wu yàlǝ́nì Nggeasala Jodan ngga, atau mala Shimiyon, andǝ Lawi, andǝ Yahuda, andǝ Isaka, andǝ Yisǝfu, andǝ Benjami ngga à nǝ̀ cam amur Nkono Gerizim, sǝ à nǝ̀ ham atsǝkbu mala Yahweh amur aɓwana.\f + \fr 27:12 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Nggur 11:29; Jes 8:33-35\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 13 Sǝ atau mala Ruben, andǝ Gad, andǝ Asha, andǝ Zebulu andǝ Dan andǝ Naftali na à nǝ̀ cam amur Nkono Ebal à nǝ̀ kwakikiria arǝ asúban mana à nǝ̀ hambia ka.
\v 14 Sǝ aburana a tàu mala Lawi nǝ̀ loasǝ gia a kùli à nǝ̀ banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\pi1 
\v 15 <<Suban na amur ɓwa mǝnana pàk ɓekǝ ɓǝ̀nzál nǝ tali, ko nggun, ko bolo-ntùl, nǝ túróbù mala amǝ'sǝlǝ pakkiagir, mana gìr'ɓeami na aban Yahweh, sǝ tsǝì kǝ peri abani aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa ka.\f + \fr 27:15 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 20:4; 34:17; Pǝris 19:4; 26:1; Nggur 4:15-18; 5:8\xt*\ft .\f*
\pi1 <<Sǝ aɓwe kat nǝ̀ ear ama, <Ɓǝ̀ do anggo!>
\pi1 
\v 16 <<Suban na amur ɓwa mǝnana pé tárrí andǝ nggé gulo raka.\f + \fr 27:16 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 20:12; Nggur 5:16\xt*\ft .\f*
\pi1 <<Sǝ aɓwe kat nǝ̀ ear ama, <Ɓǝ̀ do anggo!>
\pi1 
\v 17 <<Suban na amur ɓwa mǝnana tusǝ nzong-nzali mala ɓì mǝmurkala ka.\f + \fr 27:17 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Nggur 19:14\xt*\ft .\f*
\pi1 <<Sǝ aɓwe kat nǝ̀ ear ama, <Ɓǝ̀ do anggo!>
\pi1 
\v 18 <<Suban na amur ɓwa mǝnana ɓosǝkikusǝ nte ɓǝ̀ kyanggî njar ka.\f + \fr 27:18 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pǝris 19:14\xt*\ft .\f*
\pi1 <<Sǝ aɓwe kat nǝ̀ ear ama, <Ɓǝ̀ do anggo!>
\pi1 
\v 19 <<Suban na amur ɓwa mǝnana pūrǝ ɓashi-mǝsǝcau mala bǝri, ko mala káwá, ko mala mā-lú ka.\f + \fr 27:19 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 22:21; 23:9; Pǝris 19:33-34; Nggur 24:17-18\xt*\ft .\f*
\pi1 <<Sǝ aɓwe kat nǝ̀ ear ama, <Ɓǝ̀ do anggo!>
\pi1 
\v 20 <<Suban na amur ɓwa mǝnana nongnǝ mālá tárrí ka; acemǝnana gusǝlǝce ban-nongŋo mala tárrí ɗàng.\f + \fr 27:20 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pǝris 18:8; 20:11; Nggur 22:30\xt*\ft .\f*
\pi1 <<Sǝ aɓwe kat nǝ̀ ear ama, <Ɓǝ̀ do anggo!>
\pi1 
\v 21 <<Suban na amur ɓwa mǝnana eau girkusǝu ka.\f + \fr 27:21 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 22:19; Pǝris 18:23; 20:15\xt*\ft .\f*
\pi1 <<Sǝ aɓwe kat nǝ̀ ear ama, <Ɓǝ̀ do anggo!>
\pi1 
\v 22 <<Suban na amur ɓwa mǝnana nongnǝ mǝ'nggaule mǝnana tárrí nǝ̀ ɓǝli ko nggè nǝ̀ ɓǝli ka.\f + \fr 27:22 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pǝris 18:9; 20:17\xt*\ft .\f*
\pi1 <<Sǝ aɓwe kat nǝ̀ ear ama, <Ɓǝ̀ do anggo!>
\pi1 
\v 23 <<Suban na amur ɓwa mǝnana nongnǝ nkili-mǝɓwame ka.\f + \fr 27:23 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pǝris 18:17; 20:14\xt*\ft .\f*
\pi1 <<Sǝ aɓwe kat nǝ̀ ear ama, <Ɓǝ̀ do anggo!>
\pi1 
\v 24 <<Suban na amur ɓwa mǝnana wal-lú ɓi mǝmurkala aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa ka.
\pi1 <<Sǝ aɓwe kat nǝ̀ ear ama, <Ɓǝ̀ do anggo!>
\pi1 
\v 25 <<Suban na amur ɓwa mǝnana eare ak pàbunǝnzali ace wal-lú mǝ'kunpwasǝa ka.
\pi1 <<Sǝ aɓwe kat nǝ̀ ear ama, <Ɓǝ̀ do anggo!>
\pi1 
\v 26 <<Suban na amur ɓwa mǝnana ginǝe pà nǝ̀ kpata acau mala mǝnia yì nggurcau nǝ̀ pea raka.\f + \fr 27:26 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Gal 3:10\xt*\f*
\pi1 <<Sǝ aɓwe kat nǝ̀ ear ama, <Ɓǝ̀ do anggo!> >>
\c 28
\s1 Atsǝkbu mala okiru
\r (Ace Apǝris 26:3-13; Ɓǝs Nggur 7:12-24)
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 1 Nǝ̀ do ama, ɓǝ̀ wun nǝ̀ kwakikir wun pepè, wun nǝ̀ okî Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, sǝ wun nǝ̀ kpata anzongcau male mǝnana ǝn nggǝ pa wun yalung ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu peǎ ka, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ loasǝ wun a kùli amur anzali mala ɓanza kat.
\v 2 Ɓǝ̀ wun nǝ̀ kpata gì Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga, amǝnia yi atsǝkbu kat ka à nǝ̀ yiu amur wun, à nǝ̀ yia akà wun dǝmba.
\p 
\v 3 Wun nǝ̀ kum tsǝkbu aɓa là, sǝ wun nǝ̀ kum tsǝkbu a ɓaban.
\p 
\v 4 Wun nǝ̀ kum tsǝkbu mala ɓǝl amuna pas, andǝ kum girɓaban kpǝm, andǝ ɓǝla mala agirkusǝu ma'wun nyangsang; andá ma'wun, andǝ ambul ma'wun, andǝ anzur ma'wun nǝ̀ hatǝki nǝ ɓǝl amunia.
\p 
\v 5 Ndakade mò, andǝ tasau sùrǝ̀ gir mò nǝ̀ kum tsǝkbu.
\p 
\v 6 Puro mô andǝ kutio mô ka, nǝ̀ dum nǝ tsǝkbu.
\p 
\v 7 Yahweh nǝ̀ tsǝk aɓiwun amǝbura mǝnana à kǝ lo arǝ wun ngga ɓǝà kpa aɓadǝm wun. Yia ka à nǝ̀ pur aban yiu arǝ wun a njar mwashat, sǝ à nǝ̀ ɓangŋa aɓadǝm wun arǝ anjar tongno-nong-ɓari.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh nǝ̀ tasǝ tsǝkbu amur abah ma'wun, andǝ gir mǝnana kat wu tsǝk bù wun amurí ka; yì ka nǝ̀ tsǝka wun bù aɓa nzali mǝnana yì Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pà wun ngga.
\p 
\v 9 Ɓǝ̀ wu bwal anzongcau mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, sǝ wu kpata anjar male ka, Yahweh nǝ̀ pa wun kusǝu came kǝla aɓwana amǝfele male, kǝla mǝnana pàcau nǝ kángìr aban aká wun ama nǝ̀ pàk ka.
\v 10 Sǝ aɓwapǝndǝa mala anzali a ɓanza kat nǝ̀ sǝni ama, à kǝ tunǝ wun nǝ lullǝ Yahweh, sǝ yià ka à nǝ̀ ɓangga wun.
\v 11 Yahweh nǝ̀ tsǝa kume ma'wun nǝ̀ hatǝki kǝ̀rkǝ́r aɓa nzali mǝnana kánbì aká wun, ama nǝ̀ pà wun ngga; wun nǝ̀ ɓǝl amuna pas, agirkusǝu ma'wun nǝ̀ hatǝki, sǝ nzali ma'wun nǝ̀ pusǝa wun agir-ɓaban kpǝm.
\v 12 Yahweh nǝ̀ mǝnba wun ndà mala ram gìrɓoarna male a kùli, nǝ̀ pa wun mbulo a nzali ma'wun a kúnì male, sǝ nǝ̀ tsǝka wun bù arǝ atúró mǝnana kat wu tsǝk bù wun arǝia ka. Wun nǝ̀ pè anzali pas tangna, sǝ pà wu nǝ̀ ak tangna ɗàng.
\v 13 Ɓǝ̀ wun nǝ̀ kpata anzongcau mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, mǝnana ǝn nggǝ tsǝka wuni yalung, sǝ wun nǝ̀ tsǝkir wun, wun nǝ̀ peǎ ka, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tsǝk wun, wun nǝ̀ duk múrû, pà wun nǝ̀ duk nggilatau ɗàng.\f + \fr 28:13 \fq wun nǝ̀ duk múrû, pà wun nǝ̀ duk nggilatau ɗàng \ft ko <<wun nǝ̀ duk mǝdǝmba amúr anzali, pà wun nǝ̀ duk rítǎu aɓatea ɗàng.>>\f*
\v 14 Cè wu kyanggi kǝɓè atà anzongcau mǝnana ǝn nggǝ pà wun yalung ngga, a bu-mǝlì ko a bu-mǝnggare, aban kpata aɓea aɓakuli andǝ peri abania ɗàng.
\s1 Tangnakusǝu mala mgbikiru
\sp Musa lidǝmba nǝ banggi amǝ Isǝrayila cau ama:
\p 
\v 15 Sǝama ɓǝ̀ wu ɓinǝ okî Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, sǝ pà wun nǝ̀ bwal anzongcau andǝ angguracau male mǝnana ǝn nggǝ tsǝka wun yalung nǝ ɓabum wun kat raka, amǝnia yì asuban kat ka, à nǝ̀ sulǝ amur wun, sǝ à nǝ̀ akà wun dǝmba.
\p 
\v 16 Suban nǝ̀ do amur wun aɓa là, sǝ suban nǝ̀ do amur wun a ɓaban.
\p 
\v 17 Suban nǝ̀ do amur ndakade andǝ tasau sùrǝ̀ gir mò.
\p 
\v 18 Suban nǝ̀ sulǝ amur ɓǝl amuna ma'wun, andǝ ɓǝlagir mala nzali ma'wun, sǝ amur domwan mala amuna-ndá, andǝ amuna-mbùl andǝ amuna-nzur ma'wun.
\p 
\v 19 Aɓa puro mô andǝ kutio mô ka suban nǝ̀ yiu amuro.
\p 
\v 20 Yahweh nǝ ɓamúrì, nǝ̀ tasǝa wun asuban, andǝ múrzurǝkya, andǝ ɗwanyi kum lùmsǝo mala kàné ma'wun aɓa gìr mǝnana kat wu tsǝk bù wun arǝì ama wun nǝ̀ pè ka, she ɓǝ̀ wu kiɗikina, tà wun twalna akaurǝa ka, atàcau mala atúró mǝɓike ma'wun mǝnana à tsǝa wu pǝlǝ nzǝm wun arǝ Yahweh, wu ginǝki ka.
\v 21 Yahweh nǝ̀ tasǝa wun akwánó-twàl-là amǝ'wal-luî, mǝnana à nǝ̀ lanzǝ arǝ wun, she ɓǝà twalnata wun aɓa nzali mǝnana wu kǝ kutio ace ê ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga.
\v 22 Yahweh nǝ̀ kok wun nǝ akwánó mal-ɓwa, andǝ ɓauwa, andǝ bàndà, andǝ ɓiki pi mala bân, andǝ tǝla-mbulo,\f + \fr 28:22 \fq tǝla-mbulo \ft ko <<nggeabyau ko lwa>>\f* andǝ kiɗiki mala agirɓaban nǝ nyàɗàng andǝ kwàpì; amǝnia yì agir'mur'mwana ka à nǝ̀ pǝrta wun she ɓǝà twalnata wun ngga.
\v 23 Ɓamǝsǝ kuli mǝnana amur wun ngga nǝ̀ pàk kǝla bolo-bángŋá, sǝ nzali mǝnana aɓata kusǝ wun ngga nǝ̀ candǝe kǝla bolo-candǝa.
\v 24 Yahweh nǝ̀ tsǝk mbulo mala nzali ma'wun ɓǝ̀ pǝlǝ kǝkǝri. Kǝkǝri nǝ̀ sulǝo amur wun nǝ kuli she ɓǝ̀ wu kiɗikina ka.
\p 
\v 25 Yahweh nǝ̀ tsǝk aɓiwun amǝbura ɓǝà gandǝ wun. Wun nǝ̀ pur aban ká arǝ aɓiwun amǝbura a njar mwashat, sǝ wun nǝ̀ mesǝ nǝ mire a ɓadǝmbia arǝ anjargula tongno-nong-ɓari. Wun nǝ̀ duk gìr kàrmúrû aban anzali-murǝm mala ɓanza.
\v 26 Alú wun nǝ̀ duk girlina ace koya nyal a bumkuli, andǝ anyam-ɓabondo, sǝ kǝɓwa pà kàm nǝ̀ pǝria ɗàng.
\v 27 Yahweh nǝ̀ kok wun nǝ ceakúmsǝǎm mala Masar, nǝ rǝu-mwarkya andǝ npenye-gula, andǝ kwa'nzwari andǝ kwánó oakiban, mǝnana à pà nǝ̀ gandǝ sonzǝia raka.
\v 28 Yahweh nǝ̀ kok wun nǝ ɓamúr-pǝlǝa, andǝ do-nte, andǝ zurǝì mala ɗenyicau.
\v 29 Nǝ pwari a kùli, wun nǝ̀ nggǝ harǝkiban kǝla nte mǝnana kǝ harǝkiban aɓa pǝndǝa ka. Pà wun nǝ̀ kum lidǝmba aɓa koyagir mǝnana wu pè ka ɗàng. Kǝ parban andǝ kum ɓǝmbǝriban na wun nǝ̀ do aɓate koya pwari ka, sǝ kǝɓwa pà kàm nǝ̀ amsǝ wun ɗàng.
\p 
\v 30 Awu nǝ pur'amur ɓwama sǝ ɓeɓwa nǝ̀ yia gbárí. Awu nǝ ɓak ɓala sǝ a pà wunǝ do aɓalǝi ɗàng. Awu nǝ pandǝ anggun-anap sǝ a pà wunǝ lì ɓǝlea ɗàng.
\v 31 Aɓio amǝbura nǝ̀ wàl ndá mô a mǝsǝo, sǝ a pà wunǝ ok nyame a kuno ɗàng. À nǝ̀ umnǝ mǝdambǝriso mò a mǝsǝo nǝ̀ rǝcandǝa, sǝ à pà nǝ̀ nyesǝo wi ɗàng. Aɓio amǝbura nǝ̀ pwan domwan mala anzur mô, sǝ kǝɓwa pà kàm nǝ̀ amsǝo ɗàng.
\v 32 A mǝsǝo, sǝ à nǝ̀ bwalki amunio amuna-burana andǝ amuna-mamǝna, à nǝ̀ umnǝia a nzali mala aɓea ɓwana; awu nǝ soamǝsǝo nǝ nzal kullimuria pwari anzǝm pwari, sǝ rǝcandǝa pà kàm a buo mala pàk kǝgir ɗàng.
\v 33 Aɓwana mala ɓè nzali mǝnana wu súrǝ̀ia raka à nǝ̀ lì ɓǝlagir mǝnana nzali ma'wun pusǝ ka, andǝ mala koya gìr mǝnana wu pàktúró ace kǝ̀rkǝ́r ka. Pà wu nǝ̀ kum kǝgir ɗàng shekǝ parban andǝ gìr'kwanrǝu koya pwari.
\v 34 Gìr mǝnana amǝsǝo nǝ̀ sǝn ngga nǝ̀ tsǝo a múrpǝlǝa.
\v 35 Yahweh nǝ̀ kok wun arǝ ankūnǝ wun andǝ akusǝ wun nǝ ceakúmsǝǎm mǝɓike, mǝnana à pà nǝ̀ gandǝ sonzǝe raka; à nǝ̀ aki rǝ wun kat, twal a ɓakusǝ wun aban ká a ɓong wun.
\v 36 Yahweh nǝ̀ umnǝ wun andǝ murǝm ma'wun mǝnana wun nǝ̀ tsǝa amur wun ngga a ɓè nzali mǝnana wu súrǝì ɗàng, sǝ aká wun gbal ka à súrǝì raka. Akano ka wun nǝ̀ peri aban aɓea ɓakuli mana à peǎ nǝ nggun andǝ tali ka.
\v 37 Wun nǝ̀ duk agir kàrmúrû, andǝ oalban, andǝ ɓangginǝban aɓalǝ aɓwana mǝnana kat Yahweh nǝ̀ tsǝa à nǝ̀ umnǝ wun kàm ngga.
\p 
\v 38 Wun nǝ̀ ɓealɓeale kpǝm a ɓaban ma'wun, sǝ wun nǝ̀ pwan bǝti acemǝnana doshi nǝ̀ ya lì.
\v 39 Wun nǝ̀ pandǝki anggun-anap sǝ wun nǝ̀ būnzǝia, sǝama pà wu nǝ̀ nu mùr aɓǝla-nggunì, ko wun nǝ̀ tūki aɓǝlea ɗàng, acemǝnana anggwaso nǝ̀ lia.
\v 40 Anggun-olif nǝ̀ to a koya ban aɓa nzali ma'wun, sǝama pà wu nǝ̀ hasǝ mùruí arǝ wun ɗàng acemǝnana aɓǝla-olif nǝ̀ rá.
\v 41 Wun nǝ̀ ɓǝl amuna-burana andǝ amuna-mamǝna sǝ à pà nǝ̀ duk ama'wun ɗàng, acemǝnana aɓiwun amǝbura nǝ̀ pwania à nǝ̀ umnǝia a nzali guro.
\v 42 Adoshi nǝ̀ li anggun ma'wun kat andǝ agirɓaban mala nzali ma'wun.
\v 43 Amǝ'kúnɗàngna mǝnana à do aɓalǝ wun ngga, à nǝ̀ nggǝ loapa wun a kùli aɓa kum lidǝmba, sǝ wun ngga, wun nǝ̀ nggǝ nyar a nzali aɓa ká tǝ̀r.
\v 44 Yià ka à nǝ̀ nggǝ pa wun tangna, sǝ pà wun nǝ̀ kumô wun nǝ̀ pea wia tangna ɗàng. A masǝlǝate ka à nǝ̀ duk múrû, sǝ wun nǝ̀ duk nggilatau.\f + \fr 28:44 \fq à nǝ̀ duk múrû, sǝ wun nǝ̀ duk nggilatau \ft ko <<à nǝ̀ duk mǝdǝmba amúr wun, sǝ wun nǝ̀ duk rítǎu aɓatea.>>\f*
\v 45 Amǝnia yì asuban kat ka à nǝ̀ yiu amur wun. À nǝ̀ pǝrta wun, sǝ à nǝ̀ yia kasǝmúr wun, sheɓǝ̀ kiɗikina ka, acemǝnana wu okî Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ɗàng, sǝ wu bwal anzongcau male andǝ anê male mǝnana pa wun ngga ɗàng.
\v 46 Amǝnia yì asuban ngga, à nǝ̀ duk gir'lǝmdǝa, andǝ gir-gyambǝliban, aban wun wunǝ amǝ'kà wun tàtǝ́k.
\v 47 Mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana wu kpata cau mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ banɓoarnado andǝ ɓabumpwasǝa raka, kat andǝ amani ama yì ka pa wun agir kat nyangsang ngga.
\v 48 Acemani ka, aɓiwun amǝbura mǝnana Yahweh nǝ̀ tasǝia arǝ wun ngga, wun nǝ̀ pàkkia wia túró kǝla aguro, aɓa nzala, andǝ mǝsamur, andǝ ɗwanyi gìr'nggūrǝu, andǝ tǝla agir kat. Yahweh nǝ̀ gangndǝia wun nggun-rya mala bolo-candǝa a myal wun, she ɓǝ̀ kiɗikina wun ngga.
\p 
\v 49 Yahweh nǝ̀ yinǝ aɓwana mala ɓè nzali kuko a masǝlǝata ɓanza arǝ wun; à nǝ̀ yia zuppi amur wun kǝla nkwang; aɓwana mala nzali na mǝnana pà wun nǝ̀ bwalta lasǝia raka;
\v 50 aɓwana na nǝ dǝm-ndwakan, mǝnana à kǝ lǝmdǝ pagulo aban ajamgula ɗang, sǝ à kǝ sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr mala amuna raka.
\v 51 À nǝ̀ lì agirkusǝu ma'wun andǝ agirɓaban ma'wun, sheɓǝ̀ wu kiɗikina ka. À pà nǝ̀ nyingga wun kǝ mǝsǝsa, ko bǝsa mùr ɓǝla-anap, ko mùrú olif, ko kǝ muna-ndá, ko kǝ muna-mbul, ko kǝ muna-nzur ɗang, sheɓǝ̀ à tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nà wun wu uenaɓà ka.
\v 52 À nǝ̀ gumbǝli wun nǝ lwa a koya là ma'wun sheɓǝ̀ akanggǝrang sheran amǝ'dāh'rike mǝnana wu gūlì arǝia ka, à kpakina kat arǝ alá ma'wun aɓa nzali mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pà wun ngga.
\v 53 Wun nǝ̀ shak nyam amuna ma'wun amuna-burana andǝ amuna-mamǝna mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun pà wun ngga,\f + \fr 28:53 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pǝris 26:29; 2Amur 6:25-29; Ir 19:9; Keb 2:20; 4:10; Ezǝk 5:10\xt*\f* atàcau mala gumbǝliban nǝ lwa andǝ tanni mǝkǝ̀rkǝ́rnì mǝnana aɓiwun amǝbura nǝ̀ túr wun aɓalǝi ka.
\v 54 Nggearǝ ɓwabura mǝnana mǝ'ɓukɓuka na sǝ mǝ'sǝn-mǝsǝswatǝr na aɓalǝ wun ngga, pà nǝ̀ earî mǝ'eambi, ko māmí mǝnana earkiyice ka, ko acili amuni mana à ue ka ɓǝà lì girlina atè ɗàng;
\v 55 pà nǝ̀ eare nǝ̀ pè kǝɓwa ateà nyam amuni mana kǝ̀ shak ka ɗàng, acemǝnana kǝgìr ueki wi ɗàng, atàcau mala gumbǝliban nǝ lwa andǝ tanni mǝkǝ̀rkǝ́rnì mala tǝla girlina mǝnana aɓiwun amǝbura nǝ̀ yinǝi amur wun arǝ alá ma'wun kat ka.
\v 56 Ɓwama mǝnana mǝ'ɓukɓuka na sǝ mǝ'sǝn-mǝsǝswatǝr na aɓalǝ wun, mana pà nǝ̀ eare ɓakusǝi ɓǝ̀ je nzali raka, ace ɓukɓuka male andǝ tsǝkiru male ka, nǝ̀ dumnǝ ɓike aban burí mǝnana earkiyice ka, andǝ muni muna-ɓwabura, andǝ muni muna-ɓwama;
\v 57 yale gó mǝnana pur arǝì, andǝ bangna-muna male mǝnana loa ɓǝle ka, nǝ̀ shè aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa, ace tǝla koyagir aɓa gumbǝliban nǝ lwa andǝ tanni mǝkǝ̀rkǝ́rnì mana aɓiwun amǝbura nǝ̀ yinǝi amur wun arǝ alá ma'wun kat ka.
\s1 Mgbikiru kǝ yinǝ kiɗikiban
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 58 Ɓǝ̀ pà wun nǝ̀ tsǝkir wun, wun nǝ̀ kpata acau mala nggurcau mǝnia kat, mǝnana à gilǝia aɓa mǝnia yì malǝmce, ace mǝnana wun nǝ̀ ɓanggî mǝnia yì lullǝu mǝɓoarɓwe andǝ mǝkàrmuruì mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun raka,
\v 59 Yahweh nǝ̀ tasǝa wun wunǝ amuna ma'wun andǝ amǝkà wun akwánó-twàl-là amǝ'wal-luî, andǝ arǝkwana mǝɓike mǝnana à kǝ gandǝ sonzǝia ɗàng, andǝ arǝpangŋa mǝnana tea pà nǝ̀ mal raka.
\v 60 Nǝ̀ yinǝ akwánó mala Masar ɗǝm amur wun, akwánó mǝnana wu ɓanggia wia ka; à nǝ̀ lanzǝ arǝ wun.
\v 61 Ɗǝm ngga, Yahweh nǝ̀ yinǝ arǝpangŋa andǝ koya gìr'mur'mwana amur wun mǝnana à bang cau malea aɓa mǝnia yi Malǝmce mala nggurcau raka, she ɓǝà kiɗikina wun ngga.
\v 62 Wun mǝnana wu làkkì kǝla anlero mǝnana a bumkuli ka, aɓwana kpokyak na à nǝ̀ ue ka, acemǝnana wu okî Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun raka.
\v 63 Kǝla mǝnana Yahweh pàk banɓoarnado amur wun ace pakka wun mǝɓoarne, sǝ ace hatǝki wun ngga, anggo gbal sǝ Yahweh nǝ̀ pàk banɓoarnado amur wun ace kiɗiki wun andǝ twalta wun. À nǝ̀ ukki nlerǝ wun a nzali mǝnana wun ndo wu kǝ ká ê ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga.
\p 
\v 64 Yahweh nǝ̀ mesǝki wun arǝ anzali kat, twal a ɓè kún ɓanza aban ká ɓè kúni. Akàm sǝ wun nǝ̀ nggá kpata aɓea aɓakuli mǝnana à peǎ nǝ nggun andǝ tali ka, aɓakuli mǝnana wun wunǝ aká wun ngga wu kǝ peri abania ɗiɗyal raka.\f + \fr 28:64 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pǝris 26:33; Nggur 4:27; Nehe 1:8; Ezǝk 22:15\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 65 Aɓalǝ anzali mǝno ka pà wun nǝ̀ kum makrǝu ɗang, sǝ ban usǝlǝo pa kàm ace ɓakusǝ wun ɗàng; Yahweh nǝ̀ pa wun ɓabum gǝggǝlya andǝ mǝsǝkialǝkya andǝ ɓabum ɓungia.
\v 66 Yilǝmi wun nǝ̀ gyar aɓa bumtutya a ɓadǝm wun. Wun nǝ̀ do aɓa ɓangciu du andǝ pwari, sǝ pà wun nǝ̀ kum makɓalǝu mala àwá mala yilǝmi wun ɗàng.
\v 67 Nǝ dǝmbari ka wun nǝ̀ bang ama, <<Ɓǝ́ pwarikpana,>> sǝ nǝ pwarikpǝra ka, wun nǝ̀ bang ama, <<Ɓǝ́ dǝmbari na>> ace ǝn'o mala ɓabum mǝnana wun nǝ̀ oè, andǝ agir mǝnana amǝsǝ wun nǝ̀ sǝnia ka.
\v 68 Yahweh nǝ̀ nyesǝ wun a Masar aɓalǝ awaru-bǝsa, nǝ njar mǝnana ǝn bang nǝma pà wun nǝ̀ sǝni ɗǝm raka. Akano ka wun nǝ̀ pà ɓamurǝ wun kǝla aguro aburana andǝ amamǝna aban aɓiwun amǝbura, sǝ kǝɓwa pà nǝ̀ kúr wun ɗàng.
\c 29
\p 
\v 1 Amǝno ka à nda ka acau mala kùrcau mǝnana Yahweh banggi Musa ama ɓǝ̀ pè nǝ amǝ Isǝrayila aɓa nzali Mowap, kpapi andǝ kùrcau mǝnana angŋa dǝmba kùrni nǝia a Horep ka.
\s1 Ɓǝsǝlǝ kùrcau ɓǝ̀ duk bǝshe
\p 
\v 2 Sǝ Musa tunǝ amǝ Isǝrayila kat, banggia wia ama: <<Wu sǝnǝna gìr mǝnana Yahweh pè a mǝsǝ wun aɓa nzali Masar ka, yì gìr mǝnana pàkkî Firona andǝ amǝ'túró male kat, andǝ nzali male kat ka.
\v 3 Amǝsǝ wun sǝn amǝno yì anggea tanni, andǝ agir-lǝmdǝa andǝ agir-gyambǝliban mǝgulke ka.
\v 4 Sǝama ba yalung ngga Yahweh pà wun ɓabum mana wun nǝ̀ bwalte, ko amǝsǝu mana wun nǝ̀ sǝni, ko akiru mana wun nǝ̀ ok gìr mana wu kùtí aɓalǝi ka ɗàng.
\v 5 Apǝlǝa lumi-ine ǝn gingnǝ wun aɓa pǝɗanban. Adaura ma'wun andǝ ankura ma'wun tsǝuriki ɗang.
\v 6 Wu kum girlina mana wun nǝ̀ li, ko mùr-anap ko mba mana wun nǝ̀ nu ka ɗàng, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ kania wun ama Yahweh ka nda Ɓakuli ma'wun.
\v 7 Sǝ lang wu bwalna man yì ban ngga, Sihon murǝm Heshbon, andǝ Og, murǝm Bashan, à puro ace yinǝ munǝo arǝ sǝm, sǝama sǝm liǎ.
\v 8 Sǝm ak nzali malea sǝ sǝm gapi amǝkà Ruben andǝ amǝkà Gad andǝ gauwa-tsùrú mala amǝkà Manasa ɓǝ̀ duk nzali liɓala malea.
\v 9 Acemani ka, wu bwal acau mala kùrcau mǝnia ka sǝ wu peǎ, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu kum lidǝmba aɓa koya gìr mana wun nǝ̀ pàk ka.
\p 
\v 10 <<Yalung ngga wu ndya wu cam kat aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga; amúrû mala atau ma'wun, andǝ aɓwana-mǝgule ma'wun, andǝ amǝgulo ma'wun, andǝ aburana mala amǝ Isǝrayila kat,
\v 11 amuna mǝkeke ma'wun, andǝ amālá wun, andǝ abǝri mǝnana à nda atà wun a kàttì, twal a ban ɓwa mǝnana kǝ kasǝa wun nggun aban ká aban ɓwa mǝnana kǝ ɗàrǝa wun mùr ka.
\v 12 Wun nda kani yalung, ace mǝnana wun nǝ̀ kùtí aɓa kùrcau mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, mǝnana kùrì nǝ kángìr, mǝnana yì, Yahweh, Ɓakuli ma'wun kǝ pè nǝ wun yalung,
\v 13 ace mǝnana nǝ̀ kwakita wun ɓǝ̀ wu duk aɓwana male yalung, sǝ ɗǝm ngga ɓǝ̀ duk Ɓakuli ma'wun, kǝla mǝnana pàcau aban wun, sǝ kǝla mǝnana kánbì aká wun, aban Ibǝrayim, aban Ishaku, sǝ aban Yakupu ka.
\v 14 Wun nda nǝ nǝmurǝ wun ǝn nggǝ pàk man yì kùrcau andǝ man yì kángìr ka ɗàng,
\v 15 nda nǝ koya ɓwa mǝnana kat nda kani atà sǝm yalung aban came aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm, andǝ ɓwa mǝnana kat pà kani atà sǝm yalung raka.
\p 
\v 16 <<Wun ngga wu sǝlǝnace do ma'sǝm a nzali Masar, andǝ kutio ma'sǝm nǝɓalǝ anzali mǝnana sǝm kutiki nǝɓalǝia a njar aban yiu ka.
\v 17 Sǝ wu sǝnǝna agir'ɓeami malea, yì ankúl mǝnana à peǎ nǝ nggun, andǝ tali, andǝ bolo-azǝrfa, andǝ bolo-njengǝlan, mǝnana à nda aɓalǝia ka.
\v 18 Wu yál rǝ wun cè kǝ ɓwabura, ko ɓwama, ko ɓekǝ tàu ko ɓala aɓalǝ wun yalung mǝnana ɓabumi na rǝ ɗeki kpata Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ace ká kpata aɓakuli mala anzali mǝno ka ɗàng. Wu tsǝkir wun cè à kum kǝɓwa aɓalǝ wun mǝnana nǝ̀ duk nlerǝ pusǝ ɓǝle mala barya andǝ mǝ'lulle ka ɗàng.\f + \fr 29:18 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ib 12:15\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 19 Lang ɓwa kǝla mǝno ok acau mala mǝnia yì kùrcau mǝnana à pè nǝ kángìr, sǝ twalî ɓamurì ama ndanǝ tsǝkbu, sǝ pàk ɗenyicau a ɓabumi ama, <Ko ɓǝ̀ ǝn gya aɓa ɓamurcandǝa mem ngga, kǝgìr mǝɓane pà kàm nǝ̀ kumam ɗang.> Mǝnia ka nǝ̀ yinǝ kiɗiki mala mǝpwale atà mǝ'ime.
\v 20 Yahweh pà nǝ̀ eare nǝ̀ twalîbanì ɗàng, a kún mani ka bumlulla mǝpìne mala Yahweh nǝ̀ earke amur man yì ɓwa ka, sǝ asuban mǝnana kat à gilǝia aɓa malǝmce mǝnia ka à nǝ̀ sulǝ amurí, sǝ Yahweh nǝ̀ esǝki lùllǝì a ɓanza.
\v 21 Sǝ Yahweh nǝ̀ tàrrì aɓalǝ atau mala amǝ Isǝrayila kat ace kum gìr'mur'mwana, aɓa kpata asuban kat mala kùrcau mǝnana à gilǝia aɓa mǝnia yì Malǝmce Nggurcau ka.
\p 
\v 22 <<Anza mala amuna ma'wun mǝnana à nǝ̀ lo anzǝm wun, andǝ abǝri mana à nǝ̀ purki arǝ anzali bansauwa sǝ à nǝ̀ yiu ka, à nǝ̀ sǝn agir'mur'mwana mǝnana kumǝna mǝno yì nzali, andǝ akwánó mǝnana Yahweh soapi wi sǝ túrí aɓa rǝkwana ka.
\v 23 Nzalinì puppup nǝ̀ pì kǝring nǝ atali-earbǝsa, sǝ nǝ̀ pǝlǝ kpakanban tuɓamur mǝnana kǝgir pà kàm à nǝ̀ ɓeali aɓalǝi nǝ̀ soa ko nǝ̀ gul ka ɗàng, sǝ kǝ bondo pa nǝ̀ tò kam ɗàng; nzali ma'wun nǝ̀ pa kǝla anggea-là Sodom andǝ Gomora, andǝ Adǝma andǝ Zeboyim, mǝnana Yahweh kiɗikia aɓa bumlulla male mǝɓike ka.
\v 24 Aɓwapǝndǝa kat nǝ̀ ɗiban ama, <Ace mana sǝ Yahweh pakkî nzali man gìr mǝnia anggo? Mana yinǝ pi mala mǝnia yì nggea bumlulla ka?>
\v 25 Sǝ aɓwe nǝ̀ pà eare ama, <Nda acemǝnana à vwakibuia arǝ kùrcau mala Yahweh, Ɓakuli mala akeâ, mǝnana pangnǝia lang pusǝia à purî ɓá nzali Masar ka.
\v 26 À kùtí a kpata aɓea aɓakuli sǝ à peri abania, aɓakuli mǝnana à súrǝ̀ia ɗiɗyal raka, aɓakuli mǝnana Yahweh na pea wia raka.
\v 27 Acemani ka, bumlulla mala Yahweh pi arǝ man yì nzali, sǝ yinǝ koya suban mǝnana à gilǝì a mǝnia yì malǝmce ka amurí.
\v 28 Aɓa bumlulla mǝkǝ̀rkǝ́rnì andǝ bum-ukkia mǝgule, uia aɓa nzali malea, sǝ ramtea aɓa ɓè nzali, kǝla mǝnana à pàk yalung ngga.>
\p 
\v 29 <<Agir ɓa-sǝmbǝrǝa ka, amala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝma, sǝ agir mǝnana à lǝmdǝia ka, ama'sǝma sǝ mala amuna ma'sǝma tàtǝ́k, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm kpata acau mala nggurcau mǝnia ka.>>
\c 30
\s1 Pwanzali andǝ Twalbani
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 1 Lang agir mǝnia kat nǝ̀ yiu amur wun, yì atsǝkbu andǝ asuban, mǝnana ǝn tsǝka wunia aɓadǝm wun, sǝ ɓalǝ wun yi kasǝa arǝia aɓalǝ anzali mǝnana kat Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun mesǝkina wun kàm,
\v 2 sǝ lang wun wunǝ amuna ma'wun wun nǝ̀ nyar aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, wun nǝ̀ oki wi nǝ ɓabum wun kat andǝ yilǝmi wun kat, wun nǝ̀ kpata acau mǝnana kat ǝn nggǝ pà wun yalung ngga,
\v 3 nda wuni Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ panzǝki wun ɓǝ̀ wu nyarî bwalban-aguro ka. Nǝ̀ sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr ma'wun, sǝ nǝ̀ ramgi wun arǝ anzali mǝnana kat yì Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun mesǝkina wun kàm ngga.\f + \fr 30:3 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pǝris 26:40-45; 1Amur 8:46-50; Ir 29:14; Ezǝk 16:53; Zaf 3:20\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 4 Sǝ ko ɓǝ̀ à mesǝki wun arǝ abân kuko aɓa ɓanza ka, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ ramgi wun kano, sǝ nǝ̀ nyesǝ wun.
\v 5 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ yinǝ wun aɓa nzali mǝnana aká wun é pǝlǝ malea ka, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu é ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga. Sǝ yì ka nǝ̀ tsǝa ɓǝ̀ wu kum lidǝmba sǝ ɓǝ̀ wu hatǝki wu kútì aká wun.
\p 
\v 6 Sǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga nǝ̀ gau wun wunǝa ɓabum-candǝcau ma'wun andǝ ɓabum candǝcau mala amuna ma'wun, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu earce Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ ɓabum mwashat andǝ yilǝmi wun kat, sǝ ɓǝ̀ wu auwa.
\v 7 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tsǝk asuban mǝnia kat ka amur aɓiwun-amǝbura mǝnana à kǝ ɓinǝmúr wun sǝ à kǝ ɓikia wun ngga.
\v 8 Sǝ wun nǝ̀ okî Yahweh ɗǝm, sǝ wun nǝ̀ bwal anzongcau male mǝnana kat ǝn tsǝka wun yalung ngga.
\v 9 Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ̀ tsǝa wun nǝ̀ nyakǝti aɓa kum lidǝmba aɓalǝ atúró mala abu wun kat, aɓa ɓǝl amuna, aɓa ɓǝla mala agirkusǝu mala adomwan ma'wun, sǝ aɓa kum aɓǝlagir ɓaban. Bum Yahweh nǝ̀ nyare nǝ̀ pwasǝ arǝ wun kǝla mǝnana bumi pwasǝ arǝ aká wun ngga,
\v 10 lang wu okî Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, wu bwal anzongcau, andǝ akasǝcau mǝnana à nda a gile aɓa Malǝmce mala Nggurcau man, sǝ wu pǝlǝa aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ ɓabum wun kat andǝ yilǝmi wun kat ka.
\s1 Twal do nǝyilǝmu ko lú
\sp Musa banggi amǝ Isǝrayila ama:
\p 
\v 11 Nzongcau mǝnia ǝn nggǝ tsǝka wun yalung ngga, kútì rǝcandǝa ma'wun ɗang, ɗǝm ngga pà kuko nǝ wun ɗàng.
\v 12 Pà a kùli, mǝnana wun nǝ̀ na ama, <<Yana nǝ̀ eapa sǝm a kùli, sǝ nǝ̀ sulǝi aban sǝm ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm oè sǝ ɓǝ̀ sǝm pè ka?>>
\v 13 Ɗǝm ngga pà a nkaring nggeamùr, mǝnana wun nǝ̀ na ama, <<Yana nǝ̀ kákà sǝm a nkaring nggeamùr sǝ nǝ̀ yinǝi aban sǝm ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm oè sǝ ɓǝ̀ sǝm pè ka?>>
\v 14 Sǝama cê ka nda a nkanggari wun tù. Nda aɓa kún wun andǝ ɓabum wun, ace mǝnana wun nǝ̀ gandǝ kpate ka.\f + \fr 30:14 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Rom 10:6-8\xt*\ft .\f*
\s1 Masǝlǝata cau mala Musa
\p 
\v 15 Wu kwakikir wun! Yalung ngga, mǝ nda ban pa wun njar, ɓǝ̀ wu twal mwashat atà amǝnia ka: yilǝmu andǝ mǝɓoarne, ko lú andǝ mǝɓike.
\v 16 Mǝ nda ban tsǝka wun nzongcau yalung ama, wu earce Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, wu bwal anzongcau, andǝ akasǝcau, andǝ anggurcau, sǝ wu gya aɓa njar male. Ɓǝ̀ wu pàk mǝnia ka, wun nǝ̀ dum nǝyilǝmu, wun nǝ̀ bundǝo. Sǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga nǝ̀ tsǝka wun bù aɓa nzali mǝnana wun nǝ̀ kùtí kam, wun nǝ̀ é ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga.
\p 
\v 17 Sǝama ɓǝ̀ ɓabum wun pǝlǝa, sǝ wu ɓinǝ kwakikir wun, wu pǝlǝ rǝ wun aban peri aban aɓea ɓakuli andǝ kpatea ka,
\v 18 mǝ nda ban nunkir wun ado ama, mǝsǝcau wun nǝ̀ ueɓà. Sǝ yilǝmi wun pà nǝ̀ sauwa aɓa nzali mǝnana wun nǝ̀ yàllî Nggeasala Jodan, wun nǝ̀ ká ê ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga ɗàng.
\p 
\v 19 Yalung ngga ǝn nggǝ tunǝ kuli andǝ nzali ɓǝà duk amǝ'nakún arǝ wun ama, ǝn tsǝ́ngŋǝ̀nà yilǝmu andǝ lú, tsǝkbu andǝ súban aɓadǝm wun. Acemani ka, wu twal yilǝmu, ace mǝnana wun, wunǝ amuna-wun, andǝ amǝká-wun ngga ɓǝ̀ wu do nǝyilǝmu.
\v 20 Wun nǝ̀ gandǝ twal earce Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, wun nǝ̀ oki wi, sǝ wun nǝ̀ pa ɓamur wun kat-kat abani. Mǝnia ka nda kunkurǝm mala yilǝmu aban wun. Yilǝmi wun nǝ̀ sauwa aɓa nzali mǝnana Yahweh kánbi aká-wun, aban Ibǝrayim, aban Ishaku, sǝ aban Yakupu, ama nǝ̀ pea wia ka.
\c 31
\s1 À twal Jesǝwa ɓǝ̀ duk ɓwamǝgule amur amǝ Isǝrayila
\p 
\v 1 Pǝlǝa Musa wario kya ne amǝ Isǝrayila kat, amǝnia yì acau ka,
\v 2 ama:
\pi1 Mim adyan ngga, apǝlǝa mem lùmsǝ̀nà gbǝman-mwashat nǝ lumi-ɓari; pà mǝ nǝ gandǝ lidǝmba nǝ dupa wun ɓwamǝgule ɗǝm ɗàng. Yahweh bangŋǝ́nàm ama, <<We ka, a pà wunǝ yàllî nkaring Jodan mǝnia ka ɗàng.>>
\v 3 Sǝama Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun nǝ nggearǝì ka nǝ̀ aka wun dǝmba nǝ̀ yàl a nkaring. Nǝ̀ nggá kiɗiki nzali mala aɓwapǝndǝa mǝnia ka aɓadǝm wun, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu ak nzalinì arǝia ɓǝ̀ duk girkuma ma'wun ngga. Jesǝwa nda ɓwa mǝnana nǝ̀ dupa wun a dǝmba lang wun nǝ̀ yàl a nkaring ngga, kǝla mana Yahweh bang ngga.
\v 4 Sǝ Yahweh ka nǝ̀ pakkia wia gìr, kǝla mana pakkî Sihon andǝ Og, yì amurǝma mala amǝ'Amor, sǝ kǝla mana pakkî nzali malea, lang yi twaltea kat ka.
\v 5 Yahweh nǝ̀ tasǝia a ɓabù wun, sǝ dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ pakkia wia agir mana kat ǝn tsǝka wun nzongcau nǝma ɓǝ̀ wu pakkia wia ka.
\v 6 Wu dum nǝ rǝcandǝa, sǝ wu pangnǝ mǝsǝkàng-kàngŋa. Ɓǝ̀ ɓangciu ɓǝkǝa pakka wun, ko ǝn'ò pàkka wun arǝia ɗàng. Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga, nda atà wun; pà nǝ̀ mak wun, ko nǝ̀ ɗeki wun ɗàng.
\p 
\v 7 Musa pǝlǝa tunǝ Jesǝwa, sǝ banggi wi aɓadǝm amǝ Isǝrayila kat ama:
\pi1 Dum nǝ rǝcandǝa, sǝ wu pangnǝ mǝsǝkàng-kàngŋa, acemǝnana a nda awu nǝ kánǝ aɓwana mǝnia ka aɓa nzali mǝnana Yahweh kánbi akeâ ama, nǝ̀ pea wia ka.\f + \fr 31:7 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Nggur 1:8,35; 8:1; 11:9,21; 31:20; Ezǝk 20:42\xt*\ft .\f* Sǝ dumǝna púp, awu nǝ gakia wia nzalinì kat, ɓǝ̀ duk gìr'liɓala malea.
\v 8 Yahweh nǝnggearǝì nǝ̀ kákò a dǝmba; nǝ̀ pà atò; pà nǝ̀ nyio ko nǝ̀ vwakibuì arǝò ɗàng. Cè ɓangciu pàkkô ko ɓabumo ɓungi ɗang.
\s1 Ɓal Nggurcau mala Ɓakuli bwāng aban aɓwana
\p 
\v 9 Pǝlǝa Musa gilǝ mǝnia yì nggurcau ka, sǝ pè apǝris, yià amǝkà Lawi, yià mana à twalkiyi akwati kùrcau mala Yahweh ka, atārǝia andǝ aɓwana-mǝgule kat mala amǝ Isǝrayila.
\v 10 Pǝlǝa Musa tsǝkia wia nzongcau ama:
\pi1 A masǝlǝata koya tongno-nong-ɓaria pǝlǝa, a pwari mana à tsǝì ace twalban tangna, aɓa Lamsan mala Do aɓalǝ Agumli,\f + \fr 31:10 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pǝris 23:34; Nggur 16:13\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 11 a kúnì mana amǝ Isǝrayila kat kǝ yiu nǝi à nǝ̀ ramba aɓadǝm Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, a ban mǝnana nǝ̀ tàrrì ka, wun nǝ̀ ɓal mǝnia yì nggurcau ka a ɓadǝmba amǝ Isǝrayila kat, ɓǝà oè nǝ kiria.
\v 12 Wu ramba aɓwe, aburana, andǝ amamǝna andǝ amuna, andǝ abǝri mana à ndanǝdo aɓalǝ wun arǝ alá ma'wun ngga, ace mǝnana ɓǝà kwakikiria, ɓǝà kànì ɓanggi Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, andǝ kpata acau mala nggurcau mǝnia ka pepè.
\v 13 Anggo ka amuna malea, mana à súrǝ̀ mǝnia yì nggurcau raka, dumǝna púp à nǝ̀ oè, à nǝ̀ kànì ɓanggi Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, aɓa do ma'wun kat a nzali mana wun ndo wun nǝ̀ yàllî Nggeasala Jodan wun nǝ̀ ká ê ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga.
\s1 Masǝlǝata kwarkiru mana Yahweh pè Musa ka
\p 
\v 14 Yahweh banggi Musa ama, <<Adyan ngga, pwari lú mò gbàshìnà. Tunǝ Jesǝwa, wu yiu kǝm, wu lǝmdǝ ɓamúr rǝ wun abanam aɓa Tara Ban-peri, ace mǝnana \f + \fr 31:14 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ɓal 27:19\xt*\ft .\f*mǝ pè wi gara mala pàktúró ka.>>
\p Anggo sǝ Musa andǝ Jesǝwa wario, à kya lǝmdǝ ɓamuria aɓa Tara Ban-peri.
\p 
\v 15 Pǝlǝa Yahweh pusǝrǝi a ban Tara aɓa pǝrɓang mana cam pǝrapǝra ka, sǝ pǝrɓangnî yi came amúr bankutio aɓa Tara.\f + \fr 31:15 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ɓal 12:5\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 16 Pǝlǝa Yahweh banggi Musa ama:
\pi1 A ndo awu nǝ o, a nǝ nggá usǝlǝo atà akeo,\f + \fr 31:16 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 47:30; 2Sam 7:12; 1Amur 2:10; 11:43; 14:20,31\xt*\ft .\f* sǝ aɓwana mǝnia ka, banì pà nǝ̀ sau ɗang, à nǝ̀ kùtí aɓa pàkki atúró gyatarǝu aban kpata abǝri ɓakuli mala nzali mǝno à malanǝ̀ ká kàm aɓalǝia ka. Yià ka, à nǝ̀ vwakibuia arǝàm, à nǝ̀ panzǝki kùrcau mǝnana ǝn kurì sǝnǝia ka.
\v 17 Sǝama a pwari mǝno ka, bumlulla mem nǝ̀ pi amúrià; mǝ nǝ túrià wia nzǝmam, sǝ mǝ nǝ sǝmbǝria wia ɓamǝsǝam, sǝ à nǝ̀ ueɓà; agir'mur'mwana pas andǝ atanni nǝ̀ yia sulǝ amúrià. A pwari mǝno ka, à nǝ̀ ɗiban ama, <<Amǝnia yì agir'mur'mwana ka, à yi kum sǝm anggo acemǝnana Ɓakuli ma'sǝm ngga, nyìngŋǝ̀nà sǝm, pa atà sǝm ɗǝm raka le?>>
\v 18 Mbak-kàngkàng, mǝ nǝ sǝmbǝria wia ɓamǝsǝam a pwari mǝno ka, ace ɓealɓikea mǝnana kat à pè, mana à pǝlǝ amǝ'kpata aɓea ɓakuli ka.
\pi1 
\v 19 Acemani ka, gilǝ mǝnia yì nggyal ka, sǝ wu kánì amǝ Isǝrayila; tsǝia ɓǝà kǝ tû nggyalnì, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ duk girnakun mem arǝia ka.
\v 20 Lang ǝn yinanǝia a nzali mana ǝn pacau nǝ kángìr aban akeâ nǝma mǝ nǝ pea wia, yì nzali mana kiura andǝ mur'nyi kǝ ɓang kàm, sǝ anzǝm mǝnana à lina agir, à ɗǝmgina sǝ à nyangina ka, pǝlǝa à nǝ̀ pǝlǝa aban aɓea aɓakuli, à nǝ̀ kpatea, à nǝ̀ nyesǝcem-ɓà, sǝ à nǝ̀ panzǝki kùrcau mem.
\v 21 Sǝ lang agir'mur'mwana pas andǝ atanni yina amúrià ka, mǝnia yì nggyal ka, nǝ̀ nakun arǝia; acemana ɓalǝ amǝ'keà ka, pà nǝ̀ lórǝ́ nggyalnì ɗàng. Ko kaniama mǝ yinǝia a nzali mana ǝn pacau nǝ kángìr nǝma mǝ nǝ pea wia ka, ǝn súrǝ́nà rǝ gìr mǝnana ɗenyicau malea nǝ̀ kánǝia pě ka.
\p 
\v 22 Anggo, sǝ Musa gilǝ mǝnia yì nggyal ka\f + \fr 31:22 \fq mǝnia yì nggyal ka \ft Sǝni a 32:1-43.\f* a pwari mǝno, sǝ kànî amǝ Isǝrayila nggyalnì.
\p 
\v 23 Pǝlǝa Yahweh ka, pè Jesǝwa, yì muna-ɓwabura mala Nun, nzongcau ama, <<We ka, dum nǝ rǝcandǝa sǝ wu pak mǝsǝkàng-kàngŋa, acemana awu nǝ kánǝ amǝ Isǝrayila a nzali mana ǝn pacau nǝ kángìr nǝma mǝ nǝ pea wia ka. Sǝ mim nǝ ɓamúràm ngga, mǝ nǝ pà atò.>>
\p 
\v 24 Anzǝm mana Musa malǝna gilǝ acau mala mǝnia yì nggurcau a malǝmce, twal a tite, kya bwal a masǝlǝate ka,
\v 25 pǝlǝa Musa pè amǝ'Lawi, yià mana à twalkiyi akwati kùrcau mala Yahweh ka, mǝnia yì nzongcau ka, ama:
\pi1 
\v 26 Wu twal mǝnia yì Malǝmce mala Kùrcau ka, wu tsǝì aɓa Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun. Mǝnia ka nǝ̀ do kǝla girnakun mem arǝ wun.
\v 27 Acemǝnana ǝn súrǝ́nàcè mgbikiru andǝ murcandǝa ma'wun. (Ɓǝ̀ yalung mana mǝ nda andǝamǝsǝàm più sǝ wu lidǝmba nǝ mgbikiru arǝ Yahweh ka, mgbikiru ma'wun nǝ̀ ɓikipa lang ǝn wuna ka.)
\v 28 Wu ramba aɓwana-mǝgule mala atau ma'wun andǝ amǝ'pagara ma'wun kat, ace mana ɓǝ̀ ǝn banggia wia amǝnia yì acau ka a kiria, ɓǝà oè sǝ mǝ tunǝ kuli andǝ nzali ɓǝà duk girnakun arǝia.
\v 29 Mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana ǝn sǝlǝna nǝma, anzǝm lú mem ngga, mbak-kàngkàng wun nǝ̀ duk amǝ'kìɗìkì kǝ̀rkǝ́r, wun nǝ̀ nying njargula mana ǝn tsǝka wun nzongcau nǝma ɓǝ̀ wu kpate ka. Sǝ apwari na à nǝ̀ yiu ka, aɓalǝia ka gìr'mur'mwana na nǝ̀ nggá sulǝ amúr wun, acemǝnana wun nǝ̀ pàk gìr mana mǝɓike na ka aɓadǝm Yahweh, wun nǝ̀ loasǝ bumlulla male, nǝ agir mana abú wun peǎ ka.
\s1 Nggyal mala Musa
\p 
\v 30 Pǝlǝa Musa bang acau mala mǝnia yì nggyal ka, twal a tite yi bwal a masǝlǝate, sǝ amǝ Isǝrayila mana à yi ram kat ka, à kǝ oè.
\c 32
\q1 
\v 1 Kwakikiro we kùli, sǝ mǝ nǝ nacau;
\q2 ɓanza ɓǝ̀ ok acau mana à kǝ̀ pur a kunam ngga.
\q1 
\v 2 Came ɓǝ̀ kanigir mem kpa kǝla mbulo,
\q2 sǝ acau mem ɓǝà sulǝo kǝla ncimna dǝmbari,
\q2 kǝla rakya mala mǝsǝ-mbulo amur lolloapì bondo,
\q2 kǝla nya mala mbulo-gula amur agirpwala.
\q1 
\v 3 Mim ngga, mǝ nǝ hamnǝ lullǝ Yahweh.
\q2 Ɓǝà pè Ɓakuli ma'sǝm gusǝlǝban!
\q1 
\v 4 Yi ka, nda Tali,
\q1 túró male lùmsǝ-puppup,
\q2 sǝ anjar male kat ka, à nda pepè.
\q1 Yì ka nda Ɓakuli mǝ'domǝsǝcaunì,
\q2 mana kǝ lǝmdǝ tàrban raka;
\q2 mǝ'ɓealɓoarna na sǝ kǝ pak gìr mana nda pepè ka.
\b
\q1 
\v 5 Kat andǝ amani ka, aɓwana male lǝmdǝì wi ɗwanyi domǝsǝcau,
\q2 à nda ka amuna male ɗǝm ɗàng acemǝnana à kumia nǝ mǝɓane.
\q2 Nza mala amǝ ɗwanyi kpata gìr a njarì na
\q2 andǝ amǝ kìɗìkì.
\q1 
\v 6 Ani sǝ wun nǝ mbwe Yahweh le,
\q2 yì wun amǝ'gǝmi andǝ amǝ'ɓanggia?
\q1 Sǝ yì ka, nda Tár wun, mana pusǝ wun ngga re?
\q2 Yì nǝ̀ pàk wun sǝ nda mana dumsǝ wun ngga re?
\q1 
\v 7 Ɓǝ̀ ɓalǝ wun kasǝa arǝ apwari do mana ɗiɗyal ka;
\q2 wu ɗenyinǝ apǝlǝkia mala anza mana à kutikina ka.
\q1 Wu ɗì tár wun, sǝ yì ka nǝ̀ lǝmdǝa wun;
\q2 wu ɗika aɓwana-mǝgule ma'wun,
\q2 sǝ yia ka à nǝ̀ bangga wun.
\q1 
\v 8 Lang Ɓakuli mana Karban Kat nǝ Gulo
\q2 pè aɓwapǝndǝa anzali do malea,
\q1 sǝ yi gakita aɓwapǝndǝa ɗàng-ɗáng,
\q1 sǝ yi tsǝki anzong-nzali mala aɓwapǝndǝa ka,
\q2 pè aɓa kpata làkkì mala amǝ Isǝrayila.\f + \fr 32:8 \fq làkkì mala amǝ Isǝrayila: \ft Ɓè tǝri ka ama <<làkkì mala amuna mala Ɓakuli,>> sǝ ɓè nyesǝe ka ama <<tsǝkî komǝye atea mǝturonjar ace yálmúrí.>> \f*
\q1 
\v 9 Sǝ kāmbe mala Yahweh ka,
\q2 à nda ka aɓwana male,
\q2 Yakupu nda girkuma mana pè ɓamurì ka.
\b
\q1 
\v 10 Kumi aɓa pǝɗanban,
\q2 a kpakanban mala ɓua mala gung ɓabondo
\q1 pǝlǝa dupi wi ntongŋo,
\q2 yáli kǝla mana nǝ̀ yál mǝsǝi ka.
\q1 
\v 11 Kǝla nkwang mana kǝ kwak abuí amur amuni ace mǝnana ɓǝà mesǝì ɓá nde,
\q2 sǝ kǝ gāɗi amúrià,
\q1 kǝ mǝn abuí nǝ̀ ea,
\q2 sǝ nǝ̀ twalia a nzǝm amburi ka,\f + \fr 32:11 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 19:4; Ang 91:4\xt*\ft .\f*
\q1 
\v 12 Yahweh nǝmurǝì na gingnǝi ka,
\q2 ɓekǝ bǝri ɓakuli pa kàm atè ɗàng.
\q1 
\v 13 Yàl nǝi amúr amgbang-ban mala nzalinì,
\q2 sǝ pè wi aɓǝlagir mala bondo ɓǝ̀ li.
\q1 Linǝi nǝ mùr-nyì mǝnana pùr aɓa tali ka,
\q2 andǝ mùrú mana pùr aɓa kanggǝrang-tali ka;
\q2 
\v 14 andǝ mùrú-kiura mala domwan mala andá,
\q2 andǝ kiura mala domwan mala anzur,
\q2 andǝ mala ambulpǝndǝa,
\q2 andǝ mùrú-nyama mala amuna-nzur,
\q2 andǝ nyam agam mala amǝ Bashan,
\q2 andǝ mala ambulpǝndǝa,
\q2 andǝ mǝssa-alkama mǝɓoarne kat-kat;
\q1 sǝ a nu mùr-anap mala ɓǝla-anap mǝɓoarne.
\b
\q1 
\v 15 Lang Jesǝrun\f + \fr 32:15 \fq Jesǝrun \ft ngga ɓalǝi nda\fqa ɓwa mǝɓoarne, \ft mǝnana nda Isǝrayila.\f* nyan ngga,
\q2 pǝlǝa mgbicau arǝ Ɓakuli.
\q1 Lang lumsǝ nǝ girlina,
\q1 nyane,
\q1 nggūrǝì dǝmbǝrya sǝ ɓǝlki ka,
\q2 pǝlǝa vwakibuì arǝ Ɓakuli mana pè ka,
\q2 sǝ ɓinǝki Tali mana nda Amsǝban male ka.
\q1 
\v 16 À tsǝk Yahweh pàk mɓali
\q2 atàcau mala abǝri ɓakuli;
\q2 à lulbumi nǝ agir'ɓeami.
\q1 
\v 17 À pà gir'nkila aban ankúl mana akukwar na,
\q2 Ɓakuli na raka;
\q2 aɓakuli mana à súrǝ̀ia ɗiɗyal raka,
\q2 yì abǝri ɓakuli mana à loa yiu ka,
\q2 aɓakuli mana yàle aká wun ɓanggia wia raka.
\q1 
\v 18 Tali mana nda tár wun ngga wu burice;
\q2 wu lorǝ Ɓakuli mana ɓǝl wun ngga.
\b
\q1 
\v 19 Lang Yahweh sǝn gìr man ngga, ɓǝsǝkia;
\q2 amuni amuna-burana andǝ amuna-mamǝna male lulbumi.
\q1 
\v 20 Pǝlǝa bang ama, <<Mǝ nǝ sǝmbǝrǝia wia ɓamǝsǝam,
\q2 mǝ nǝ sǝn lang sǝ masǝlǝatea nǝ̀ pa;
\q1 acemana yia ka, nza mala amǝkpata njar kìɗìkì
\q2 andǝ amǝ ɗwanyi domǝsǝcau na.
\q1 
\v 21 À tsǝem ǝn pak mɓali nǝ gir mǝnana kǝ ɓakuli na raka,
\q2 sǝ à lulbumam nǝ ankul malea.
\q1 Acemani ka, mǝ nǝ tsǝia à nǝ̀ pak mɓali arǝ aɓwana mana yàle, à kǝ aɓwana na raka.
\q2 Mǝ nǝ lulbumia nǝ aɓwana mala ɓè nzali,
\q2 mana agǝm-aɓwana na ka.
\q1 
\v 22 Bumlulla mem longŋa earke nǝ bǝsa,
\q2 sǝ nǝ̀ pisǝ nzali andǝ agirɓaban malea.
\q1 Nǝ̀ earke nǝ̀ nggá bwal ban ɓanza mala alú a tà-nzali.
\q2 Nǝ̀ pisǝ akusǝ ankono.
\b
\q1 
\v 23 <<Mǝ ndo mǝ nǝ gwaliki agir'mur'mwana amúrià,
\q2 mǝ nǝ mal amundi mem amúrià.
\q1 
\v 24 Mǝ nǝ tasǝ nzala amúrià, mana nǝ̀ li rǝcandǝa malea,
\q2 sǝ kwánó-ɓikea mǝnana nǝ̀ lia ka,
\q2 andǝ kwánó-twàl-là mǝ'wal-luî;
\q1 mǝ nǝ tasǝ anyamɓikea amǝ'nǝmgiban arǝia,
\q2 andǝ an'yau barya ɓǝà kwarkia.
\q1 
\v 25 Amur anjarɓala ka, aɓia-mǝbura nǝ̀ wal-luia nǝ nggeabyau,
\q2 sǝ arǝ aɓala malea ka, à nǝ̀ do aɓa ɓangciu.
\q1 Aɓia-mǝbura nǝ̀ wal-lú alaggana andǝ ansarina malea,
\q2 sǝ abangna-muna andǝ aɓwana mana à ena,
\q2 sǝ à ndanǝ mbù amúrià ka, à pà nǝ̀ au ɗàng.
\q1 
\v 26 Ən bang nǝma ɓǝ́ mǝ nǝ mesǝkia kuko,
\q1 mǝ nǝ tsǝa aɓwapǝndǝa nǝ̀ lórǝiǎ,
\q2 cau malea pà nǝ̀ pa aɓa ɗenyicau mala aɓwapǝndǝa ɗǝm ɗàng.
\q1 
\v 27 Sǝama ǝn ɓanggi lulbum mana ɓiumǝbura nǝ̀ yinǝi ka,
\q1 acemǝnana yakǝla amǝ'ɓinǝmuria nǝ̀ ɓwarkio aɓa ɗenyicau malea
\q1 sǝ à nǝ̀ na ama, <Bù sǝm, nda mǝnana pà sǝm limurǝm ngga;
\q2 Yahweh nda mana pàk mǝnia yì agir kat ka ɗàng.> >>
\b
\q1 
\v 28 Yia ka, à nda ka aɓwana mala nzali mana à pànǝ ɗenyicau raka,
\q2 à kǝ gandǝ bwaltagìr ɗàng.
\q1 
\v 29 Ɓǝ̀ à ndanǝ kwaro ka, à nǝ̀ bwaltagìr man;
\q2 à nǝ̀ sǝn gìr mana nǝ̀ nggá kumia a masǝlǝate ka!
\q1 
\v 30 Lang sǝ gìrnî nǝ̀ pǎ
\q2 ama ɓwa mwashat nǝ̀ gandǝ pǝr aɓwana á-mwashat,
\q1 ko ana raka, aɓwana ɓari
\q2 nǝ̀ loasǝtà aɓwana á-lum ngga?
\q1 She ɓǝ̀ dumǝna ama,
\q2 Tali malea angŋa dǝmba mangŋǝ́nia,
\q1 ko ana raka, Yahweh angŋa dǝmba
\q2 vwakinabuì arǝia ka!
\q1 
\v 31 Acemǝnana <<tali>> malea ka, pa kǝla Tali ma'sǝm ɗàng;
\q2 ko aɓisǝm amǝbura nǝ nggearǝia ka
\q2 à earǝna ama anggo sǝ pa.
\q1 
\v 32 Nggun-anap malea ka, pur nǝban nggun-anap mala amǝ Sodom,
\q2 sǝ arǝ aɓaban-anap mala amǝ Gomora.
\q1 Aɓǝla-anap malea ka, à lumsǝ nǝ barya,
\q2 sǝ adangŋanshi ɓǝla-anap malea ka, amǝ'lùlle na.
\q1 
\v 33 Mùr-anap malea ka, barya mala an'yau na,
\q2 yì barya mǝ'wal-luî mala aɓamba.
\q1 
\v 34 Yahweh na ama, <<Gìr mǝnana ǝn kanì mǝ nǝ pè ka,
\q1 pà kàm aban ramba abanam a bah,
\q2 ǝn girkuni atà agir-ɓoarna mem re?
\q1 
\v 35 Mbweban a kúnì gìr ka, mem na;
\q2 Mǝ nǝ mbwe.\f + \fr 32:35 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Sam 24:12; 2Sam 22:48; Ir 11:20; 51:36; Nah 1:2; Rom 12:19; Ib 10:30\xt*\ft .\f*
\q1 Lang pwari male yina ka,
\q2 kusǝia nǝ̀ gbǝtǝri;
\q1 pwari gìr'mur'mwana mana nǝ̀ kumia ka, gbàshìnà,
\q1 sǝ pwari kìɗìkì malea ka
\q2 ndo kǝ yiu amúrià a kaurǝa ka.>>
\q1 
\v 36 Ɓakuli ka nǝ̀ lak aɓwana male a ɓashi,
\q1 nǝ̀ sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr mala aguro male,
\q1 lang nǝ̀ sǝni ama rǝcandǝa malea malǝna,
\q2 sǝ kǝ ɓwa pà kàm mana ue ɗàng,
\q2 ko guro ko ɓwa mana guro na raka.
\q1 
\v 37 Pǝlǝa Yahweh nǝ̀ ɗìban ama,
\q2 <<Aɓakuli malea ka à ndake,
\q2 yì <tali> mana à alta àwá abani ka,
\q2 
\v 38 yì aɓakuli mana à lì mùrú-nyama mala agir'nkila malea,
\q2 sǝ à nu mùr-anap
\q2 mala apagir mala girnùná malea ka?
\q1 Yàle ɓǝà lo, ɓǝà bwala wun nggam!
\q2 Ɓǝà pa wun ban-auwa!
\b
\q1 
\v 39 <<Sǝ adyan ngga, wu sǝni,
\q2 kǝ mim nǝmurǝam mǝ nda!
\q1 Ɓè kǝ ɓakuli pa kàm ɗàng,
\q2 she kǝ mim!\f + \fr 32:39 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Isha 40:25; 43:11-13; 46:9; Ezǝk 36:23\xt*\f*
\q1 Ən nggǝ wal-lú ɓwa,
\q2 sǝ ǝn nggǝ tsǝk ɓwa ɓǝ̀ dum nǝyilǝmu.
\q1 Ən nggǝ tsǝk penye,
\q2 sǝ ǝn nggǝ sonzǝ penye,
\q1 sǝ kǝɓwa pà kam nǝ̀ gandǝ amsǝ ɓwa
\q2 a ɓabuam ɗàng.
\q1 
\v 40 Ən loasǝ buam a kùli,
\q2 sǝ ǝn kángìr nǝma:
\q1 Kǝla mana mǝ ndakam nǝ yilǝmu tàtǝ́k ka,
\q1 
\v 41 pwari mana mǝ nǝ kolǝkún kafe mem mǝlinzame,
\q2 sǝ mǝ nǝ bwali a buam ace pak ɓashi ka,
\q1 mǝ nǝ pakkî aɓiam amǝbura gìr arǝia
\q2 a kúnì mǝnana à pè ka,
\q1 sǝ mǝ nǝ mbwe ka aɓwana mana
\q2 à ɓinǝmuram ngga.
\q1 
\v 42 Mǝ nǝ tsǝk amundi mem ɓǝà nu nkila
\q2 sǝ ɓǝà wal-wale,
\q1 sǝ nggeabyau mem ngga,
\q2 nǝ̀ li nyama andǝa nkile;
\q2 yì nyam aɓwana mana à wal-luia,
\q2 andǝ amana à bwalia-guro ka,
\q1 sǝ nǝ̀ kasǝ ɓamur aɓwana-mǝgule mala aɓibura.>>
\b
\q1 
\v 43 Wun aɓwana, arǝ anzali,
\q1 wu pak banɓoarnado wunǝ aɓwana male,
\q1 acemǝnana yì ka nǝ̀ mbweban nǝ mǝɓane
\q2 a kúnì nkila mala aguro male;
\q1 nǝ̀ mbwe ka aɓi-mǝbura
\q2 a kúnì mǝɓane mana à pàk ka;
\q1 nǝ̀ pàk gìr mala mbwe ka aɓwana
\q2 mana à ɓinǝmǝsǝi ka,
\q1 sǝ nǝ̀ shawuɗi nzali andǝ aɓwana male.
\p 
\v 44 Pǝlǝa Musa yiu andǝ Jesǝwa, muna-ɓwabura mala Nun, sǝ bang acau mala mǝnia yì nggyal ka kat, sǝ aɓwana kwakikiria aban oe.
\p 
\v 45 Lang Musa malǝna naki amǝnia yì acau aban amǝ Isǝrayila kat ka,
\v 46 pǝlǝa banggia wia ama, <<Wu bwal amǝnia yì acau mana kat ǝn bangga wun yalung ngga, nǝ ɓabum wun kat, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu pè amuna ma'wun ɓǝ̀ duk nzongcau abania, ɓǝà kpatea nǝ tsǝkiru sǝ ɓǝà pàk acau mala mǝnia yì nggurcau ka.
\v 47 Amǝnia yì acau aban wun ngga, acau na anggo hapǝlu ka ɗang, acau yilǝmi wun na. Nǝ amǝnia yì acau, sǝ yilǝmi wun nǝ̀ sauwa aɓa nzali mana ado wun nǝ̀ yàlî Nggeasala Jodan, wun nǝ̀ nggá e ɓǝ̀ duk ma'wun ngga.>>
\s1 À bangce lú mala Musa
\p 
\v 48 A kǝ pwari mǝno ka, Yahweh banggi Musa ama,
\v 49 <<Kyane aban tsaɗya mala ankono Abarim a bu-nzali Mowap, a nkaring Jeriko. Kya eau amur Nkono Nebo sǝ wu pelǝban nǝ njar-nzali wu sǝn nzali Kan'ana, yì nzali mana ǝn nggǝ pè amǝ Isǝrayila, ɓǝ̀ duk girkuma malea ka.
\v 50 Amur mǝno yì nkono a eau ka sǝ awu nǝ wǔ, a nǝ ká atà akeô, kǝla mana mǝ'eambo Haruna wǔ amur Nkono Hor, sǝ o atà akê ka.
\v 51 Mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana, wun kǝm ngga, wu měm, a ɓadǝmba amǝ Isǝrayila, a ban máɗí-mùr mala Meriba, mana a Kadesh, a pǝɗanban mala Zin ngga. Wu gandǝ lǝmdǝ gulo mǝfele mem aɓalǝ amǝ Isǝrayila ɗàng.\f + \fr 32:51 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Ɓal 20:1-13\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 52 Acemani ka, awu nǝ sǝn nzalinì aban sauwa, sǝama, a pa wu nǝ ká kàm a nzalinì, mǝnana ǝn nggǝ pè amǝ Isǝrayila ka ɗàng.>>
\c 33
\s1 Tsǝkbu mala Musa amur Isǝrayila
\p 
\v 1 Mǝnia ka, nda tsǝkbu mana Musa, yì ɓwa mala Ɓakuli, bang amur amǝ Isǝrayila sǝ paklú ka.
\v 2 Bang ama:
\q1 Yahweh pur nǝban Saina;
\q1 lo kǝla pwari amur Edom,
\q1 sǝ tǎ amur aɓwana male nǝ njarban Nkono Paran;
\q1 amǝturonjar á-lum yiu atè,
\q1 nǝ bǝsa mǝ'earke atà buì mǝlì.
\q1 
\v 3 Nǝ mǝsǝcau, Yahweh kǝ lǝmdǝì aɓwana male earcearǝu;
\q1 amǝfele male kat ka à nda a ɓabuì.
\q1 Acemani ka, yià kat à kǝ twalkusǝo,
\q1 sǝ nǝbano sǝ à kǝ kum kanigir,
\q1 
\v 4 yì nggurcau mana Musa pà sǝm,
\q1 mǝnana nda girkuma mala ɓwabundǝa mala Yakupu ka.
\q1 
\v 5 Yahweh yi duk murǝm amur Jesǝrun,\f + \fr 33:5 \fq Jesǝrun \ft ko aɓwana male, amǝ Isǝrayila.\f*
\q1 lang aɓwana-mǝgule andǝ atau mala Isǝrayila kat
\q1 yi ram rǝia abanɓwáná ka.
\b
\q1 
\v 6 Nying tàu mala Ruben ɓǝ̀ auwa, ɓǝ̀ kǝa wù ɗàng, sǝama aburana male ɓǝà ue kpokyak.\f + \fr 33:6 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Tite 49:3-4; Akas 5:15-16\xt*\ft .\f*
\m 
\v 7 Sǝ amur tàu mala Yahuda ka bang ama:
\q1 We Yahweh, ok ɓua mala Yahuda, sǝ wu yinǝi ɓǝ̀ kùtí aɓalǝ aɓwana male.
\q1 Kat andǝ amani ama, nǝ abui sǝ kǝ munǝo ace ɓamúrì ka,
\q1 awu nǝ bwali wi kàm arǝ aɓimǝbura!
\m 
\v 8 Amur tàu mala Lawi ka, bang ama:
\q1 Tummim mò andǝ Urim mò\f + \fr 33:8 \fq Tummim mò andǝ Urim mò \ft ka nda dobuno-pǝris, ko agir mǝnana apǝris pàngŋǝ̀nà-túró nǝia ace kum eare mana à alte aban Ɓakuli ka. \f* ka, amala Lawi, ɓwa mǝɓafoe mò na,
\q1 mǝnana a mwami a Massa,
\q1 a nungirǝu wunǝi a máɗí-mùr mala Meriba ka.\f + \fr 33:8 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pur 17:1-7; Ɓal 20:2-13; Nggur 6:16; 9:22; Ang 95:8\xt*\ft .\f*
\q1 
\v 9 Yì ka nacau amur tárrí andǝ ngge ama,
\q1 <<Yàle, ǝn dǝmbǝricea ɗàng.>>
\q1 Pǝlǝa lǝmdǝ ama, súrǝ̀ amǝ'eambi ɗàng, sǝ amuna male ka, būrǝcea.
\q1 Sǝama, bwal cau mò,
\q1 sǝ tsǝkiri arǝ yál kùrcau mò.
\q1 
\v 10 Yi ka, nǝ̀ kanî Yakupu anzongcau mò,
\q1 sǝ nǝ̀ kanî amǝ Isǝrayila anggurcau mò.
\q1 Nǝ̀ yinǝ pàgir mala pisǝ muku-gìr loasǝ yele mǝ'rǝmɓoarne a ɓadǝmbo,
\q1 andǝ apagir mala pisǝe kǝring amur gyangŋan mò.
\q1 
\v 11 We Yahweh, tsǝkbuo amur sǝlǝpe male,
\q1 sǝ wu ak túróbù male.
\q1 Ɓungi ankpakota aɓimǝbura andǝ mala amǝ'ɓinǝmúrí
\q1 ace mǝnana ɓǝà kǝa gandǝ lo ɗǝm raka.
\m 
\v 12 Amur tàu mala Benjami ka, bang ama:
\q1 Ɓwa mǝnana Yahweh earkiyi ace raka, ɓǝ̀ do a nkanggari aɓata yalban male.
\q1 Acemǝnana Yahweh kǝ pu amurí koya bu-pwari ka,
\q1 a nkpamtar Yahweh sǝ kǝ usǝlǝo.
\m 
\v 13 Amur tàu mala Yisǝfu ka, bang ama:
\q1 Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝkî nzali male bù nǝ aɓoro mǝɓoarne kat-kat mala kùli,
\q1 mala ncimna, andǝ mala amúr mǝlime mǝnana à nong atà nzali ka;
\q1 
\v 14 andǝ mala aɓoro mǝɓoarne kat-kat mǝnana pwari yikiyinǝi ka, yì aɓǝlagir,
\q1 andǝ mala aɓoro mǝɓoarne kat-kat mǝnana koya zongŋo kǝ pusǝ ka;
\q1 
\v 15 andǝ agir mǝɓoarne kat-kat mala ankono share-ɓanza,
\q1 andǝ mala ɓoro mǝɓoarne kat-kat mala amgbang-ban mala anza ɓara-ɓara;\f + \fr 33:15 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 49:26; Hab 3:6\xt*\ft .\f*
\q1 
\v 16 andǝ mala aɓoro mǝɓoarne kat-kat mala nzali,
\q1 andǝ agir mǝnana kat aɓalǝi ka;
\q1 andǝ dǝmcauwa mala ɓwa mǝnana ndanǝdo\f + \fr 33:16 \fq ndanǝdo \ft ko pusǝrǝi\f* aɓa nkwarki\f + \fr 33:16 \fq nkwarki: \ft nkwarki mana kǝ earki bǝsa à bangce aɓa \xt Pur 3:3-4\xt*\ft ka.\f* ka.
\q1 Agir mǝnia kat ka, ɓǝà yiu amur Yisǝfu,
\q1 a kún-múr ɓwa mǝnana à tàrì-ɗàng aɓalǝ amǝ'eambi ka.
\q1 
\v 17 Aɓa ɓoarɓwa ka, nda kǝla muna-dǝmba jamnda;
\q1 anjawe ka, anjawe ndwakan na.
\q1 Nǝ amǝnia yì anjawe ka, nǝ̀ tulki aɓwapǝndǝa mala anzali, yia kat,
\q1 sǝ nǝ̀ ramtea aban ká arǝ masǝlǝata abân mala ɓanza.
\q1 Mǝnia ka, nda tsǝkbu mem amur aɓwabundǝa mala Ifǝrem
\q1 andǝ á-pas mala aɓwana mala Manasa.
\m 
\v 18 Amur tàu mala Zebulu ka, bang ama:
\q1 Pak banɓoarnado, we Zebulu, aɓa purgya mô,
\q1 sǝ we Isaka ka, aɓalǝ agumli mô.
\q1 
\v 19 À nǝ̀ tunǝ aɓwapǝndǝa ɓǝà yiu a nkono malea;
\q1 akano ka, à nǝ̀ pà agir'nkila mala docauɓoarna;
\q1 à nǝ̀ nun gǝna nǝɓa nyakǝti mǝnana aɓalǝ anggeamùr ka,
\q1 andǝ agir-ɓoarna mǝnana à sǝmbǝrǝa aɓa sala ka.\f + \fr 33:19 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 49:13; Akas 5:15,18\xt*\ft .\f*
\m 
\v 20 Amur tàu mala Gad ka, bang ama:
\q1 Ɓwangsǝban ɓǝ̀ pa aban Ɓakuli mana kǝ tangsǝ nzong-nzali mala Gad ka!
\q1 Gad kǝ kumsǝo kǝla im,
\q1 ace san bù andǝ nggu-ɓamuru.
\q1 
\v 21 Tàr nzali nggea-mǝɓoarne ace ɓamúrì.
\q1 Sǝ lang aɓwana-mǝgule mala atau mala Isǝrayila yi ram ngga,
\q2 à ear ama kāmbe nzali mǝnana nda ace mǝyál-múrú ka,
\q2 ɓǝà tàrì ɓǝ̀ duk mala tàu mala Gad.
\q1 Tàu mala Gad ka kpata nzongcau mala Yahweh
\q1 sǝ pak agir mǝnana Yahweh kasǝa ama amǝ Isǝrayila ɓǝà pea ka.
\m 
\v 22 Amur tàu mala Dan ngga, bang ama:
\q1 Dan ngga, muna im na,
\q2 mana kǝ yalki nǝɓa Bashan ngga.
\m 
\v 23 Amur tàu mala Naftali ka, bang ama:
\q1 Naftali ka, ndanǝ kume kǝ̀rkǝ́r mala earmúrú mala Yahweh,
\q1 sǝ lùmsǝ nǝ tsǝkbu male;
\q1 yi ka, nǝ kum liɓala mala ban njar-nzali andǝ njar-kunmur.
\m 
\v 24 Sǝ amur tàu mala Asha ka, bang ama:
\q1 Ɓwa mǝnana kútì amuna-burana kat nǝ tsǝkbu ka, nda Asha;
\q1 wu ɗeki ɓǝ̀ kum dǝmcauwa aban amǝ'eambi,
\q1 sǝ ɓǝà ɗeki ɓǝ̀ lim kusǝi aɓa mùrú.
\q1 
\v 25 Kún nggea-là male ka ɓǝà yalí nǝ bolo-candǝa andǝ bolo-bángŋá,
\q1 sǝ kǝla mana anonggio mala yilǝmi pak ka,
\q1 anggo sǝ rǝcandǝa male ɓǝ̀ pa.
\b
\q1 
\v 26 Kǝ ɓwa pa kam kǝla Ɓakuli mala Jesǝrun ɗàng,
\q1 mana kǝ san bumkuli ace yiu a bwalo kàm,
\q1 sǝ kǝ yàl amur apǝrɓang aɓa ɓoarɓwa male ka.
\q1 
\v 27 Ɓakuli mala share-ɓanza ka, nda npù mò.
\q1 Sǝ anggwarbui mana à ndakam tàtǝ́k ka, à nǝ̀ mbalio.
\q1 Yì ka, nǝ̀ pǝr aɓio amǝbura a ɓadǝmbo,
\q1 sǝ nǝ̀ nggǝ bang ama, <<Wu twaltea!>>
\q1 
\v 28 Anggo sǝ Isǝrayila nǝ̀ do aɓa rǝpwala;
\q1 sǝ Yakupu ka, nǝ̀ do kǝɓwa pà nǝ̀ zunggǝli ɗàng,
\q1 aɓa nzali mala mǝsǝsa andǝ bǝsa mùr-anap,
\q1 yì ban mǝnana bumkuli kǝ nya ncimna ka.
\q1 
\v 29 Bumpwasǝa mô ka nda kpǝm, We Isǝrayila!
\q1 Yan ɗe kǝla we, wun aɓwana mana Yahweh amsǝ wun ngga?
\q1 Yi ka, nda ntwangŋo mana kǝ pa wun gbasha,
\q1 andǝ nggeabyau mala jali ma'wun.
\q1 Aɓiwun-amǝbura nǝ̀ ɓun aɓadǝm wun,
\q1 sǝ wun nǝ̀ parkia a nzǝmia. \fig Masǝlǝata nacau mala Musa aban amǝ'Isǝrayila|alt="Moses' last words to the Israelites" src="CO00871B.TIF" size="col" loc="33:29" copy="Cook OT Images" ref="33:1-29"\fig*
\c 34
\s1 Lú mala Musa
\p 
\v 1 Musa loapi ɓawanban mala nzali Mowap, wari a Nkono Nebo, sǝ kya eau a ɓong Nkono Pisga, mǝnana nda a njar-takuli mala Jeriko ka; abanì sǝ Yahweh lǝmdǝì wi ɓá nzali Gilǝyat kat yi puro a njar-nza a nggea-là Dan;
\v 2 lǝmdǝì wi kat andǝ nzali Naftali, nzali Ifǝrem, andǝ nzali Manasa; puppup andǝa nzali Yahuda, kya puro a kún Nggeamùr a njar-nzali,
\v 3 andǝ bu-nzali mala Negev, tite a ɓawanban mana a ɓangŋaban mala amǝ Jeriko, yì Nggea-là mala anggun nkangga, yi pur a Zoar.
\p 
\v 4 Pǝlǝa Yahweh banggi Musa ama, <<Mǝnia ka nda nzali mǝnana ǝn pacau ace nǝ kángìr aban Ibǝrayim, andǝ Ishaku, sǝ Yakupu ama mǝ nǝ pè amǝ'keà ka. Ən ɗekio wu sǝni nǝ mǝsǝo, sǝama a pà nǝ yàllî Nggeasala Jodan, awu nǝ kútí kam ɗàng.>>
\p 
\v 5 Nda Musa, mǝtúró mala Yahweh, paklú akano a nzali Mowap, kǝla mǝnana Yahweh bang ngga.
\v 6 Yahweh tsǝk-luí a ɓè ɓangŋaban a nzali Mowap, tù aban là Bet-Piyor, sǝ ko yalung ngga kǝɓwa súrǝ̀ mǝsǝrǝ ban mǝnana ɓembe male pàk kàm ngga ɗàng.
\v 7 Musa ka ndanǝ apǝlǝa gbǝman-mwashat nǝ lumi-ɓari lang paklú ka, sǝ kat aɓa ě male mǝno anggo ka, amǝsǝi ka à nda gǝraɗau, sǝ rǝcandǝa mala nggūrǝì ka amsǝ ɗang.
\v 8 Amǝ Isǝrayila twal anongŋo lumi-tàrú à ndarǝ ɓua-lú Musa aɓa ɓawanban mala nzali Mowap. Anzǝm mǝno ka anonggio mala bumkiɗikea andǝ ɓua-lú Musa ka à yi malâ.
\s1 Cau nzǝm lú mala Musa
\p 
\v 9 Kaniama Musa nǝ̀ wù ka, Yahweh lùmsǝ̀nà Jesǝwa muna-ɓwabura mala Nun nǝ bangŋo mala sǝlǝe, acemǝnana Musa ka angŋa dǝmba tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nà abui amur Jesǝwa. Acemani ka amǝ Isǝrayila okî Jesǝwa sǝ à pǎ kǝla mǝnana Yahweh tsǝki Musa ama ɓǝà pàk ka.
\v 10 Twal a bákú mǝno ka, à ɓǝsǝlǝ kum ɓekǝ mǝɓangnǝa aɓa Isǝrayila kǝla Musa ɗàng, mǝnana Yahweh bangcau nǝi ɓamǝsǝu andǝ ɓamǝsǝu ka.
\v 11 Kǝɓwa pà kàm kǝla yì, mǝnana pàk agir-lǝmdǝa mǝpa'ndali andǝ agir-gyambǝliban mǝnana Yahweh tasǝi sǝ kya peǎ aɓa nzali Masar, amur Firona andǝ amǝtúró male kat, andǝ nzali male puppup ka ɗàng.
\v 12 Nǝ́ rǝcandǝa mǝgule Musa pàkki atúró pà ɓangciu a ɓadǝm amǝ Isǝrayila kat.\f + \fr 34:12 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 6:22\xt*\ft .\f*
